


translate English day6_ar_rkn_dea73e68:


    pl "I... I, um..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_6cd9e06a:


    nar "I try to say \"I love you too,\" but I can't manage to force it out of my throat."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_87de8c2f:


    nar "The weight of the burden I'd bear if I said them is too heavy. I'm still not prepared for it."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_640439c1:


    nar "And, at this point, I also know I'm not right for her."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_3281611c:


    ar "...It is alright. You needn't lie for my sake."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_12e8554d:


    ar "The simple fact that you were thinking of me gives me the greatest happiness."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_6263a93d:


    pl "Cut that out! Don't assume you know how I'm feeling!!!" with sshake


translate English day6_ar_rkn_48eca00a:


    ar "Br-Brother...?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ebbd1c8f:


    nar "And yet the word \"but\" has been wavering before my eyes the whole time.{w} I know I need to reject her--right now."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a1833010:


    nar "But I can't shake it off because I'm still a little kid who needs to be insistent with his own foolishness.{w} I'm sure her light will continue making me feel pathetic."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_71c6f41a:


    nar "I'm a miserable coward.{w} But what about her? Sure it was awkward and naive, but she just conveyed her feelings to me the best way she could."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_59cdec52:


    nar "And it's nothing new--she's only ever told me the truth.{w} She's never even lied once."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_c0a77db0:


    nar "And now she wants an honest answer from me."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_161e4e73:


    nar "Ignoring that request and constructing some sort of excuse to escape the situation would be..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_394896c3:


    nar "Well, it would be even more shameful than brushing aside that which lies deep in my very character."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ecaa5577:


    nar "I take in a breath to rally myself; my throat quivers as I do.{w} She's still waiting for an answer."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ea9d9b68:


    pl "...You and I aren't right for each other."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_4cd193f3:


    pl "You've gotten all the best education and upbringing since you've always basically been the princess of the Magic Department."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_2ae15af1:


    pl "But I never heard about any of that before I got here. I basically still don't know a thing."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_8b4ac493:


    pl "I still don't have the wealth, the fame, or the qualifications to be your husband.{w} Not that I'd hate the idea!"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_cfbe0756:


    pl "You'd have to be crazy NOT to accept feelings like yours.{w} I just... I don't think this is right."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_77b12b05:


    pl "Mentally, I'm still too much of a kid to be with you, and all I ever do is slack off."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_3e7b1a1e:


    pl "I also don't have any special talents to make up for it.{w} And I don't want to admit to my own shortcomings here, but I'm a coward who's constantly suspicious of others."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a97ee104:


    pl "I can't stand stiff and formal places--they get boring.{w} So I'm not really earnest about sticking to studies or training or whatever either."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_1aeef8a2:


    nar "I'm so embarrassed saying all this that I almost have to stop in the middle.{w} She keeps opening her mouth as if to argue, then closing it right after."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_6150e85c:


    pl "But you're... You're so different.{w} Arnie, you're amazing."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_41247389:


    pl "You're physically capable, you have a good head on your shoulders, you've got a bunch of stigmata, everyone likes you... Your future is basically guaranteed to be bright."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a1787167:


    pl "But you never brag about it or get overconfident.{w} You hold yourself down, keep yourself modest."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_4c83a565:


    pl "And I'm not even done yet!{w} You always think of others before yourself, and you're so earnest about your daily training..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_d6a04f49:


    pl "Plus, you have just about the prettiest face I've ever seen.{w} AND a family who loves and supports you."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_71dcae01:


    pl "I don't fit into any of that equation.{w} I don't have the right to be at your side--in fact, I barely have the right to try and follow in your shadow."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_63cd7f0d:


    pl "And with someone like me hanging around nearby, who knows what kind of awful rumors will spread?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ba0e40e1:


    pl "They'll bring shame to you, and that'll turn me into an even bigger burden."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_02b7eed1:


    pl "I'm not brave enough to handle all that pressure!{w} But..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_f64466f1:


    ar "......"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_0d05ec70:


    pl "But I love you..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7eb60d01:


    nar "Arnie immediately hugs me.{w} As her long hair flows down over my shoulders, I feel her heartbeat in her chest--before she pulls away a moment later."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_098ddfac:


    ar "I, I'm terribly sorry... That was very rude of me, and... Please forgive me.{w} It's just, I'm... I'm so happy..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_1ba26c9f:


    nar "She puts a hand to her forehead, her face a mess.{w} Apparently she was heating up--a fact from which I once again felt her true feelings."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_142cbaa7:


    nar "I was really happy for it too, but the first thing that hit me was a disgusted fear."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_3904dfb0:


    nar "Before I could ask a stupid question, I placed one of my hands on her."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_5ba3ff5f:


    pl "I don't doubt that you're sincere.{w} It's just... I'm really scared."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_13e8bea6:


    pl "What if the Magic Department bishop finds out I'm not actually the one he wanted?{w} What if he needs to find a replacement?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_9b7e7e3d:


    pl "What happens when you need to marry that person instead?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_601d4c7c:


    ar "In the very slim chance that were to happen, I would..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_0ea437cd:


    nar "The passion gone from her expression again, Arnie looks at me, then averts her gaze."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_8c5eac08:


    nar "The hand that touches me is hard and cold, like a wooden statue.{w} I realize I've been too naive."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_f1b999d8:


    ar "I would surely marry that person."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_e087181d:


    ar "If it meant being able to repay my debt to my uncle and to make my family and this department a little better..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_fe70e83e:


    ar "Then as an Alternata, I would do my duty."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_436058a7:


    pl "Oh... R-Right.{w} Haha... Sorry for asking something so weird."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_4ecae678:


    ar "However..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_407d7dd1:


    nar "Her smooth fingers slide between my fingers, and our hands join.{w} Her stiff, forceful hand matches the determination on her face."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_29d229af:


    ar "In this moment, I'm sincerely thinking only of you."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_bbf358e5:


    ar "If unease still remain in your heart after this answer, then I will do anything to prove it to you."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_d19b47fb:


    pl "Prove it? What are you talking about?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_0a887fb2:


    ar "As the eldest daughter of the Alternatas, I have lived a strictly chaste life for the sake of the man who would become my husband."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_3fb464b1:


    ar "Purity, for me, was something to be offered up along with my sacred heart to the spouse that I love..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_96fd2b0e:


    ar "To the companion I'll spend my life with.{w} I was taught it was a basic tenet to be upheld in order to contribute to God with a pure heart."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7a490e0f:


    pl "...What are you getting at?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_9ca2be8c:


    ar "Brother [na], if I said I was willing to offer it up to you... Would you trust my heart?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_bcddd675:


    nar "I try to sift through the information coming in through my ears.{w} But in reality, it doesn't take much--the implication is clear."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_1ee2fee7:


    nar "It's just that the implication is really affecting my thoughts."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ad93de59:


    pl "...Arnie, I'm sorry for doubting you.{w} I know how serious you are, so you don't need to do something like that just for me."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_5f7a7c20:


    pl "What I mean is... I've never really thought about staying pure before marriage, or religious morals or whatever..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_b4a882bd:


    ar "You must have thought my remark was an impulsive one."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_589b47ec:


    pl "Well... This really isn't like you, Arnie."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_5bc1385b:


    ar "I suppose I would be lying if I told you momentary emotions were not affecting me.{w} But this is a decision I have made."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_8dd97cea:


    ar "If I am able to physically prove to you that, in this moment, I love you with all my heart and wish to offer my all to you..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_393153ca:


    ar "Then isn't that what true sublimity is?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_116e1149:


    pl "But your family's taught you this for a really long time and it's been your top priority ever since.{w} You'd be ruining all of that."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_d773ba18:


    pl "Are you sure about this?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ef05c53b:


    ar "I think not of these feelings as shameful or impure.{w} After all, guilt comes from having committed something shameful."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_58e35652:


    ar "Thus, if I do not feel ashamed, my heart may remain sacred and pure.{w} And that is the heart I wish to devote to you."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_56ddec00:


    pl "I..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_0fc8a435:


    nar "For a moment, dark curtains fall around the edges of my vision.{w} And there, I find a deep part of me."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_44d69159:


    nar "Darkness slowly strangles my mind.{w} The dark is the memories of that night--of my awful, vulgar, pure self."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ed205853:


    nar "Her hand is perfectly steady, yet mine shakes uncontrollably."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_cd7d2f4c:


    pl "It might just end up corrupting your soul.{w} You might regret it--no, you definitely will... Are you still alright with that?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_f6bd3d8d:


    ar "Brother [na2]."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_fc3d1928:


    nar "Softly, she says my name. I look down and wait for her to speak, but hear nothing."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_fdd2aa9d:


    nar "I raise my head again slowly in the silence and make eye contact.{w} Her blue eyes have been waiting for mine to look into them."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_1c07aaa3:


    ar "I do not see how any of that matters."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_0dd26582:


    nar "Finally, she provides the answer I've been waiting for.{w} The words I had hoped for this whole time--the words I couldn't say to myself."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ae7968a0:


    ar "Those above me have explained this."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a982bb61:


    ar "It is purity that truly gives the one named Arne Alternata her worth.{w} I've always listened to it and accepted it without much resistance."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7aaa9eed:


    ar "And yet you found so many other positive qualities that I possess."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a21e20f1:


    ar "You found things deeper down than what they've called my true nature."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_30ba1a1f:


    ar "And that has irrevocably changed my way of thinking."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_437989d6:


    ar "My value as a person will not be somehow lost simply for losing my purity."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a38c28aa:


    ar "For all that I have received from you, I will now give in return.{w} I shall show you all the positive qualities you have."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_0257503f:


    ar "So... Would you honor me by accepting my selfish request?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_79ab7c70:


    nar "I let go of her hand and embrace her."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_1e9ebf9f:


    nar "Her hair, black like my own, tickles my cheeks and neck.{w} My gloved hands are soaked with sweat, and I hesitate to touch her back."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_2a4f02e9:


    nar "As my arms wrap around her, she feels faintly warm, unlike her cold hands."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_27a2343c:


    nar "I hug her more tightly and come up against her clothing decorations, but even that suffocating pain can't get me to let up."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_3d80c19f:


    nar "Vivid heat and passion rises up through me from the floor, mixing with excitement and happiness; it all nearly chokes me."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_6a4779f7:


    nar "All I want to do right now is wholeheartedly accept this person who has fallen in love with me, but the utterly unfamiliar scene beyond her disrupts my focus."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_077667f0:


    ar "...For a while--"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_fdc39ec3:


    nar "It happened just as I leaned my head back and looked at her to kiss her."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_3151eda7:


    nar "She gently stops my lips with a finger--which is back to its normal warmth now.{w} Is she finally doubting this, or is she embarrassed?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ce9b006b:


    pl "Do you want to stop...?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_572e8524:


    ar "No, not at all.{w} I just wanted to ask something... Have you any experience kissing, Brother [na2]?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_81188489:


    pl "Y-You're asking me if this is my first kiss?!"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ddda77dc:


    ar "Yes... I know it's a rude question, and I apologize if it's offended you."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_fbc64cd6:


    ar "There is a famous superstition in the capital regarding kissing to seal an oath."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_b7607ef7:


    ar "The mouth is a passage for words and breath, and so the first time you offer your mouth to someone, you promise to henceforth speak and breathe only for their sake."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_1be0470f:


    ar "At least, that is what children like to add to it.{w} Still, I think it's very important to assign some sort of meaning to it."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_8c72a397:


    pl "I hear that a lot.{w} Kissing, huh... Nope, I haven't. Well, more like anyone I've kissed was never a romantic interest or anything, so..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_c3c63659:


    ar "...I see. Then please retain your mouth for yourself.{w} This act is something I am giving to you, after all."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_6e1d232a:


    ar "You needn't make a single oath or prepare yourself for anything."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ff478069:


    pl "Ha ha ha... Don't think about it too hard, right?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7b4fed48:


    ar "Yes, that's right."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_86e722c9:


    pl "Alright. Thanks for understanding... And sorry."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a3a6960f:


    ar "...Why don't we cleanse ourselves first, then?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_c45f371d:


    pl "R-Right! Yeah. Good idea."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a8f8490a:


    ar "Well, that is... This room is rather small, but there is a separate shower room.{w} Please use it first if you'd like."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_5d7c283b:


    pl "M-Me first?{w} Does that have some kinda meaning too?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_206e49cc:


    ar "No, not at all, but... I need time to settle my nerves."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_8240f489:


    pl "I guess even people like you get nervous sometimes, huh?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_4ebbf917:


    ar "...Of course."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_6364dea2:


    pl "Right, right.{w} Anyway, I'll go in first..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_b2224f93:


    nar "Washing myself in an unfamiliar place is very unsettling.{w} I keep staring at the nice, organized items, rubbing the normal-smelling soap on myself, and exhaling."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_b9e03785:


    nar "It's going to happen again.{w} Whenever I'm alone somewhere cold and damp, I start thinking of those miserable things again."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_8534f857:


    nar "I pour hot water over myself to wash away the unwanted thoughts.{w} I ruminate on everything Arnie said to me."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_ar_rkn_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_ar_rkn_926c908e:


    "\n The sound of running water finally stops."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_2ce45267:


    "It wasn't a long wait. Or, rather, I'm pretty sure quite a bit of time has passed, but it went by in a flash as I thought about other things."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_8ba6f0b6:


    "But when I hear the door open and look up, all the things I imagined disappear in a poof of meaninglessness."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_53af8591:


    "That's how far beyond my ideas--my limited, empty memories when it came to women's bodies--her body is."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_cbbb206b:


    et "I want to try and express what I'm seeing with a word other than simply \"beautiful,\" but no other word comes to mind."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_b3b66497:



    nvl clear
    "\n The muscles in her neck--her tiny little waist--the pale skin enveloping her bones, almost transparent, clear enough for me to see blood vessels through it."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_b7c85e81:


    "As I'm looking her up and down, she gently bites her lip and puts out the lights in the room."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_4f6f81ab:


    "Small streaks of the midnight sun's light leak in through the window curtains, illuminating her.{w} We both sit down on the bed."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_3a982b45:


    et "With her black bathrobe on, and her hair ornaments taken out, she almost seems like a different person.{w} Water droplets still dot her long hair."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_b3483153:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"...Brother [na2]?\""


translate English day6_ar_rkn_71d1a713:


    "Her familiar voice snaps me out of my entranced staring."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_577df8f1:


    "\"S-Sorry. Did that creep you out?\""


translate English day6_ar_rkn_41a5912f:


    "\"No... Not that. I just want to confirm one final time."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_d85306bb:


    "Do you...truly wish to do this with me?\""


translate English day6_ar_rkn_6994c3ce:


    "As I look up at the unexpected question, she gives a start and hangs her head."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_2c68db4e:


    et "It might just be my imagination, but it sounds almost like her dignified voice has wilted, just a little bit."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_613fe5b2:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"As you know,\" she said, \"there isn't much interesting about me. My skin isn't soft like that of other girls, my breasts are not exactly voluminous, and I haven't any experience."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_bb19a76e:


    "My body is not up to the task of satisfying you, and so it may be an unpleasant experience--one you may even regret.\""


translate English day6_ar_rkn_c45c6604:


    "If anyone else heard that, they'd have burst out laughing."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_76cc8088:


    et "But I don't laugh. Instead, I imagine her being in the shower, probably thinking so earnestly about everything, giving a cold, hard look at her own soaking body."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_cc9f1c4d:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"If it comes to that, then just let me regret it."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_9225ebb2:


    "It'd be another thing you're giving to me, right? I've gotta accept it.\""


translate English day6_ar_rkn_e548df11:


    et "She stops trying to tighten her bathrobe.{w} If only I'd had time to come up with something cooler to say...{w} But she seems happy just with this."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_91a52ca9:



    nvl clear
    "\n After that, we embrace, then move ourselves to the middle of the bed.{w} My arm almost falls asleep pressed down against the sheets."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_efdc895c:


    "Each of us breathes in the exhaled breaths of the other, sticking so close that we can feel even a blink against our skin. It makes me happy that, as we grope about on the sheets, we're able to feel each other's skin in its entirety."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_0244e5fb:



    nvl clear
    "\n If there were any lines I wasn't supposed to cross, I've forgotten them. I wonder how other people would react if they found out about this. I feel a sense of superiority welling up within me..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_ar_rkn_f7e040cb:


    "\n \"...Urgh!\"" with sshake


translate English day6_ar_rkn_569e8087:


    "That's when I feel an out-of-place pain. It comes on suddenly, assailing my passion-softened mind without mercy."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_af159f07:


    et "It's sharp, as though tearing through my skin. I feel a warm liquid fill the back of my nose and obstructing my breathing. Blood pools on the bed's white sheets."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_4dfc0e0a:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Uh... I'm sorry, I've been a little tired lately...\""


translate English day6_ar_rkn_e93dda19:


    "I quickly lift my arm to wipe my nose. But strangely, I can't stop the bleeding.{w} Some of the water is still in there as my hand passes by, and it falls down to my chin and drips from it. Some of the liquid gets through my lips; it tastes salty."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_693a3ee6:


    et "Worried, Arnie raises her head to get a grasp on the situation. I meet her gaze, seeing blood on her shoulder, and her staying still."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_cf0e7b48:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Brother [na2]...?\""


translate English day6_ar_rkn_4bf5f79e:


    et "The blood got on her while I was embracing her--it came from my arm. The wound on it has opened back up. I tried to at least stifle the pain, wanting to avoid the worst possible outcome, but it was no good. Through clenched teeth, a whimper of pain I'd have otherwise held in makes it out of my mouth."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_96f82344:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I'm okay. I'm okay, seriously, I'll be okay... Arnie...\""


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7757a942:


    "I grap my stinging arm, hoping that the blood will stop. My neck shudders under the pain, and blood spurts from my throat with each word I croak out."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_f4759a57:


    et "I just wanted to set her at ease, but all she's doing is assuring me it'll be okay, just like me."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_ar_rkn_67a4eafe:


    "\n My consciousness rapidly fades."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_c795d267:


    et "The heat of joy and sadness decorating the top of the bed instantly cools with a raw-smelling, sharp chill."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_ar_rkn_36587090:


    gr "...How are you feeling, [na2]?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_eb3795f0:


    pl "I'll be fine now... Thanks, Doctor."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a8948247:


    gr "Well, I'm glad you're \"fine,\" you know!{w} You really scared me!!!"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_3f483e50:


    gr "What did I tell you yesterday?{w} You may recover from injuries faster than most, but this is a deep wound. You shouldn't push yourself."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7aff6d5f:


    pl "Haha... I don't remember straining my arms that much, really.{w} But maybe I let my guard down because they didn't hurt at all. I'll be more careful in the future."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_0e6bc2c7:


    gr "I sure hope so. I'd rather not scare the rest of my patients with cases like this."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_b41cd70b:


    gr "Your symptoms are so unusual that if anything worse were to happen, we may not be able to help you with current medical techniques."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_9f64b082:


    pl "Couldn't you do something with cursed arts or whatever?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a3a56fd5:


    gr "The healing arts aren't all-powerful.{w} If something strange happens, like your blood vessels dying, it really will be too late."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_e250878f:


    gr "Obviously, I'll do everything I can to help you.{w} Which means telling you to get some rest for now. No overdoing it, okay?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_c33a01c5:


    nar "I remember the warning the health department bishop gave me yesterday."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_06797f5e:


    nar "The pain faded quickly, but it really starts to sink in now: one wrong move and I could have lost the use of that arm forever."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_4def6244:


    pl "Hey, did Bishop Greg say anything?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_966922c9:


    gr "The bishop? He said he didn't see any major issues. You could ask him yourself, though."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_347cdd77:


    pl "Ugh. He'd probably blow his lid at me..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_408eaba2:


    gr "Hee hee. You're so scared of the bishop.{w} He may sound like he's on a high horse all the time, but he's really a worrywart."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_5cb0e229:


    gr "I'd love it if you two got to talk more if you get the chance. Not today, of course, but later."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_62a5134c:


    gr "He is technically your general practitioner, after all--not me."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_82536fa8:


    pl "Well, alright. I'll be fine now, so you go back and get some rest too.{w} Sorry for making a mess for you while you're working."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_e6ca40af:


    gr "You can call me at any time if anything happens, got that?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_046e1dad:


    nar "Doctor Grette opens the door, but before she leaves the infirmary, she stops and nods to someone.{w} I have a good hunch who she's nodding to, despite not being able to see them."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_9d6e941c:


    ar "Brother [na]!"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_5b4e774f:


    pl "I figured it was you, Arnie.{w} Did you carry me all the way here?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_b9cefbf5:


    ar "No, I simply supported you while you walked here."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_8e0a2e78:


    pl "Really? I don't even remember that.{w} Anyway, sorry for causing all that trouble for you. I know it was sudden..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_81364768:


    ar "No, it's... This is due to my own lack of caution.{w} I made you overdo it. I deeply regret my actions."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ae55a710:


    pl "Wait, what are you even talking about?{w} Geez... You're making it weird. Don't apologize like that!"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_625a2475:


    pl "Anyway, if you really want someone to blame, then blame me.{w} I didn't tell you I was hurt."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_e280cbe8:


    nar "Yeah. It's all my responsibility."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_c73a8ff8:


    ar "...My apologies for asking, but may I see the injury?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_3ec27cc1:


    pl "Sure. Not much to see, though."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_cedf9052:


    ar "Hmm... I've been curious ever since the first time you showed me, but this is no ordinary wound.{w} Do you have these kinds of marks on both arms?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_4482f95a:


    pl "Apparently, yeah. Got the scars themselves when I was really little, though.{w} How do they look to you, Arnie?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_1dbd83e0:


    ar "Well, this is the first time any of us have seen wounds like these, myself included.{w} They feel different than the normal scars of healed injuries."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ee6a51f6:


    pl "Yeah, thought so. Sigh...{w} No one's more curious about it than me!{w} One minute I'm fine, then the next I'm falling apart. What's with that?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_b30ca0d9:


    ar "Hmm..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_c6db9bfa:


    pl "Something else catching your attention?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_6b6b1284:


    ar "This is purely speculation, so you may feel free to ignore it.{w} But, well, I believe these may be stigmata."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_fd21f9be:


    pl "My friend said the same thing yesterday.{w} Apparently stigmata have the same kind of rupturing and symptoms."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_91c55b0b:


    pl "And I mean, sure, it's kinda like that.{w} But I already have two stigmata--one on each palm."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_af8a5479:


    ar "To tell the truth, that's been bothering me as well.{w} Stigmata appear on the surface, just above the places on the body with the largest masses of sacred power."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7ae8e81c:


    ar "That's why they usually appear in connected forms.{w} At least, they do for every priest here, including me."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_cdd523a5:


    pl "Now that you mention it, yeah. I don't think I've ever seen stigmata split up like these two."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_6d483091:


    ar "I shouldn't exactly say there is no precedent whatsoever, though.{w} When one's sacred power is higher than average, they can sometimes appear in separate locations."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_d7e1f325:


    ar "Which is also why we can't always draw a correlation between the number of stigmata someone has and their level of sacred power."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ccb21e57:


    ar "And if you do somehow have a body like that..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_f4f1caf7:


    ar "...then your wounds would provide a pathway to proving that sacred power must be flowing through your entire body."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_c948202f:


    pl "I mean, er, I guess.{w} But I can't see the Pestis. I can't even see evil spirits."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7d4a583d:


    ar "Indeed, which is why this is all naught but a hypothesis.{w} It could also be a mere temporary phenomenon as well."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_c6496d0c:


    ar "It's said that sacred power can be given and received through physical contact.{w} That is a discussion of a more magical basis, however."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_6d69444b:


    pl "If I had crazy sacred power like that, I bet I'd have been able to act all high and mighty a lot. That stinks!"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_0646a0d4:


    ar "I can't say I agree.{w} Sacred power and stigmata are said to be blessings bestowed by God on his people, but in all honesty, they are better called vestiges."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_118c09e5:


    ar "The vestiges of our creation by our heavenly Father--the proof that we are all children of God."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7244581e:


    pl "But didn't you just call them blessings?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_e9463327:


    ar "Yes. And, of course, we are all thankful for this blessing, myself included."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_c8964f6c:


    ar "The very reason mankind is able to fight the Pestis in lands where man cannot live and still survive is the sacred power God has granted us."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a4a21c1c:


    ar "We must always be thankful for that fact, never forgetting who provided us with these bodies of ours."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_665268a2:


    ar "And that is the basis of our faith. One day, we shall have to return this power of ours, these bodies of ours, to their original owner--God Above."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_1b145ba5:


    ar "Because of all that... I believe that the more sacred power flows within one's body, the closer one is to Him."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_f952bee8:


    ar "I have never said it so directly before, but I have a guess that the eldest Alternata's short life..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_292d373b:


    ar "...is based in that as well, and not solely the divine revelation."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_1f9c568e:


    pl "Well, that's... That's all not really something I can just ignore, huh?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_fa5c06c0:


    ar "I seem to have planted only the seeds of anxiety within you, and for that I apologize."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7f60787d:


    ar "As I explained, this is nothing more than speculation on my part, so I don't believe you need to take it so seriously."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a64a99ab:


    ar "Though I am ashamed to admit it, I've always had a bad habit of daydreaming during my studies..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_b5e8d2ab:


    pl "Nah, it was cool to hear. And I dunno if that qualifies as a bad habit, either.{w} You're more creative than I thought! Or more inquisitive. Something like that."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_04e6bb30:


    ar "It is all because I was never able to completely shed myself of the habit."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_9ebfefbc:


    ar "I'm terribly sorry for doing something embarrassing."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_76e29de7:


    pl "Hey, seriously, it's no worry. If you didn't have a couple old habits from when you were a kid, you'd be a pretty boring adult."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_bc7e0adb:


    ar "Hee hee hee... While I'd prefer to stay by your side for longer, I must return for the day."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a7d992f0:


    pl "Right. You've got work tomorrow, don't you? Sorry you had your hands full with me instead."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_d8fc191b:


    ar "I shall be fine. I have made my choice, and I have no regrets. Truly, thank you for sparing me some of your precious time today."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_03563fc8:


    ar "Please rest well."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_861cfb8c:


    nar "Arnie pulls the covers over me, then goes to leave the room. As she does, though, she keeps turning back and bowing to me."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_ceedc82b:


    nar "My thoughts race in the silence. My arm still doesn't hurt. It didn't yesterday, either."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_651c05a0:


    nar "It only hurt the moment it tore; now that it's healed, I don't feel anything. And I didn't feel anything until it tore, either."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7f0254f1:


    nar "The only time pain reared its ugly head was in that very moment--almost like it was warning me of something."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_a713c898:


    nar "I go back through my fading memories of what happened yesterday. What's the commonality between yesterday and today?"


translate English day6_ar_rkn_791f24dc:


    nar "Was it my recognition of someone as a woman? Or was I overexcited?{w} Or maybe..."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7df81b3c:


    my2 "This is a sin. You have broken taboo."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_d05b5558:


    nar "I hear the faint voice of the angel."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_2ef6e39c:


    nar "I'm not very surprised. The angel always appears when I'm not sure of what to do or when I experience something awful. And then she gives me her teachings."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_cba518dd:


    nar "I close my eyes to accept her divinity, and in the darkness, I see her vividly appear."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_56931ae7:


    nar "Her two immaculate white wings shine brighter than anything I've ever seen with my own eyes."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_dcc5aae0:


    my2 "The sin of offering yourself to the Pestis without proper resolve.{w} The sin of desiring the flesh that must be offered to the Pestis, without proper resolve."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_0f1c84f5:


    my2 "This is my warning to you, before you receive divine punishment. You will not be able to shift this blame onto anyone else."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_f458070b:


    my2 "When she told you she would shoulder all your responsibility, you could have resolved yourself properly and promised her to shoulder your own."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_1cd95a60:


    my2 "But you didn't."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_453d8424:


    nar "I was relieved at how Arnie encouraged me.{w} I tried to accept her by depending wholly on her and sacrificing nothing."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_1ce31ae5:


    nar "It isn't just resolve I'm missing--it's belief. I am still too filled with the angel to offer everything I am to her."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_27173db6:


    nar "The sin of attempting to accept purity with a clouded heart.{w} The second sin of not feeling guilty about it."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7ce76d0a:


    nar "The angel moves her fingers, drawing an arc along my back, which rests against the bed.{w} Her hands have never reached me even in my dreams, but now they feel warm and delicate."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_5cc895f0:


    my2 "If there is still a part of you that believes, [na2], then I will allow you to entrust that sin to me."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_93796b16:


    my2 "That, however, would be no more than a confession."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_7b163e13:


    nar "By the time I realize the angel's hands have left me, my eyes are open again--and a new mark has appeared on the arm I was looking at."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_1afe93dd:


    nar "If this is a warning, then it's also an opportunity.{w} The angel has given me a chance."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_50fdc98a:


    nar "I put my hands together and pray to her--a simple confession.{w} The full weight of the responsibility must be on my shoulders."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_03122cbf:


    nar "Which is why, even when I'm done praying, I hang my head for a very long time under that light."


translate English day6_ar_rkn_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_ar_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_ar_8804abba:



    nvl clear
    "\n I had a very, very long dream. With my vision blurred and my head throbbing in pain as if trapped in a vice, it feels like I've been asleep for seven days."


translate English day7_ar_c633cf33:


    "All I know for sure is that my consciousness remains trapped in that dream, though I can't for the life of me remember what happened."


translate English day7_ar_7a26e823:


    "I get the feeling I had a nightmare, but I also feel like it wasn't so bad, too."


translate English day7_ar_94aca8d8:


    "With long dreams, they're usually so pleasant that you never want to wake up--or so terrifying that it's impossible to come back to the waking world."


translate English day7_ar_648c3dd7:


    "Not wanting to think about it any more, I sink my throbbing head into my pillow. {w}I'm so done with thinking."


translate English day7_ar_d7ae7cd2:


    "How much time have I wasted reflecting on my dreams lately?"


translate English day7_ar_c4056ed6:


    et "I don't need to waste my resting hours anymore.{w} The angel doesn't speak to me solely in my in dreams--she speaks to me in real life..."


translate English day7_ar_478b31fc:



    nvl clear
    "\n With my head facing the wall, I find myself gazing at the brilliant, white light shining in through the window."


translate English day7_ar_8105756b:


    "The sun, which set during the night, has risen once again to mark the morning.{w} That faint light must mean it's a new day."


translate English day7_ar_91031fe1:


    "My body feels heavy.{w} I squeeze my eyes shut, but the pounding in my head doesn't stop. I doubt I'll be able to rest any longer."


translate English day7_ar_9cc593e7:


    "Maybe it isn't just me--maybe I really did sleep for seven days. For some reason the idea excites me a bit, but I'm pretty sure that's just fantasy."


translate English day7_ar_3923c360:


    et "As my mind awakens from the dream, my memories come back to me. In my head, I go over what needs doing today."


translate English day7_ar_06a49c8f:



    nvl clear
    "\n First, I've gotta get out of bed.{w} I need to prepare for the morning by securing a washing station before the washroom is filled with people, and I should probably wash the clothes I've been wearing this whole time."


translate English day7_ar_108d26cd:


    et "Once I'm clean and clothed, I'll say hello to Maya, then go take the bishop's class.{w} It'll be a little awkward facing her, but I'll just be listening and not talking to her, anyway."


translate English day7_ar_f0780563:



    nvl clear
    "\n Work sucks, but I think I can manage it.{w} I'm still technically a newbie here, but I'm starting to learn the ropes."


translate English day7_ar_b456ec53:


    "But right now, I'm lying in a salty-smelling bed under a too-familiar ceiling.{w} I can hear the footsteps of the priests outside the door, getting ready for the day like they always do."


translate English day7_ar_33fa2f05:


    "I could do it if I wanted, but I don't want to.{w} Not just my Cleanup Department work, either--I don't want to do anything, including getting out of bed."


translate English day7_ar_58c1b5f6:


    et "Is it just a whim, or is it indolence?{w} Either way, I fold my arms over my stomach again and try to go drift back to sleep."


translate English day7_ar_9bbfedfc:



    nvl clear
    et "\n \"I, Arne Alternata, love you from the bottom of my heart.\""


translate English day7_ar_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_ar_db003e02:



    nvl clear
    "\n I immediately leap out of bed. Holding my wakeful head in my hands, I criticize myself.{w} Miserable good-for-nothing! When are you ever going to grow up?!"


translate English day7_ar_eb680463:


    "I throw on my clothes. My hair's a mess, but there's no time to bother with it. If I get going right now, I shouldn't be late."


translate English day7_ar_4f70f1db:


    "If I have time to let powerlessness and contemplation occupy my mind, I have time to rush over there.{w} It isn't much of a change, but I'd like to be a little more put-together than I am."


translate English day7_ar_6dcf8e11:


    et "I want to become someone who can proudly stand at her side. I don't have any crazy talents or useful skills, but she still chose me."


translate English day7_ar_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_ar_9d84731f:


    "\n ...I run into the department to find the morning meeting has already begun."


translate English day7_ar_af1e75bd:


    "The bishop notices me come in late, but doesn't bat an eyelid.{w} She just tells me to take my seat."


translate English day7_ar_319d5736:


    et "I do so, and as I listen to her boring speech, I redo my loose belt. I think I hear laughing."


translate English day7_ar_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_ar_972ae056:


    "\n I can't just let live carry me along anymore.{w} I have to whip my lazy self into shape, and give myself rewards occasionally."


translate English day7_ar_b3fde37b:


    "What if I think about it like this?{w} Right now, at most, I'm just a guy in the corpse disposal team. But what if I married Arnie one day?"


translate English day7_ar_a3e880f0:


    "I'd get to live in a crazy mansion, which is something that never would have happened otherwise. I'd get to sleep in a huge room, eat at tables filled with meals made of warm broth and fresh ingredients..."


translate English day7_ar_2cacb056:


    "I could spit in the faces of everyone else on the disposal team. I could be at Arnie's side...{w} And she could be at mine..."


translate English day7_ar_f2c3a9aa:


    et "Rub, rub, squeak, squeak."


translate English day7_ar_74794e25:


    sc "[na2]."


translate English day7_ar_6e28bd1e:


    pl "Huh?"


translate English day7_ar_3f07090b:


    sc "...I think you're overdoing it with the cleaning cloth."


translate English day7_ar_642fb55a:


    pl "Oh..."


translate English day7_ar_7a2b1ff1:


    sc "I'm impressed at the effort you're putting in to come in while injured.{w} But you have to be more aware. Don't zone out like that."


translate English day7_ar_65b23eac:


    pl "Ha ha ha... Quit it. It's not like you to worry. You're the one who needs to be more aware."


translate English day7_ar_ee3327e4:


    nar "I use the bucket next to me to squeeze out the dripping cloth."


translate English day7_ar_d7c41c27:


    nar "As it firms up, I see a few hairs still on it, as well as someone's trash."


translate English day7_ar_262bc9d8:


    nar "They flow off the cloth into the dark, mixed-up water, and I head out of the bathroom, his pitch-black footsteps following me for a while."


translate English day7_ar_fa21754d:


    nar "Today's job was quick.{w} I don't want to admit it, but having a helper makes things way easier."


translate English day7_ar_560ae469:


    nar "He starts walking immediately after seeing me leave."


translate English day7_ar_54988cac:


    nar "I take the job of pushing the cart, but seeing its clattering contents makes me let go of it accidentally."


translate English day7_ar_a3bc630c:


    sc "Thinking about yesterday?"


translate English day7_ar_b9c1701b:


    pl "Yeah, kinda."


translate English day7_ar_856bef7d:


    nar "Yesterday, huh..."


translate English day7_ar_d0d2ae7d:


    pl "Does the Magic Department not like the Cleanup Department?"


translate English day7_ar_0f05aa82:


    nar "His steps speed up a little.{w} The mood was relaxed before, but it seems tenser now. Maybe it's just me?"


translate English day7_ar_282c6fac:


    pl "I know it's a sensitive issue, but... I figured I should know."


translate English day7_ar_03618940:


    sc "Right... Sigh, I'm not surprised you're curious."


translate English day7_ar_e5174896:


    nar "Our two sets of footsteps return to their original pace."


translate English day7_ar_261d1733:


    sc "I don't mean anything by this, so listen until the end. The Magic Department's bishop basically views the Cleanup Department as his enemy."


translate English day7_ar_a5ce540c:


    sc "We may be the sandbag department that gets all the criticism of blame, but..."


translate English day7_ar_05ab8a88:


    sc "...since their bishop has a lot of influence and authority, almost nobody is outright hateful towards them."


translate English day7_ar_b0723fea:


    sc "Anyway, that's the reason for it. The Cleanup Department won't pretend to like it even when the Magic Department is celebrating something."


translate English day7_ar_92b3dd9a:


    sc "I don't know how their priests feel about the whole thing, but a bishop represents their department."


translate English day7_ar_948d368f:


    pl "I guess so... The bishops were arguing again yesterday, after all."


translate English day7_ar_77791284:


    sc "......"


translate English day7_ar_aabd69ab:


    pl "He must really know what buttons to press if he can make Bishop Haku mad like that.{w} Do you know anything about it?"


translate English day7_ar_f0b40638:


    sc "...Look, you know I don't like talking about that person, right?"


translate English day7_ar_9a2fd4f3:


    pl "Sorry, sorry, I didn't mean to upset you.{w} I just figured that if I knew, I wouldn't go stepping on any landmines..."


translate English day7_ar_a4f53452:


    pl "And I can't exactly ask that person about it, you know?"


translate English day7_ar_6444205d:


    sc "...Sigh."


translate English day7_ar_46b3b073:


    nar "Thinking he's angry at me, I peek at his face. He seems a little put off by the strange topic, but fortunately, he doesn't seem mad."


translate English day7_ar_26ed8e06:


    sc "I don't think it's that he knows what buttons to press, especially. He's probably not interested in the first place."


translate English day7_ar_73b2b366:


    sc "But from the way he acts, I'd guess he hates her father more than he hates her."


translate English day7_ar_7fbe2d18:


    sc "Plus, the bishop's been leading the disposal team ever since it was under the Magic Department's jurisdiction. He's essentially her former boss."


translate English day7_ar_26f0a854:


    sc "I'm sure you can figure out the rest with a little thought."


translate English day7_ar_dce88a4e:


    nar "In other words, he's mad that the man who killed his little brother to become cardinal split away from the disposal team he led,"


translate English day7_ar_453585f6:


    nar "then appointed his own daughter to the position of bishop.{w} That's pretty easy to understand."


translate English day7_ar_16634e95:


    nar "Securett stays quiet for a little while after saying all that, but then stops in front of a certain room."


translate English day7_ar_0ce36069:


    nar "It has the word \"morgue\" written on it."


translate English day7_ar_9a18249e:


    pl "What's this place?"


translate English day7_ar_b30213d0:


    sc "It's where we preserve the corpses."


translate English day7_ar_4a6bfec0:


    pl "I thought they all got cremated as a group or buried."


translate English day7_ar_967eb627:


    sc "Normally, yes. But some families want to bury their own, too."


translate English day7_ar_8b822e5a:


    pl "Huh... The temple really does have everything."


translate English day7_ar_c84bdbba:


    sc "...I'll wrap things up, so you two can head back now.{w} We did a lot of walking today."


translate English day7_ar_fcb04dac:


    nar "\"You two\"...?"


translate English day7_ar_140cd481:


    pl "Right... Thanks for that."


translate English day7_ar_958016e4:


    nar "Securett enters the room and closes the door, and it goes quiet. I felt a brief chill from the door as it opened."


translate English day7_ar_fe84ed08:


    nar "It seemed like he purposely shut it loudly. I know that's a thing he does when he's angry."


translate English day7_ar_71e1cbdc:


    nar "I just...walk away.{w} My tapping footsteps are steadily joined by another set."


translate English day7_ar_59fbd106:


    my "You talked about nothing but the Magic Department today, [na2]."


translate English day7_ar_507502a8:


    nar "Suddenly, I hear her voice. In the shadows, her eyes watch me like twin water droplets."


translate English day7_ar_e6bd97b6:


    my "...You could have just asked Arnie if you were curious."


translate English day7_ar_ebbaaa07:


    my "You were asking about it for her anyway, right?"


translate English day7_ar_071206b2:


    pl "I mean... Not necessarily... Maya, wait, are you mad?"


translate English day7_ar_5a87f159:


    my "No... It's just, well.{w} We helped you out today, since you're injured."


translate English day7_ar_497d2c02:


    my "But you never seemed interested in what we were saying. It's like you were preoccupied the whole time..."


translate English day7_ar_56a315d0:


    my "And you kept asking Cue questions that he didn't like..."


translate English day7_ar_434db5ee:


    pl "...I'm, well... Sorry. I've had a lot on my mind lately. I promise I wasn't trying to ignore you on purpose."


translate English day7_ar_1046ee5e:


    pl "I'm really grateful you helped me today."


translate English day7_ar_33c7d778:


    my "Mmm... It's okay. I wasn't trying to blame you or anything."


translate English day7_ar_2ba819af:


    my "I should be the one saying sorry. I know you're tired, and I know I'm being annoying...{w} Oh. Congratulations on your move to the Magic Department."


translate English day7_ar_9e3c4ce7:


    pl "Right. Thanks..."


translate English day7_ar_916a17ad:


    my "Still, this is only the second week of the month, so...{w} I'm just concerned."


translate English day7_ar_123ef55e:


    nar "I can't respond to that. Anything I say will sound like an excuse."


translate English day7_ar_9cf61dbe:


    nar "Maya goes quiet and stares at me for a few moments before silently passing by me."


translate English day7_ar_fd4c10fb:


    nar "I start walking in the other direction.{w} At first I'm mostly guilty about it, but as I walk, I start to feel like it's unfair."


translate English day7_ar_13ceb535:


    nar "Even though none of that had to do with being in the Magic Department--it was just what I have to be cautious of as a Cleanup Department priest."


translate English day7_ar_d3ca0c1e:


    nar "Maybe that's normal in the capital, but I didn't even know about the Magic Department's existence until I came here. Isn't it natural for me to ask questions?"


translate English day7_ar_d629a1f8:


    nar "If they're sad about losing a buddy, they can make a new friend. If they're jealous, well...nothing I can do about that.{w} What does she want me to do?"


translate English day7_ar_ab6db25e:


    my2 "If there is still a part of you that believes, [na2]..."


translate English day7_ar_47703db9:


    nar "That voice comes back to me.{w} The angel's voice--firm as if to warn me about something, gentle as if to comfort me about something, soft and murmured."


translate English day7_ar_d59a9f54:


    nar "After recalling the voice, I stop and stand there. I can't make a single move.{w} I can't exhale; the breath feels trapped in my throat."


translate English day7_ar_bc023e79:


    nar "I open my stigmata-engraved hands and slowly press against my eyelids. In the darkness, her eyes flash."


translate English day7_ar_8146fb36:


    nar "They ask me:{w} are you sick of this?"


translate English day7_ar_d5102e6c:


    pl "No... No, I'm not."


translate English day7_ar_17bfd8dc:


    nar "My eyes still shut, I shake my head. If anyone walked by right now, they'd think I was insane."


translate English day7_ar_590b49ea:


    nar "The pounding in my temples turns into an unpleasant pain. My head strings and throbs."


translate English day7_ar_bfeca827:


    nar "That pain...is guilt."


translate English day7_ar_68a789c7:


    pl "I doubted the angel's existence again..."


translate English day7_ar_367d3ebb:


    nar "I stagger over to the wall and lean against it. The angel doesn't want me to be with her. Why?"


translate English day7_ar_0790e09e:


    nar "I consider many things in the blackness of my mind, but they all fade away, unable to explain anything at all."


translate English day7_ar_4b3142e6:


    nar "And then another thought comes to me.{w} \"Move,\" it says. \"Go somewhere. It doesn't matter where...\""


translate English day7_ar_0989409c:


    nar "Before opening the infirmary door, I tell myself once again: this isn't running away, just prioritizing what needs to be done."


translate English day7_ar_76a0202a:


    nar "I open the door and realize the Health Department bishop is inside."


translate English day7_ar_7ee2fa2d:


    nar "I know this because the usually warm air--possibly adjusted to Ms. Grette's liking--now feels a little more chilly."


translate English day7_ar_d21e0a80:


    nar "And, as I predicted, I see the bishop sitting in a chair. But when I spot the person who is already there talking to him, I freeze."


translate English day7_ar_737b5c4b:


    nar "The bishop and the boy look up, having heard me enter.{w} It's Bishop Erzsebet of the Magic Department."


translate English day7_ar_da08977c:


    er "Well, look who it is! Hello, [na].{w} It's not often you come here, is it?"


translate English day7_ar_7c4839cb:


    pl "Hey. That's my line... Er, I just had a question for the Health Department bishop."


translate English day7_ar_a0b27093:


    nar "I look away, and the Health Department bishop coughs, his face looking oddly pale.{w} I almost think he's signaling to me."


translate English day7_ar_6295efe0:


    nar "Is he telling me to be more respectful? I guess there's someone even he's daunted by."


translate English day7_ar_740651fe:


    gg "...Well, take a seat. What is it you wanted to ask?"


translate English day7_ar_71d3a1ea:


    pl "Were you two finished, sir?"


translate English day7_ar_c8510b5b:


    er "Ha! Why, you little... I go a day without seeing you, and suddenly you know how to talk properly."


translate English day7_ar_eca77057:


    pl "Ha ha ha... Well, it's not very important, but... There was something I wanted to ask..."


translate English day7_ar_93377dac:


    er "About your injuries, I presume?"


translate English day7_ar_03fb2cfd:


    pl "Y-Yes sir."


translate English day7_ar_a3153cb1:


    er "Then you've come at a good time. We were just talking about that, in fact."


translate English day7_ar_229fb611:


    pl "You were? Why?"


translate English day7_ar_8b0e4d94:


    er "This is part of my work. You may still belong to the disposal team, but I was the one who brought you to the capital, wasn't I?"


translate English day7_ar_2f8a4ecc:


    er "I have both a responsibility to ensure your safety and a right to hear reports on your condition."


translate English day7_ar_cb6198f5:


    er "Because I couldn't see you face to face, I didn't know what happened."


translate English day7_ar_5fc28cfe:


    pl "Huh... I guess you were curious too, then, Bishop?"


translate English day7_ar_d8bc9d88:


    er "Of course.{w} However many mongrels may linger about in your presence..."


translate English day7_ar_52b536bc:


    er "...never forget that you are a member of the Magic Department, and have been ever since you set foot in the capital."


translate English day7_ar_84c811fa:


    nar "This is all a surprise, but it's also good timing."


translate English day7_ar_a721014f:


    nar "If I can make a good impression here, then I doubt he'll alter my engagement with Arnie anytime soon."


translate English day7_ar_071609d5:


    gg "How have you been feeling since then, [na]?"


translate English day7_ar_962aaed0:


    pl "Like nothing happened. It doesn't even hurt..."


translate English day7_ar_736b4f46:


    pl "Oh, but when it healed, my markings increased. Oh, but I think you saw that already, Bishop."


translate English day7_ar_ef7e2a09:


    gg "That is good to hear. Please make sure not to strain yourself again."


translate English day7_ar_e0185666:


    pl "I've been trying my best ever since you told me to the first time. Yesterday...{w} Well, I wasn't doing anything in particular yesterday."


translate English day7_ar_d9ddf247:


    gg "Now that you mention it, I don't believe you've told me much about what happened. Could you explain for me?"


translate English day7_ar_24498a9f:


    pl "...I'm telling you, it was nothing.{w} I went to see a friend--well, you know because you saw me yesterday. I was visiting Arnie."


translate English day7_ar_e7004e9d:


    pl "We were having some tea, and then... As we were talking, I suddenly collapsed."


translate English day7_ar_fcab0421:


    gg "Mm."


translate English day7_ar_667237f4:


    nar "Unconsciously, I peer at the Magic Department bishop's expression. He's listening to me with a cold look on his face."


translate English day7_ar_b59140af:


    gg "At the time, you exercised use of sacred power you'd never used before, but that place was close to a field."


translate English day7_ar_fa4f43fa:


    gg "Your stigmata were probably affected by the Pestis after responding to it there."


translate English day7_ar_4cfce02c:


    pl "I may have been close, sir, but I wasn't IN the field."


translate English day7_ar_a7d09b9a:


    pl "Neither of our sacred power was strong enough to see it, but the boundary was visible."


translate English day7_ar_fdb46252:


    pl "That's why I tried to go around it, then ran into one of the Lost."


translate English day7_ar_2e70842c:


    gg "Why was that enough to convince you of the field's size?"


translate English day7_ar_12a90f80:


    gg "Just because a field exists somewhere doesn't mean there will be any direct effects on your body or surroundings."


translate English day7_ar_2617711f:


    gg "What you two saw was no more than the boundary of that field as it grew stronger."


translate English day7_ar_de5b4e8d:


    gg "My guess is that while you attempted to detour around it, you didn't extricate yourselves from it completely."


translate English day7_ar_d9435610:


    pl "Then what happened yesterday? I was right here in the temple."


translate English day7_ar_26c52d8e:


    pl "I thought the temple had a field around it that kept the Pestis and ghosts and such away."


translate English day7_ar_a237b12b:


    gg "...I'm not sure.{w} Unless you give me a precise explanation of what happened, there's no point in me speculating."


translate English day7_ar_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day7_ar_3fc7e836:


    gg "Allow me to ask you this, then.{w} Those arms are yours. As the one involved, what do YOU think was the cause?"


translate English day7_ar_c9de7809:


    nar "Their eyes gather to me. While I want to get to the root of this issue, I also don't feel like being upfront with them."


translate English day7_ar_8642a060:


    nar "I slowly hang my head and put my hands together, as if in prayer."


translate English day7_ar_b78a5236:


    pl "...Because I did something I shouldn't have. Not in terms of my conscience, or laws, or morals, but..."


translate English day7_ar_2c7ed3fb:


    pl "I guess I should say that I crossed a line that I wasn't supposed to..."


translate English day7_ar_adaecf91:


    pl "Like I decided someone else's value for them, and that was wrong of me..."


translate English day7_ar_7df9d8fc:


    gg "Wounding the body of one of the Lost is not a sin.{w} Nor is having a chat with a girl you like, of course."


translate English day7_ar_47a38142:


    nar "My trembling goes away as I hear his calm voice. I look up again and see that his expression is back to its usual dryness.{w} Relief wells up within me."


translate English day7_ar_51bee4f6:


    pl "R-Right. Things have just been a little complicated lately..."


translate English day7_ar_477b2b08:


    er "Perhaps there truly was a field present then."


translate English day7_ar_e0fb62bc:


    nar "But it doesn't last long. The Magic Department bishop finally opens his mouth and speaks after having listened in silence."


translate English day7_ar_4caa0e04:


    er "It likely would have been invisible to Arne, but of course, it would have been invisible to me as well.{w} You, however, were able to see it."


translate English day7_ar_a6bb5653:


    pl "What? No, I... I didn't see anything there..."


translate English day7_ar_569451b7:


    er "Yes you did. In fact, it was probably the only thing you saw.{w} Both that day and yesterday."


translate English day7_ar_beaa0699:


    er "Think back. At the time, what were you looking at?"


translate English day7_ar_47113428:


    nar "I let my mind go back to that time."


translate English day7_ar_00c22c05:


    nar "Around me... I wasn't looking at anything.{w} I didn't have time to care about the scenery, nor the trembling Maya or the blood of the Lost spilling from its gut."


translate English day7_ar_eba605f4:


    nar "And yesterday was such a rush that I didn't have time to look around.{w} At the time, all I was looking at was..."


translate English day7_ar_c9f1255a:


    er "Exactly. You were cornered on all sides--the only thing your eyes were looking at was the other person."


translate English day7_ar_94e8abbc:


    pl "What... What do you mean...?"


translate English day7_ar_12b5c7c3:


    er "I'm saying that it was the person forming your field, and that the Pestis had befallen you."


translate English day7_ar_545e58e3:


    gg "You mean to say the cause was oversensitivity?"


translate English day7_ar_5b5de354:


    er "What are you saying, Cornish? That's too spiritualistic.{w} I speak not of such empty concepts."


translate English day7_ar_ce4570a2:


    er "This boy's sacred power was likely what created the field. Or, more precisely, his latent abilities."


translate English day7_ar_2c23f0ab:


    gg "...That strikes me as similar to what the Academics Bishop said a few days ago as well."


translate English day7_ar_deaae533:


    er "Hmph. Well, she is a witty woman."


translate English day7_ar_6ac3f650:


    pl "I see... I heard something like that too.{w} She said it was just speculation, but that maybe all the wounds on my arms mark sacred power..."


translate English day7_ar_2ff47368:


    gg "Speculation indeed. That's impossible."


translate English day7_ar_35d56a14:


    er "But it's worth asking, isn't it?"


translate English day7_ar_9090b05f:


    er "I was the one who brought him here, and nobody else. I would expect him to have a latent ability or two."


translate English day7_ar_18b7a140:


    gg "Conjectures like those will incite delusion on his part. They will only increase your risk of developing psychological issues."


translate English day7_ar_12531f0a:


    er "Please. Do you honestly still believe the theory that the Pestis is completely unrelated to mental illness?"


translate English day7_ar_112a6119:


    er "I thought the girl under your command was researching that very idea."


translate English day7_ar_554dba18:


    gg "This doesn't have anything to do with her. I am only supporting her because I believe her opinion to be correct..."


translate English day7_ar_d6929a91:


    gg "In any event, [na].{w} Without any solid evidence, all of that is mere speculation. Don't take it too seriously."


translate English day7_ar_584e1e3a:


    nar "It seems to me like he doesn't necessarily believe his ideas are right--just that he WANTS them to be."


translate English day7_ar_e804f143:


    nar "One of those \"it HAS to be this way\" sort of things."


translate English day7_ar_6e693518:


    nar "But the Magic Department bishop surprisingly doesn't get angry, despite his viewpoint being rejected."


translate English day7_ar_4bdde630:


    nar "In fact, he chuckles, as though he'd seen this coming all along. It's very much an attitude an adult might take with a child."


translate English day7_ar_2d2796c1:


    er "My, my. I thought that, for a whelp, you were a more understanding sort. I suppose the temple has corrupted you too much."


translate English day7_ar_c35ae8ce:


    pl "How long have you been working here, Bishop Eri?"


translate English day7_ar_7792edff:


    gg "Bishop...Eri?"


translate English day7_ar_653d95f7:


    pl "I mean... If I just called him \"Bishop\", you wouldn't know which one of you I was talking to, so..."


translate English day7_ar_a13c02d3:


    pl "Plus, it takes up a lot of time, calling you each by your full name--Bishop Erzsebet, Bishop Gregor."


translate English day7_ar_57abaadd:


    er "Ha ha ha! So these are the nicknames Arne mentioned to me.{w} Very well! Color me interested. What shall you call this one, then?" with sshake


translate English day7_ar_9b01b988:


    pl "Hmm... His name is Bishop Gregor, so just Bishop Greg."


translate English day7_ar_ec81c03f:


    gg "......"


translate English day7_ar_b6f0ef41:


    er "It has been a long time...{w} Alternata children usually begin working at the temple immediately after their coming-of-age ceremony, after all."


translate English day7_ar_0d30952e:


    er "I was already a bishop by the time this man came here."


translate English day7_ar_94f44560:


    er "I've been here since that ungrateful little girl from the Cleanup Department, that you hang around like droppings in a goldfish bowl, started losing her baby teeth, much less the screws holding her head in place."


translate English day7_ar_f1817f4b:


    pl "Huh..."


translate English day7_ar_3ced6b0c:


    er "Indeed, the sound of her head spinning grated on my ears."


translate English day7_ar_4f63eebf:


    er "And I'm sure you're thinking the reason I can't reconcile with that man is because I simply have an inferiority complex that gets in the way, or something along those lines."


translate English day7_ar_6556424a:


    nar "My eyebrow twitches. That was exactly what I've been thinking, to the letter."


translate English day7_ar_a4e8d6a2:


    nar "Not that I'm all that fond of the Cleanup Department, but scorning it just because he has a personal grudge against the cardinal isn't exactly fair."


translate English day7_ar_b677fae5:


    nar "If the two departments didn't have this grudge, stuff like what happened this morning would *never* happen."


translate English day7_ar_2bbec271:


    er "I failed to become cardinal because I lacked the requisite talent."


translate English day7_ar_94e499b1:


    er "If there is one who has received the divine revelation, then it is their duty as a believer to give that person their blessing.{w} I no longer have even a scrap of interest in the authority itself."


translate English day7_ar_bd788718:


    er "If he who leads does naught but stay put, so to will those below him be unable to flow.{w} And so I wish to yield my position to Arne in the near future."


translate English day7_ar_34d0c0d0:


    pl "The position of bishop, sir?"


translate English day7_ar_88840747:


    er "Indeed. Alternata priests usually succeed the bishop's position at age twenty-five."


translate English day7_ar_b87fb82f:


    er "However... As I've explained to you once, that man has profaned the name of our Lord with his illegitimate methods."


translate English day7_ar_8c89f949:


    er "I only believe that he should be punished in accordance with his deeds."


translate English day7_ar_a16702e8:


    er "He has fulfilled none of his duties--as a believer, a bishop, a cardinal, and as the father of a daughter."


translate English day7_ar_0811ffa0:


    er "For him to lead this temple is evidence of the world gone wrong."


translate English day7_ar_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day7_ar_369e9443:


    er "The look on your face betrays your inability to believe.{w} But you may think what you wish. I've not the desire to repeat myself."


translate English day7_ar_4435d8ba:


    er "Only lies bear repeated elucidation.{w} The truth does not, as it will one day be revealed."


translate English day7_ar_028640db:


    er "Man himself can become the Pestis. You would do well to keep that fact in mind, if nothing else."


translate English day7_ar_2197bd81:


    er "...And it would seem you are once again unhappy with my words, Cornish. To everyone's great surprise, I'm sure."


translate English day7_ar_8bfd6dfa:


    gg "...Just as one mustn't compare people to fields, no Pestis in human form exists."


translate English day7_ar_557348c6:


    er "Without knowing the truth, none of this ventures beyond the realm of speculation.{w} I suppose you are free to believe what you will, though."


translate English day7_ar_52d22c97:


    gg "Is that all you wanted to ask, [na]?"


translate English day7_ar_1f97a4ac:


    pl "Oh, um... Yes, sir."


translate English day7_ar_288f81d4:


    gg "Then I'll be heading back to the infirmary.{w} Lord Alternata?"


translate English day7_ar_b9de05c0:


    er "Ah, yes. It's that time already."


translate English day7_ar_6ea27fa3:


    nar "The two of us leave the room first, while Bishop Greg follows and turns out the lights."


translate English day7_ar_c1794ffa:


    nar "I wanted to get to the bottom of all this, but I have more questions than answers now. It's frustrating."


translate English day7_ar_6fe0b1f7:


    pl "I'll be leaving, then. Take care, Bishop Eri."


translate English day7_ar_c07c1b8d:


    er "[na], what do you think of the hypothesis I proposed?"


translate English day7_ar_b7398d80:


    pl "...Umm.{w} I didn't really understand it. But are you completely sure it's right?"


translate English day7_ar_dfeb479e:


    er "None of us can be certain yet.{w} If it turns out to be true, it would mean that you have entrusted too much of your heart to Arne."


translate English day7_ar_eb1e660c_2:


    pl "......"


translate English day7_ar_777a2538:


    er "And, as a result, you would have been punished for going against her--the field."


translate English day7_ar_2d113e47:


    er "Bringing it close to what you said--the crime of crossing a line."


translate English day7_ar_eb1e660c_3:


    pl "......"


translate English day7_ar_f4e3ac4f:


    er "Do you remain silent because I must not know of that which you must say?{w} Or because you don't WANT me to know?"


translate English day7_ar_65c205d1:


    pl "No, it's just..."


translate English day7_ar_6b22a53e:


    er "Don't worry--I will not take back what I said. I need you, and I trust you."


translate English day7_ar_9f2e7ec2:


    er "Whether or not our relationship is one-sided is fully up to you."


translate English day7_ar_7ea08964:


    pl "...If it doesn't go the way you want it, will you send me back and look for someone else?"


translate English day7_ar_ee3fcf74:


    er "You don't seem to have understood me. You are the one person who has been granted to me for the sake of my reforms."


translate English day7_ar_bcd8dd4f:


    er "It would serve me naught to send you back now and seek out another."


translate English day7_ar_6fc3263d:


    pl "Then what am I even supposed to do?"


translate English day7_ar_bf42dfb5:


    pl "I could work hard at my job, study, and hone my sacred power, but wouldn't that all just be the same as doing nothing in the end?"


translate English day7_ar_15f66f49:


    pl "Are you ACTUALLY going to marry me to your \"beloved\" Arnie?"


translate English day7_ar_799f69a5:


    er "Let me ask you, then. What CAN you do?"


translate English day7_ar_0218ac68:


    pl "Huh?"


translate English day7_ar_341638a4:


    er "This path leads to the Magic Department's domain--the center of this sacred temple.{w} A domain wholly unlike the disposal team's, which struggles with manpower issues and has lost its former influence."


translate English day7_ar_f6f9c131:


    er "Do not be so arrogant as to think you can accomplish anything.{w} You would be better served thinking about your own fate."


translate English day7_ar_ed46fc2b:


    nar "After he leaves, I just stand there for a little while.{w} Arnie comes to mind. I bow my head to the empty space."


translate English day7_ar_36c304c5:


    nar "I haven't been able to do a single thing.{w} I was late to work. My friends are handling most of my workload."


translate English day7_ar_5752261e:


    nar "And then I couldn't find anything out, which didn't help my mood at all."


translate English day7_ar_70b2f9ed:


    nar "To top it all off, I couldn't even give a good impression of myself to her uncle. I've wasted the entire day."


translate English day7_ar_0b5d0c57:



    nvl clear
    "\n I originally wanted to go see Arnie, but I lost my way getting there, so I ended up heading back to the dorms."


translate English day7_ar_a7ea09d6:


    "I wouldn't be able to endure the shame if I saw her now."


translate English day7_ar_7547845d:


    et "I pull the blanket over me. A while passes, but I can't sleep at all.{w} I'm too anxious."


translate English day7_ar_7ee9056a:



    nvl clear
    "\n It seems to me like she doesn't even know how she feels or what she wants. Like she's just being controlled by the sense of justice her family instilled in her."


translate English day7_ar_e607967f:


    "If she has more opportunities to think for herself, if her perspective widens, won't she regret saying she loves me and lose her feelings towards me?"


translate English day7_ar_e6b95149:


    "I shake my head several times to ward off the thoughts. It's not that I WANT to have those doubts."


translate English day7_ar_75c9e7b4:


    "I'm thinking about it all because I don't have any convictions in anything.{w} But she chose me."


translate English day7_ar_d61459c8:


    "And if Arnie's feelings for me are real, then I'm the only one who CAN be at her side. No one else can."


translate English day7_ar_2329e810:


    et "But if it's just a misunderstanding, then..."


translate English day7_ar_43e777ae:



    nvl clear
    "\n Reform, trust, fate..."


translate English day7_ar_23612a8f:


    "The more I mull over his words, the stranger I feel."


translate English day7_ar_b3a01fc4:


    "I can't blame myself, really--it was a difficult matter from the start, which is why I can't get it out of my head.{w} But I also feel like there's a different, more important problem."


translate English day7_ar_8c04e23d:


    "I'm overlooking something. But what?"


translate English day7_ar_223f2bd1:


    "I know they warrant my trust. But the more I think about it, the stronger my doubts become."


translate English day7_ar_844ef4a3:


    et "I shut my eyes tight, trying to force myself to stop thinking about it."


translate English day7_ar_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_ar_rkn_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_ar_rkn_c055fc61:



    nvl clear
    et "\n Faith is not something an individual decides with free will--it is determined by their fate. {w}I've doubted and rejected this, over and over, and I was punished for it."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_547f0b30:


    nar "Morning. I must have slept like a baby, because I feel physically refreshed. My head hurts, though. Today, I'll..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_5314943b:


    nar "I'll go to work and apologize to those two for yesterday.{w} Once the ill feelings are cleared away, I'll go see her."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ca964f97:


    nar "I couldn't go to the training grounds yesterday, so Arnie is probably worried."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_c5a7bd15:


    nar "If she asks me why, how will I answer?{w} I wasn't feeling well? I was busy with work?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_e7fa1355:


    nar "I should probably think up a better excuse while I'm at work."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_a74b6122:


    nar "There's a piece of paper stuck between my dilapidated door and the wall with a thumbtack.{w} The first thing I see is Securett's name written on it."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6a8b73aa:


    nar "I get a bad feeling about this."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_dea062bd:


    nar "\"Take your time. If you feel ill, inform the bishop.\""


translate English day8_ar_rkn_f80bc651:


    nar "...After opening my half-closed eyes all the way and reading it, I frantically pull it out of the door.{w} I look around--nobody's here. No footsteps or voices either."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_49980122:


    nar "And the sky... Though the midnight sun dominates the sky right now, the sky is a little blue early in the morning, but now it's pure white out the window."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_d4d43338:


    pl "...Haaah!"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_a71b4802:


    nar "My lungs involuntarily take in a breath of air. Everything that follows happens in an instant."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_7e083294:


    nar "I rush back into my room, throw on my cassock, then dash out of the dorms over the smooth floors."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_3f652856:


    nar "My hair flutters, and the cold wind grazes against my flushed right cheek."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_b1c57bfe:


    nar "I reach the temple entrance out of breath, but I spur myself on and continue running."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_27e9f8fa:


    nar "What am I doing? Have I become this lazy? How am I supposed to show my face to Arnie like this?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_9fb31761:


    nar "When I think that, I unconsciously sniffle. Feeling like I'll burst into tears otherwise, I give a firm shake of my head. I just have to be in time. If I'm in time, I can still..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_c66c896d:


    nar "The department room is empty, absent of the bishop or the other familiar priests, but I can hear a little bit of talking.{w} Several priests are inside."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_07d94656:


    nar "Despite seeing them every day, I can't get used to those scoundrels."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_25577766:


    nar "As soon as I open the door, they all quickly shut their mouths and grin in my direction."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_f7ff7d3c:


    nar "I look at my feet to avoid their stares and quickly enter the room."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_041a91d6:


    nar "I snatch up the folder from my desk--the only folder left in the room."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_21418d0d:


    nar "I'm grateful for the consideration, but standing out like this is going to spread rumors of me being some kind of problem child."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_9c791fb7:


    ex1 "Whoa! Must be nice. Hey, think if we got specially selected by the Magic Department, we'd be able to do whatever the heck we wanted?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_f180798a:


    nar "My skin crawls. I expected them to be talking about me, but my head suddenly comes back up and glares at them.{w} And I regret it immediately."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_b9904d96:


    ex2 "Hoo, boy, if eyes could kill!"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_057087ad:


    ex3 "You idiot. It's because you were so loud about it!"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_82d26e89:


    ex1 "Oh, who cares. I'm envious and that's a compliment. Right?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6f98641c:


    nar "My body shivers as though a terrible chill has settled over it, but everything from the neck up is hot. My face burns."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_60934f49:


    nar "Despite how hard I'm grinding my teeth, my ragged breath escapes from between them."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6de7cbc1:


    nar "The word \"stop\" floats through the mess in my mind, but I don't have the time to think about what to do with that warning-like word."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_b5b25e9f:


    pl "Why?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_f369433e:


    nar "Why are you doing this to me? What did I ever do to you? That's what I try to say, but I can't."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_57479033:


    nar "The sadness wells up from my throat before I can, and I feel like if I say any more, the tears I've been holding back are going to rush forth."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_5f799db3:


    nar "So the words get stuck in my throat and don't come out.{w} They're silent for a moment, but then they narrow their eyes and look between themselves and me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_b5d173b0:


    nar "And then one of them finally slips up, laughing, causing the other two to join in with him."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_5b8e93ef:


    nar "Their dry laughter drowns out the silence in the room."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_55c8f277:


    nar "The three men hit each other's shoulders and legs as they laugh uproariously, leaving me standing there, frozen."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_f997e2d6:


    ex1 "Why am I jealous? Because you're an incompetent loser from God knows where who got thrown a bone, sold his body, and ended up getting into the Magic Department!"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_772fb86b:


    nar "My hands immediately grab the legs of the desk next to me and lift it up."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_330f5042:


    nar "As it overturns, all sorts of things fall out of the drawer, and then it leaves my hands."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_e513d2bc:


    nar "Like a radio suddenly being turned off, the slam of the desk on the floor stops their laughter dead in its tracks."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_ar_rkn_9c6eac8c:


    "{nw}" with sshake


translate English day8_ar_rkn_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_ar_rkn_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_ar_rkn_91f52706:


    "\n As the center one goes down, the other two struggle to turn their necks. I'm faster. I pick up a chair and brandish it overhead."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_e2fb3e06:


    "Every time I smash it down on their bodies with so much in them or on their hard skulls, I feel the vibrations resonate through the chair."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_d348e6b5:


    "An ugly figure passes by me from behind, throws the door open, and runs away. My hands start to get numb. Their beastlike moans and shrieks have steadily stopped."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_9774a631:


    "Suddenly, I lost my balance and fall."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_a4abe6bf:


    "A burning pain spreads through the back of my head, and my vision twists and warps like I'm standing in the middle of roaring flames."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_05e8f991:


    et "A man springs into view, holding a shovel, glaring at me with blood-red eyes."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_ar_rkn_dc80aeff:


    "\n \"You little bitch! You're trash! You're scum!\""


translate English day8_ar_rkn_d345a974:


    "His red, cracked lips expel pure indignation.{w} Lukewarm saliva flies into my face."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_0a2a0442:


    et "I still don't know what I was thinking.{w} But I manage to yank the shovel out of his hands, and his fists don't hurt even a little."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_0535a3b0:



    nvl clear
    "\n I see his purple uvula dangling in the air from his screams. But I don't hear any words anymore."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_cdc78d9b:


    "It was the same the other day. I can't sense anything but what's happening right in front of me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_7c64f98c:


    "I squeeze my hot, sweat-slicked hands around the shovel's shaft and bring it down with all my might.{w} A hard, muddy liquid falls apart, spilling all over the floor."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_690bff61:


    "A dull thud. The momentary feeling in my hands of metal against someone's head--"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_618b1be4:


    et "Flabby, limp limbs. Blood and sweat scattered atop crushed flesh. Before the foam rises to his mouth, he squeezes out one word: \"Stop.\""


translate English day8_ar_rkn_10df87cb:



    nvl clear
    "\n He's stopped moving by now, but his wide-open eyes are still staring at me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_f2fc78c2:


    et "As I gaze into those two clouded spheres, I relax my hands.{w} I hear the shovel hit the floor, and finally, peace and quiet returns to the room."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_96ca1fa2:


    nar "The shallow pool of blood near his head glints white with light."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ac9ebc2b:


    nar "Maybe he's already dead.{w} Maybe I killed him.{w} I'm surprised at how calmly I can think. I don't feel anything."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_0a854363:


    pl "...No, that's not it."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_92d30705:


    nar "Suddenly, I realize that there is an emotion raging within me--but it's completely different from fury, joy, or sadness.{w} And it's not the first time I've felt it."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_73f7e5c8:


    nar "I'm sure everyone feels this way at some point."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_1a49e421:


    nar "It's how I felt when I was little, and I trapped and killed a mouse that had left its dirty marks all over my snack."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_5ff64d95:


    nar "I tighten my sweaty hands into fists, and as the pained groans continue, my mouth widens into a smile. In my heart, I'm saying the words \"serves you right\" loud and proud."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_77813230:


    pl "No... No, that's wrong!" with sshake


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6451d745:


    nar "I let out a noise--maybe a scream--and run away.{w} Terror at what my hands have just wrought--terror at myself--begin to crush me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ce387150:


    nar "I run further than that terror will be able to chase me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_50418b06:


    nar "I hear my own breathing in my ears. A girl appears in the back of my mind."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_8f26d179:


    nar "The warmth that held my hand--her warmth--feels so real now. Real enough to torture me.{w} I want to shout that it's not what it looks like."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_48ba55c8:


    nar "It's not what it looks like, Arnie. I didn't mean to do any of that.{w} I wasn't being serious, I..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_2ad729c6:


    pl "Arnie...!" with sshake


translate English day8_ar_rkn_d6f35c0b:


    nar "I see her in the distance and run to catch up to her."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_4e1c5f1a:


    nar "At first, I'm worried she's just an illusion. But after seeing the confusion on her face, I'm relieved."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_577e57a9:


    ar "Brother [na2]? What is it...?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_dfcd847e:


    pl "Arnie... Arnie, I... I...!"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ebacd921:


    nar "Suddenly hearing a stir, I take a look around.{w} Behind her, all of the priests are giving me dubious stares."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_3f1c7d40:


    nar "The strained air drifting from them is almost palpable--in fact, it feels like it's digging into my skin.{w} Heat quickly rises to my face."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_c55a5eac:


    nar "Arnie tries to put her hand on my shoulder, but I reflexively pull away."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_2ea9e76d:


    nar "It's not that I don't want her to. I just want to get out of here as soon as I can."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ea357494:


    pl "Err... Haha, it's nothing."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_be7bd9c3:


    pl "Sorry for getting in the way of your work again...{w} I'll, uh, talk to you later..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_b160667f:


    ar "Brother [na2], why do you look like--"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_80ec228f:


    pl "I'm sorry... I'm so sorry!!!" with sshake


translate English day8_ar_rkn_8fb74d8a:


    nar "I run away again, leaving a shocked Arnie behind.{w} By the time my head cools enough for me to calm down and go back to the temple, I walk instead of running down the hallway."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_f3d659c3:


    nar "I'm so pathetic it's killing me. I didn't mean to surprise her like that.{w} I wonder what the look on her face was like."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_e4991d7a:


    nar "It's still early. I should go back to work right now."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_d6b6c3b7:


    nar "The previous room I saw comes to mind.{w} Chairs and desks in irregular rows. Garbage littered about. Blood seeping into the wooden floors..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_cd1faf49:


    nar "And a bloodied man who might still be sleeping on the floor."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_344b283d:


    nar "I have none of the courage I'd need to go back there. But all the paperwork and tools are in that room."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_7394320a:



    nvl clear
    "\n I scratch my head, puzzling over what to do, then feel something jutting out of my skin.{w} I bring my hand down; my nail has a foreign, dark-black thing stuck to it, as well as a tangle of hair."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_154534b5:


    "The blood clotted there.{w} I stop in my tracks. A man I don't know is reflected in the window pane."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_0c6acf61:


    "Disheveled hair to cover the face. Two eyeballs, bloodshot, visible past the low-hanging hairs. Hardened blood stuck to dry lips..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_51fd7a7a:


    "That man is none other than me.{w} I recall what Arnie said in shock. This is what she saw."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_3c467c02:


    "Everyone there saw, too, not just her.{w} I hold in the urge to give a few fake laughs."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_935fad61:


    et "My face is hot--all the way to my ears now."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_ar_rkn_371f58a3:


    "\n I take a shower right away, then go back to my room.{w} I lock the door, too, despite knowing nobody is going to come visit."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_fa256f2c:


    "I sit on the side of my bed for a while before undoing my bandages on a hunch."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_f74f39a9:


    "My hand trembled in fear, but there's nothing wrong with my arm. It doesn't particularly hurt anywhere, either.{w} I finally breathe a sigh of relief."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_38cce470:


    "That's right. This means I haven't broken a taboo. This means I haven't done anything the angel would warn me against."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_b045e260:


    "I just did what I could, naturally. They humiliated Arnie and me. They needed to be suitably punished."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_3d461236:


    et "And I handed down that punishment. I'm not to blame..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_d9c0b641:



    nvl clear
    "\n I join my hands and close my eyes to pray to the angel.{w} But I don't get any answers from her."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_3b2121f1:


    "Feeling empty, I open my eyes again. I hear the bell notifying everyone that it's lunchtime."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_8154f626:


    "Maybe it's just how hazy my mind is right now, but all my emotions are blurring my memory. I start to get pointlessly irritated."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_0fbf824c:


    et "No matter what else I do, or did, today, I have to go see Arnie.{w} Otherwise, today will turn out to be another worthless day."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_fa3d25ed:



    nvl clear
    "\n I'm scared of wasting time. It's an instinctual fear, without a clear reason."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_e5bfa6b2:


    "But on the other hand, I get so angry when I ask myself why I've never thought about it before."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_21f79992:


    "If I'd realized sooner, I might have been able to be normal.{w} The anxiety, the unease tormenting me wouldn't have been quite as powerful."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_3e8d4318:


    "And I start to feel like I don't even have much time left at all--though I don't know the reason."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_2477e13b:


    et "I'm sure there's something I need to do right now. Something that can ONLY be done right now."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_75a68187:


    ar "Brother, are you truly alright?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_d0369ae4:


    pl "Oh, uh... Yeah.{w} I told you, I got mixed up in an accident at work and was kind of in shock."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_35c2574a:


    ar "I see..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_9841498f:


    ar "You've wounded your head, though. While you may feel fine now, there's no telling if and when symptoms might appear."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_331b0bbb:


    ar "Please pay a visit to the infirmary before going back to your room today."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_86ec7ae4:


    en "That's right. A whole lot of people heard about your injuries. They're worried about you."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_4caffecd:


    pl "Ha ha ha... Thanks. Both of you."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_d820d745:


    nar "I was a fool for thinking I could talk to Arnie alone like nothing had happened."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_3fe07742:


    nar "I don't hate talking to Enoch, but with what happened yesterday, it's still awkward to be with him."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_c70edb0f:


    nar "He gives a big, goofy smile whenever our eyes meet, as though he understands how I feel.{w} His unevenly sharp teeth get to me though."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6e1785f6:


    pl "Sorry for bothering you while you were resting."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_c761c68b:


    ar "Please, think nothing of it. We both think of you as family. You needn't apologize."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_93763e51:


    en "She's right, y'know. We enjoy being in your company, [na]."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_10b2f129:


    pl "I'm happy to hear it.{w} Oh, and sorry for not visiting yesterday. Nothing happened, right?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_cfcfdf73:


    en "Nothing happened? Well, Sis here was worried sick that you didn't say anything about not coming."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_aec5a861:


    ar "Enoch, you don't need to harp on it..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_385b4077:


    en "No point keeping it a secret, right?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_62c54a4c:


    en "Ha! We got some tea leaves from the Academics Department we wanted to share with you.{w} Want some?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_4d24885c:


    pl "Thanks, but I'll pass today. It's so hot outside, so...{w} Do you have any snacks or anything?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_c6e8228f:


    ar "We do not. I'm terribly sorry..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_5f2206f8:


    en "The Magic Department doesn't really do the whole \"treats with tea\" thing."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ed152bfb:


    en "Magicians need to train their bodies. Consuming too much wheat flour and sugar is bad for the health."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_3fa776f9:


    pl "Oh... I didn't know that. That'd be pretty rough for me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_bc330017:


    pl "Not that I'm in love with sugary treats or anything, but whenever Dr. Grette offers some, I can't stop myself, y'know?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_213ccb9c:


    ar "Auxiliary Bishop Grette is incredible at baking them, after all."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_b6588986:


    ar "Unfortunately, I must refuse any food from outside, so I don't get many chances to actually eat them."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_bef5d1ae:


    pl "Wait, you can't eat stuff from the outside?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_64f902b1:


    ar "It's a rule my uncle set. He believes only specific kinds of foods and ingredients are pure."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_fe56b1aa:


    en "And a lot of people would love to off her, since she's the eldest Alternata."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_20e00dbc:


    en "Food only gets put in front of her at the table after someone's tested it.{w} Including the bishop himself."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_1b061f76:


    en "Then again, I just eat whatever. And yeah, I love Auxiliary Bishop Grette's treats too."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ad066cff:


    pl "Off her... Even though we're in the temple?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_b97f0f9d:


    ar "All priests receive of God's favor and serve Him with the same intent, so I have no reason to doubt any of my siblings."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_3f769193:


    ar "The reason I can't eat food from outside is because I can't let my family's concern for me go to waste."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_781f4a67:


    ar "Does that answer satisfy you? Enoch."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6db27fbc:


    en "It might seem pretty strict, but it's best to stop danger before it happens."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_42e10978:


    nar "I look at them again. They're so tall I have to look up."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_07317f6e:


    pl "...So that's why you're always near Arnie, huh? Since you have to protect her."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6728bec6:


    en "Yeah, pretty much..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_cf3b66e0:


    en "But I'm far from being a master, so a lot of the time she ends up protecting me instead!"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_0cd9f21a:


    ar "Just knowing someone is there to watch my back is enough to reassure me, however."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_9bccd55d:


    pl "You two really get along like two peas in a pod, huh..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_5b034900:


    en "......"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_e410abc0:


    pl "...Like you were even BORN together."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_2dbd0471:


    en "Oh, well...{w} M-Magicians are all technically family, so we do partially share a bloodline..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_7669537d:


    ar "We were not able to be born together, but we've been together since we were young, so the two of us were always influencing one another."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6dad5929:


    ar "After all, aside from each other, there was nobody we could really talk to."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_32235db7:


    pl "Did you not like your servants?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_7fedacc7:


    ar "Oh, we had no other servants where I lived.{w} Enoch was the only one my uncle let in to help take care of me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_c23945b7:


    pl "Then he did all the chores and stuff too?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_868abe3c:


    en "Mm. It was rough. I mean, the place was a mansion."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_97716caa:


    en "And the only people around were Sis and occasionally the bishop, so it wasn't actually that bad."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_4e839fe6:


    ar "The private tutors from whom I received my education would also change regularly, so I was never able to grow close with them either."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6b60a4dc:


    pl "Did he really need to go THAT far?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_f938cfd3:


    en "Well... I'm sure he was really anxious at the time.{w} It was just after what happened to his younger brother."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_a233c82c:


    en "The others aside, taking in a child who had been driven out of his family alleviated two worries."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_3a507f5e:


    en "First, that I'd reveal his plans to someone else--and second, that she would be threatened."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_7e16937f:


    ar "The mansion I lived in was originally my uncle's property. And ownership reverted to him after my father passed."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_cca6f014:


    ar "Left with a young child, my uncle first got all my father's affairs in order, then fired all the servants at the mansion."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_45f5fc1f:


    ar "I can understand his decision now, but... I was so young and ignorant at the time that I hated my uncle for it."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_c8110d46:


    pl "Huh... I can't imagine you hating anyone."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_b282ab48:


    en "You might not be able to imagine it now, but at the time, Arne was really picky about her likes and dislikes."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_a1f4ce5d:


    en "And she'd get depressed when the bishop scolded her, too.{w} As for me, I had it the worst, always getting caught in the middle..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_64b3aa6f:


    ar "Indeed. I owe Enoch a large debt because of it--one I may never be able to fully repay."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_15c7ed03:


    en "H-Hey, Sis... I'm telling you, you've already done more than enough in return."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_9efeb6b6:


    nar "I nod, keeping my silence, hoping this conversation will end soon.{w} I knew I shouldn't have asked."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_76527e0e:


    nar "A young Arnie. An Arnie I don't know."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_5bde3eab:


    nar "No matter what the topic, it always sounds like they're boasting about their relationship. It doesn't quite make sense to me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_278902b4:


    nar "As if in consideration of how I'm feeling, I hear a knock at the door."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_502c6a19:


    en "...Oh, you two can continue. I've gotta go."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_74afca44:


    ar "Is everything alright?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ea50fc6a:


    en "'Course it is. I'm an auxiliary bishop just like you, remember?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ea5bf6cc:


    ar "Then I leave it in your hands. Call me if anything happens."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_e36c1850:


    en "Right. [na], you just stay here and relax!"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_d8489864:


    nar "He's gone in a flash."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_bf08d378:


    nar "People can be cunning at times. Despite all my worrying about it, now that the table is actually set for me, I can't help but have some misgivings."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_7acf3f6a:


    nar "The expression on her face is calm as always, but when she meets my gaze, she lowers her head."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_57f3c40e:


    nar "Come to think of it, this is the first time I've had a face-to-face conversation with her since that day. Realizing that makes things just as awkward for me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_32bdba71:


    pl "...So, yesterday, I ran into Bishop Eri at the infirmary."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_097aa8ac:


    ar "The infirmary... Ah, I assume you were there to hear a report from Bishop Gregor."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6bc11e5e:


    pl "Yeah, that's right. We all had a little chat together, but it was so uncomfortable for me that I wanted to die."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_0cdf6ac1:


    ar "Hee hee... What sort of conversation was it?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_e9bad14a:


    pl "You know. About my arm. But we basically just worried about it for a while, since we don't have any real information yet."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_033c1ac0:


    ar "I am partially to blame for causing you such mental trouble, Brother. I'm terribly sorry."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_36ed97e5:


    ar "Were I equipped with but more knowledge and strength, I may have been able to help..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_516f7dfa:


    pl "Hey, don't be. You're always helping me out, you know? Makes me feel a little guilty."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_2d8c895a:


    ar "I may be full of shortcomings, but if I have helped you in some way, then I am happy."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6eb8adb5:


    pl "I... Well, I want to help you out too."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_0e689fe6:


    pl "But you're already perfect, so I don't know what I can even do to help..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_4c697c59:


    ar "The mere fact that you live and breathe helps me greatly."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_568eb200:


    pl "Ha! What's that even mean?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_9c3acc6f:


    nar "I laugh and look up. Arnie, however, isn't laughing at all--the look on her face is serious."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_f2ef9f6f:


    ar "I've explained before that I'm only alive and breathing because of so many other people being kind to me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_eab3ad74:


    ar "Their kindness itself is the strength that supports me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_e3ec98e6:


    ar "But you, Brother [na2], are now a part of my life, and you have helped me even more than words can express."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_76801d06:


    pl "...Could I, uh, sit next to you?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_08a3cd88:


    ar "By all means."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_26561ce9:


    nar "I take the empty seat.{w} It sucks a little how I can feel a tiny bit of his lingering warmth, but Arnie smiles at me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_50c1c008:


    nar "After all my worrying and hesitating, I just silently take her hand and squeeze it--that firm, strong hand that seems like it was carved from wood."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_d11ef1d1:


    nar "At first, she doesn't squeeze back. But as the comforting silence continues, she eventually does."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_cf54ba8e:


    pl "I'm sorry for leaving you in the dark yesterday. I'll make sure to come every day from now on so you're not worried."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_dfb2b6ad:


    ar "As long as you are in my thoughts, Brother [na2], I can wait as long as I need. You will never disappear from my thoughts, nor from my heart."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_e8032472:


    ar "Thus, wanting to meet you, see you, and feel you are merely selfish desires of mine."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_231a8c54:


    ar "But if you would honor me by fulfilling those desires, then I cannot think of any greater happiness..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_a6dd1ef4:


    pl "Do you trust me, Arnie?{w} I'm not super earnest, and I'm weak-willed. I might turn into a bad guy who does bad things."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_071354fd:


    ar "My apologies for returning a question with a question, but do you trust me, Brother?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_2bd371ca:


    pl "Of course I do! I've never even thought of NOT trusting you."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_59a76b54:


    ar "Then please, have that same faith in yourself. After all, I have utmost faith in you."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_2e0af410:


    ar "If you are to have faith in my decision, you must then have faith in yourself as well."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_495faafe:


    nar "She tightens her hand around mine, tightly enough to form a bond that won't come undone."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_9c31b11e:


    ar "Brother [na2], I really do love you."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_172b5b47:


    nar "The moment I hear that, my clouded, stormy mood immediately rises, once again making me realize something."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_13b2fcc3:


    nar "I honestly have come to love her, too."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_af34d289:


    nar "She gives me satisfaction with her soft, plain words, making them sound like truths everyone believes in by default."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_8f3abd23:


    nar "And she's always done that. The sense of satisfaction eliminates any of the restless, dangerous thoughts that might be in my head, giving support to my decaying oath."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_c418ac02:


    nar "But it only lasts for a moment. Suddenly there's a hard knock on the door, and all the bliss relaxing my body vanishes."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_0283f345:


    nar "It feels like I just rolled out of bed after a happy dream."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_644b94f7:


    ar "...Brother."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_490088ed:


    nar "I try to ignore it by remaining silent, but Arnie shatters the attempt with a single word."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_7c226f98:


    nar "A bit uneasy, I give her hand one more squeeze before letting go."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_e32810a4:


    pl "I'm, uh... I'm gonna get going."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_820e5422:


    ar "Oh? You are free to wait here, if you wish."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_e0d3e462:


    pl "It's fine. It was a good way to spend the time, but... I've gotta get back."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ed88ddff:


    ar "I see. I suppose I shouldn't keep you here for very long.{w} I'll prepare some snacks for tomorrow."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_bbd81e86:


    pl "Seriously, it's okay. You don't need to do all that.{w} Anyway, I'll see you tomorrow."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_4d0f1af8:


    ar "Yes... Take care."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_70970dae:


    nar "With my head hanging all the while, I hasten past the priests standing in front of the door."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_10e6c8f3:


    nar "I feel like I hear Enoch's voice at some point, but I ignore it.{w} He won't think I'm weird from just that."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ddf5084b:


    nar "Actually, he probably thinks I'm really weird already. But I don't want to think about it right now."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_904cd8c0:



    nvl clear
    "\n All the temple's sounds feel so close to my ears, slicing into each and every thought that comes to mind."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_0bbb0bf2:


    "One of them says \"Man, I wish I was Enoch.\"{w} Jealous of Enoch, whom Arnie always saves."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_8db8f6a6:


    "If you're gonna be that unserious about it, then quit talking about the past like that. I can't do that, remember? You're making me look like a lazy person."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_10702abf:


    et "In fact, I wish an extreme situation like that would occur. I was happy for her words.{w} But that stuff's not what I want. What I want is something more decisive."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_c88f9850:



    nvl clear
    "\n If only I could have a debt to her it would take more than a lifetime to repay.{w} If only she could then give it to me straight, telling me how I'm helping her in specifics."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_972127b9:


    "But for each of these empty desires that I can never bring to fruition alone, filthy emotions well up within me again."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_77a2e645:


    "They've gotten stronger than I remember them being at first. Before I knew her, I never even noticed them."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ba50a982:


    "I do like her, but it's like the clearer my feelings for her grow, the more I lose hope in myself."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_808cf724:



    nvl clear
    "\n And I ended up lying to her again today because I don't want to hurt her right now."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_a054dce7:


    "It was only a little lie, also made to protect myself. But if I'm already doing that, how long until the lies get bigger?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_3c23d464:


    "I have faith in her... I have no choice but to have faith in her. Because she has faith in me."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_78eb36d1:


    "If I can't be honest with her, then who can I be honest with?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_a8257eb7:


    "Just carrying these sins won't absolve me of them. Who can I talk to that will forgive them?"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_03ed773d:


    et "......"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_ar_rkn_c5a920cf:


    "\n As my head dips, I see a light. A faint light that will never disappear, even if others try to put it out, welcoming me with its radiance."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_761c75b8:


    "I wasn't just wandering around the temple--I was coming back here."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_cb4ef9d8:


    "Those two blinding white wings can't be from this world."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_fd3d8de7:


    "My eyes would be destroyed if I tried to look directly at them. My head naturally falls. I drop to my knees."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6b214259:


    "Raising my trembling hands, I try to touch her skin.{w} I hate myself for not knowing a better way to do it."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_6c42623f:


    et "But this angel gives me a chance despite my irreverence. I am able to touch her.{w} Tears start falling from my eyes unconsciously."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_29231063:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"It was me. I beat up the guys in the department room. One of them tried to get away, but one of them might have died."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_3599844c:


    "When it was all over, and it was quiet again, I didn't feel guilty.{w} I was delighted, actually... Delighted that I had beaten them so badly."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_db9d005f:


    "I was happy. But I know that's not right. I can't go on like this...\""


translate English day8_ar_rkn_4d5efdc8:


    et "I grasp her soft hands with mine and weep like a newborn baby."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_21155c99:



    nvl clear
    "\n I'm touching the angel.{w} My eyes haven't been struck blind. I can speak without vomiting. My head feels clear, mentally and physically."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_bd9fb90a:


    "The angel descended to Earth for my sake."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_360a22f4:


    "Ah, what an honor it is.{w} Forgive me. Grant me your compassion and save me from my foolish path."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_19138c63:


    et "Forgive me my sin!"


translate English day8_ar_rkn_05f0e653:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I let my impure impulses take over and wielded violence against a Cleanup Department priest, desecrating the goodwill of everyone who trusts me..."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_aa69cd29:


    "But I don't know how to repent for my sin, so I wanted to ask you...\""


translate English day8_ar_rkn_ac1a5ba0:


    "Given words, my sin takes on weight.{w} Once every sin has been revealed, I can accept this as reality."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_25f856e5:


    "The light no longer conceals the sinner, nor avoids them. Instead, it flows to me from overhead."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_bc910063:


    "As long as the angel forgives this sin, I can remain human."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_62479fef:


    et "In the shadow cast by her wings, with a warm wind striking me... I welcome the most beautiful light in the world."


translate English day8_ar_rkn_76b2fe88_7:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_ar_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_ar_71bf4652:


    "\n When I wake up, I'm on my bed.{w} My head hurts. When I think about yesterday, it stings even more."


translate English day9_ar_9de074e7:


    "I'm also in pain--so much I want to curl up into a ball. I roll up my pants leg and see the trace of a small bruise there."


translate English day9_ar_1e7bf840:


    et "It's proof of my worship of a being I must kneel to."


translate English day9_ar_09ce2e5d:



    nvl clear
    "\n My memories end with seeing the angel."


translate English day9_ar_c42a7a4a:


    "Though it was like a dream, it was not a fantasy born of my own weakness, my own desire to abandon everything out of shame and guilt. It was real."


translate English day9_ar_cdbe291e:


    "I should have confessed my sin to Arnie. I should have told her everything--including what sort of person she'd placed her faith in."


translate English day9_ar_f2998fbe:


    "But I didn't, and now I'm even worse off for it."


translate English day9_ar_8e8e2a4d:


    "The angel lightened the burden of my sin in order to give me a push forward."


translate English day9_ar_0b1b467e:


    "Once my thoughts are in order, my sleepiness fades. I quickly put the blanket aside and get out of bed."


translate English day9_ar_2c4efb68:


    et "The azure of the dawn lingers outside the window, too.{w} My heart clenches."


translate English day9_ar_6e8f8324:


    nar "Before I open the door to my room, I try imagining what's going to happen now."


translate English day9_ar_253d1a93:


    nar "I didn't go back to the department room yesterday, so I don't know what happened after all that."


translate English day9_ar_acaaedcf:


    nar "I can't hear any fuss coming from the room, so he probably really isn't dead."


translate English day9_ar_829fe358:


    nar "After all, the disposal team priests always jump at the opportunity to go crazy about thrilling incidents."


translate English day9_ar_4914eb09:


    nar "I wasn't in my right mind at the time, so I didn't have any awareness of those around me. Everywhere in the temple, it's just people."


translate English day9_ar_6fc2861d:


    nar "I'm certain someone saw me--the suspicious man running down the hallway, eyes wide, blood trickling from his forehead."


translate English day9_ar_4ffd40ff:


    nar "And one of them got away with all his limbs attached, too. The disposal team priests already hate me. If this turns into a rumor, then--"


translate English day9_ar_8bf7f7ea:


    hk "Brother~?"


translate English day9_ar_16102b47:


    pl "...Whoa."


translate English day9_ar_46feaa1c:


    nar "When a thin shadow passes overhead, I get the feeling that it's earlier in the morning than I thought. Standing behind me is her--the bishop."


translate English day9_ar_d2a959f8:


    nar "I've been purposely avoiding her lately, so it's been five days since I met her like this."


translate English day9_ar_c1f9fd2e:


    nar "I'd like to move out of Haku's way and let her go past, but my panic and tension keep my legs glued in place."


translate English day9_ar_4ceba3ff:


    hk "Hmm? What are you doing staring at the door like that?"


translate English day9_ar_1fb5b17c:


    nar "She talks just as slowly as she always does. Her eyes blink, relaxed, without a hint of doubt or criticism in them--just confusion at the current situation."


translate English day9_ar_ab50b6ad:


    nar "That isn't how someone would look at a crazy person, at least."


translate English day9_ar_e2a1ba2a:


    pl "Oh, uh... Sorry.{w} I've been late for a few days now, but now that I'm on time, I got a little awkward about going in... Ha ha ha..."


translate English day9_ar_44f7f3f6:


    hk "Hee hee... You're like a stray cat peeking into someone else's home.{w} You're ever so mischievous, Brother [na]~..."


translate English day9_ar_245bda8a:


    pl "I wasn't trying to peek at anything..."


translate English day9_ar_6b120820:


    hk "Oh, but of course. This isn't someone else's home for you...{w} Okay, let's go in, shall we~?"


translate English day9_ar_a9c555ae:


    nar "Noticing the bishop come in, the noisy classroom falls silent."


translate English day9_ar_e3445c3f:


    nar "The priests all bow their heads at once, but their eyes are all on me. I want to believe it's because I came in with her."


translate English day9_ar_41ad18e5:


    nar "I keep my head down and go to the empty seat in the back of the classroom. A quick glance at the floor reveals no traces of blood at all--it's clean."


translate English day9_ar_c6c3860b:


    nar "The moment I raise my head to pull the chair out from my desk, my gaze meets Maya's.{w} She recoils, seeming surprised, and immediately looks down."


translate English day9_ar_38ab127a:


    nar "It's the same way she always acts, but she's especially awkward about it today. I don't hear much of what the bishop says."


translate English day9_ar_05db3853:


    nar "As the morning meeting continues, my upper body stays facing forwards, but my eyes constantly move around. That's when I notice the seats for the three guys yesterday are empty."


translate English day9_ar_a80c4400:


    hk "Those are all the messages for today. Love one another, as God loves you!"


translate English day9_ar_0d5b465b:


    nar "Her final words break the silence, and the room begins to stir. As people start leaving their seats, Maya stays, still looking down."


translate English day9_ar_bb1c0a94:


    nar "Confused as to what might be going on, I pray that she doesn't get up before I have a chance to say something to her."


translate English day9_ar_88b656c9:


    pl "M-Maya...?"


translate English day9_ar_314ad28f:


    nar "She's not surprised this time. She was probably waiting for me to talk to her, in fact."


translate English day9_ar_c99ae1be:


    my "Good morning, [na2].{w} You're...early today."


translate English day9_ar_b00e5508:


    pl "Yeah, I've been late every day, huh... Ha ha ha. I wanted to turn over a new leaf, you know?"


translate English day9_ar_6dd56a5d:


    my "Oh..."


translate English day9_ar_0131c18f:


    pl "...How have you been?"


translate English day9_ar_ad803655:


    my "How... The same as always. We talked two days ago, didn't we?"


translate English day9_ar_33ed8116:


    pl "I guess. It's only been two days, but for some reason it feels like it's been a really long time..."


translate English day9_ar_c887e81b:


    my "I think you're just worn out..."


translate English day9_ar_7c85aced:


    pl "Hey, about yesterday... Sorry for not helping you with work."


translate English day9_ar_912f03a3:


    my "Huh?{w} Oh, no... It's okay. Cue gives me easy jobs anyway, and I can do them myself now..."


translate English day9_ar_c5434d8a:


    my "There's really nothing you need to feel guilty about, so you don't need to worry."


translate English day9_ar_c7bb2851:


    pl "Oh? That's good, then. I mean, you're not a kid, either, right?{w} What's the plan for today?"


translate English day9_ar_c70209f8:


    my "Today... I'll do things myself again. I think you should focus on your own job as much as you can, [na2]..."


translate English day9_ar_6e855cd3:


    my "I have to get used to working by myself soon anyway..."


translate English day9_ar_e754be4e:


    pl "Huh? What do you mean?"


translate English day9_ar_3ac089a5:


    my "Well... We won't be able to work together after you go to the Magic Department, right?"


translate English day9_ar_bda408bf:


    my "I thought that was maybe why you seemed so distant lately..."


translate English day9_ar_f1898989:


    pl "Huh? No, that's not it! I'd never put distance between us!!!" with sshake


translate English day9_ar_47bee075:


    my "W-Wait, I'm not trying to criticize you!"


translate English day9_ar_ca518b6d:


    my "S-Sorry, I'm just being oversensitive... Sorry for making you mad..."


translate English day9_ar_d64ac6dc:


    pl "Wh-What are you apologizing for...?"


translate English day9_ar_3334fc23:


    my "......"


translate English day9_ar_533f45a2:


    pl "...I should go do my own job too."


translate English day9_ar_bb4b566a:


    my "Mm-hmm... Work hard today."


translate English day9_ar_39f51531:


    pl "Yeah, you too..."


translate English day9_ar_e760b6db:


    my "...I'm glad yesterday worked out."


translate English day9_ar_5e3b7177:


    nar "Before I can answer, Maya gets out of her seat and leaves the room."


translate English day9_ar_79be25c2:


    nar "Though she's no longer in sight, her voice lingers in the back of my mind."


translate English day9_ar_565e49c7:


    nar "The voice I heard that day, and before that--so many times.{w} The angel's voice."


translate English day9_ar_a13ec9a1:


    nar "She always stays at my side, makes sure I'm safe, and keeps watch in case I commit a sin."


translate English day9_ar_195eff43:


    nar "\"I'm glad yesterday worked out.\""


translate English day9_ar_f28ee0d2:


    pl "Yeah."


translate English day9_ar_d2a27a51:


    nar "I say that softly, out loud, in order to accept what she left me with--whether it was meant to be nice or a warning."


translate English day9_ar_640a01c2:


    nar "The room quickly quieted down. The others still here are all paying attention to their conversations, and not to me."


translate English day9_ar_06453e59:


    hk "You're still here?"


translate English day9_ar_1b4dff0a:


    nar "A soft, almost dreamlike voice disrupts the silence."


translate English day9_ar_ac613907:


    nar "She doesn't usually come to me to talk, but with what happened before, the fear in me is gone."


translate English day9_ar_b72ec5cf:


    pl "I figured you'd go straight to work after the morning meeting, Bishop. You never stick around like this."


translate English day9_ar_95dcafd9:


    hk "Hee hee... Well, time does indeed march on. But occasionally you get a bit of free time, and it's important to use it to rest your body and mind."


translate English day9_ar_72dab811:


    hk "How about it? Feel like having a little free time to enjoy a light conversation with me?"


translate English day9_ar_ac5d5101:


    pl "A light conversation with you, Bishop, is a chance to really relax. So go right ahead."


translate English day9_ar_adf8d15c:


    hk "Because time does march on, after all, you must still do the work entrusted to you with care, you know."


translate English day9_ar_fba1c37b:


    hk "You don't have much time left in the Cleanup Department, do you?"


translate English day9_ar_fcdb2f24:


    pl "Yeah, yeah. I know, Bishop."


translate English day9_ar_3761df4c:


    hk "How have things been with you and those of the Magic Department?{w} Getting along well?"


translate English day9_ar_54425142:


    pl "Why do you ask?"


translate English day9_ar_57219cb4:


    hk "Ever since you started working here, you've been regularly meeting them, haven't you?"


translate English day9_ar_11b8aac4:


    pl "You knew I've been popping over for visits...?"


translate English day9_ar_7cf77399:


    hk "The bishops have their own ways of learning things."


translate English day9_ar_92a1be6a:


    pl "That's a little scary... Are you going to get mad at me for being friends with people from the Magic Department?"


translate English day9_ar_f9900642:


    hk "Mad...?{w} M-Me...?"


translate English day9_ar_e95bebb6:


    hk "Oh, mgh!{w} I am not a scary person, you know..."


translate English day9_ar_59434d4d:


    hk "Is there some other reason you have for thinking that way...?"


translate English day9_ar_b429184b:


    pl "Er, no...{w} Sorry. The joke went too far."


translate English day9_ar_dc847a01:


    pl "Their bishop doesn't like this department much. I was just worried you were put off by the whole thing."


translate English day9_ar_b10fc8cc:


    hk "Oh, my. While I'm quite thankful for your thoughtfulness, I find the whole matter just as regrettable as you."


translate English day9_ar_42a01e80:


    pl "...Do you, um, hate the Magic Department bishop?"


translate English day9_ar_5ab5f362:


    hk "Hate him...?"


translate English day9_ar_1e6cb678:


    hk "Why, never!{w} I am only as high in his eyes as my uselessness permits, after all..."


translate English day9_ar_110549ae:


    hk "If I hated him, I'd be blaming someone else for my faults. I would be embarrassed as a person to do such a thing."


translate English day9_ar_b8b72126:


    pl "Yeah, I guess I think the same way... Though I guess those of us who have a lot of faults just have to work harder, huh?"


translate English day9_ar_cbb97085:


    hk "That's why it's so regrettable. It's nigh impossible to personally change someone's long-standing views on something..."


translate English day9_ar_26f7a9af:


    hk "I was only asking him questions because I was worried about you, Brother."


translate English day9_ar_a80acf6f:


    pl "In that case, thanks. Anyway... I'm on okay terms with them now, I guess. Especially Arni--"


translate English day9_ar_920a274c:


    pl "er, the auxiliary bishop, Lady Arne. She's been taking good care of me."


translate English day9_ar_a5f86669:


    hk "She is quite a wonderful person, isn't she?"


translate English day9_ar_67d62797:


    hk "Before her magnanimity and valiance, even a bishop like myself cannot help but lower my head."


translate English day9_ar_2b299c23:


    hk "I've been hearing about her for a long time.{w} Even just the rumors of her virtues and future have made such a stir at the temple..."


translate English day9_ar_d5dfb9f6:


    pl "Yeah, that's it! I feel like she's so far above me, you know?"


translate English day9_ar_5ef1acf1:


    pl "I'm already honored she's nice to me, but she's thoughtful beyond just being nice, too..."


translate English day9_ar_0b8d4b21:


    pl "To call it anything but good luck on my part would warrant divine punishment."


translate English day9_ar_ddbeb655:


    hk "She is a perfect person, isn't she?"


translate English day9_ar_fa99c0e0:


    pl "She really is."


translate English day9_ar_982f29a5:


    hk "Well-honed swords are sometimes lauded as perfect, but the sharper the blade, the more likely it is to injure someone."


translate English day9_ar_1dc2ca6f:


    pl "...?"


translate English day9_ar_6afb4ccf:


    hk "What I mean is, sometimes being perfect in and of itself can be a fatal flaw."


translate English day9_ar_ef95afad:


    hk "From afar, perfection is beautiful, but closer up..."


translate English day9_ar_c92c80b1:


    hk "Reach your hand out, and a moment later, shhhp!!!{w} Of it goes."


translate English day9_ar_58ba43a6:


    pl "You mean, like... No matter how perfect someone may seem, they always have faults?"


translate English day9_ar_60041d40:


    hk "Close, but not exactly.{w} I mean that perfection itself becomes a person's flaw."


translate English day9_ar_390c3a49:


    hk "If someone has no vulnerabilities, that makes them cold--and also unapproachable, doesn't it?"


translate English day9_ar_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_ar_51247eb2:


    hk "That's why any kittens who looove going for walks should always return before it gets dark.{w} Meooow."


translate English day9_ar_c8b4fcfe:


    pl "Yeah, but a wanderer basically has a different home every day, right?"


translate English day9_ar_feb5bb61:


    hk "You're right. The place where a brother feels is home--rather, that is his home."


translate English day9_ar_ecc094c2:


    pl "I'm glad you're worrying about me, but I get it. You don't have to say it. I'm a little past the age to be yelled at for playing with knives."


translate English day9_ar_d5e9ce49:


    hk "Yes, yes... I know I shouldn't worry. I've taken up so much of your time...{w} I must get going, now."


translate English day9_ar_2fd16695:


    pl "Oh... Right. I gotta get to work too."


translate English day9_ar_6a5a4399:


    hk "Do your very, very best today, okay?"


translate English day9_ar_39590888:


    hk "...Oh, by the way, Brother. Have you submitted the proper paperwork for your departmental transfer?"


translate English day9_ar_440d6b42:


    pl "...Yeah, a long time ago.{w} This month's deadline is way past at this point."


translate English day9_ar_101b8fba:


    hk "Ah, I see...{w} Oh, dear me, always messing things up..."


translate English day9_ar_8d882ac3:


    nar "With a leisurely gait, she leaves the room.{w} I'm the only one here now."


translate English day9_ar_e1f61d83:


    nar "What was she even trying to say? To put distance between Arnie and me? It's a little late for that at this point."


translate English day9_ar_4ffd1cf6:


    nar "She at least knows she shouldn't worry, but several of the things she said are starting to get to me."


translate English day9_ar_4b329109:


    nar "It's like a wind brushing against the ominous feeling I purposely put a lid on."


translate English day9_ar_b62a685a:



    nvl clear
    "\n Anyway, none of it's worth thinking about."


translate English day9_ar_4d7481aa:


    "Before the smoke of needless anxiety begins to billow, I use the cleaning detergent and water to wash down the mess in front of me."


translate English day9_ar_817ac954:


    "The melted pieces of flesh look like they came from a different creature altogether, with only a scant trace here or there indicating that it originated from a human."


translate English day9_ar_8b080beb:


    "If I had to make an analogy, it was like an egg that a little bird hadn't been able to break out of."


translate English day9_ar_58d277c8:


    et "But these pieces hold no meaning.{w} I sweep them up with a broom, then put them down the tiny drain."


translate English day9_ar_237fc256:



    nvl clear
    "\n There's no point thinking about it."


translate English day9_ar_960b78ff:


    "Just as the melted flesh won't stick back together and reform, just as a bird won't hatch from a dead egg, it's something that will never happen."


translate English day9_ar_ba7878a8:


    "Arnie has faith in me and we're in love."


translate English day9_ar_7792497f:


    "If there's anything wrong with this relationship, it's me. But that just means I have to work hard to fix it."


translate English day9_ar_e7678e3e:


    "Even though everything is going so well--to the point where there's no need to think about it anymore."


translate English day9_ar_ed550419:


    et "......"


translate English day9_ar_951a88ca:


    nar "On my way back to the workplace after finishing up, I see Enoch."


translate English day9_ar_30843e69:


    nar "He's pretty far away, but there's no mistaking that black hair, the fancy clothes, or the height."


translate English day9_ar_b848536d:


    nar "The pairing is normally hard to imagine, but when I consider he might be here to see me, I'm happy."


translate English day9_ar_d2e2876f:


    nar "But I can't go up to him and talk to him."


translate English day9_ar_ed011501:


    nar "I don't realize it until I get closer, but he's talking with several other people."


translate English day9_ar_0fae69fa:


    nar "And all of them are familiar faces. Faces that I saw every day--faces that I would never get used to."


translate English day9_ar_a4291612:


    nar "That one--the one I saw yesterday."


translate English day9_ar_476035c3:


    nar "He notices me from afar, then says a quick good-bye, and the rest of the people scatter."


translate English day9_ar_21cdc8ad:


    pl "...Enoch?"


translate English day9_ar_80ec9e64:


    en "...Oh, hello, [na].{w} You on your way back?"


translate English day9_ar_e042c23f:


    pl "Yeah. What are you doing out here?"


translate English day9_ar_e87c95e8:


    en "It wasn't a special mission, really--just that now that I'm back at the temple, I decided to stop by and say hello."


translate English day9_ar_0953c22e:


    en "It may surprise you, but the Magic Department works alongside the Cleanup Department pretty often."


translate English day9_ar_541eb208:


    en "I've got a friend or two among the priests here."


translate English day9_ar_5e5b6d65:


    pl "Huh... Well, I guess the disposal team was originally part of the Magic Department..."


translate English day9_ar_eba4f781:


    en "It's not like one is superior and the other is inferior, though."


translate English day9_ar_4ba96313:


    pl "...Are you friends with those guys?"


translate English day9_ar_c88f95f0:


    en "Eh, sort of. They're sociable and kind of fun to be around."


translate English day9_ar_64781758:


    pl "...Were they talking about me?"


translate English day9_ar_34fc692a:


    en "What?"


translate English day9_ar_5c8ff805:


    pl "I asked if they were talking about me."


translate English day9_ar_c29b29fa:


    en "Uh... Well, I can't say we WEREN'T talking about you at all, but..."


translate English day9_ar_812ba55e:


    pl "So you were.{w} I knew you were. What did they say?"


translate English day9_ar_26a44747:


    pl "What the hell did those assholes say about me?!" with sshake


translate English day9_ar_22afc6ff:


    en "Umm, well... It wasn't about anything concrete, it's just...{w} Normal stuff..."


translate English day9_ar_cbe8b22e:


    en "They said, \"good luck.\""


translate English day9_ar_9208c2e1:


    nar "My vision blurs all at once. My body moves, entirely regardless of my intent."


translate English day9_ar_fcee8638:


    nar "With my back to Enoch, I leave my heavy bag on the ground and leave the workplace."


translate English day9_ar_9387abe2:


    en "[na]?"


translate English day9_ar_02e3c24c:


    nar "Leaving him behind, I enter the temple."


translate English day9_ar_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_ar_3a1321ea:


    "\n I probably should have taken a cold shower, but instead I headed straight to the department office."


translate English day9_ar_de8887aa:


    "Nobody is there. Only silence drifts on the air but there's a low shadow nonetheless. I take a couple steps from there and arrive at my locker."


translate English day9_ar_fe3a5f6b:


    "I'm pretty sure this must be different from what I always see."


translate English day9_ar_e36ee864:


    "It's not a vague sense of something being out of place--it's like my intuition is making me uneasy. Carefully, I reach for the handle. Something's definitely there."


translate English day9_ar_d8fe9f30:


    et "Slippery, but hard--I touch both something that feels like rubber and something sharp.{w} It's a thumbtack."


translate English day9_ar_817c6e50:



    nvl clear
    "\n They're all along the inside of the handle, held on by hardened glue."


translate English day9_ar_add10a3c:


    "Feeling like a criminal shoved down under a guillotine, I manage to use my nails to open the door."


translate English day9_ar_faf8e69c:


    "Inside, it's pretty empty, since I haven't brought the tools back yet.{w} I look up, then I look down...and spot something in the corner."


translate English day9_ar_19c5d8f5:


    et "Since it's all the way on the bottom of the locker, I have to squat down to see it."


translate English day9_ar_5a1a9e8b:



    nvl clear
    "\n I go into the dark locker and I'm immediately hit with a stench I'm pretty used to."


translate English day9_ar_a84a299d:


    "For a moment, I fall forwards--I was already leaning--and my forehead touches the mucky wall.{w} My knees, which I've been trying my best to keep off the floor, crumple."


translate English day9_ar_5b98a9c5:


    "I can still only see an outline in the darkness, but I felt eyes, a nose, a mouth, hair, shrunken organs--I can tell, even though I don't want to, that it's a dead mouse."


translate English day9_ar_7d72b69f:


    "I hadn't slipped by accident, either. Someone's behind me.{w} In fact, I sense two people."


translate English day9_ar_96e07320:


    "As I try to come out of the dark, cramped locker, they push me further in and go to shut the door."


translate English day9_ar_47be9326:


    "Naturally, there's no way the door will shut. It keeps opening, the old hinges creaking over and over until they loosen, brutally slamming into me."


translate English day9_ar_fcdf743d:


    "My whole face is covered in that animal's dirty flesh that had been left there for so long. I can't even breathe. My blackened vision begins to go red and yellow."


translate English day9_ar_39b6c633:


    et "I want to throw up."


translate English day9_ar_4ffb6c7a:



    nvl clear
    "\n After several times, a hand reaches deep into the locker, grabs my head, and drags me out."


translate English day9_ar_1074e725:


    "My vision is still blurred. As I gasp for fresh air, grayish water filled with scum pours down over my head."


translate English day9_ar_3d6c1dae:


    "And that's it.{w} For a few moments, I hear several people laughing, but then it goes quiet."


translate English day9_ar_2945535d:


    et "Covered in the terrible stench, the only thing I can do is crawl away."


translate English day9_ar_f2204417:



    nvl clear
    "\n Rage wells up inside of me.{w} Pointless abuse and revilement are the only things that escape my teeth, clenched so hard it hurts."


translate English day9_ar_b663249d:


    "They sound miserable, wretched. I should have killed them when I had the chance.{w} And yet now I'm the bad guy?"


translate English day9_ar_60c6761a:


    "If I was going to beat them to a pulp anyway, I shouldn't have hesitated to just kill them. Then they wouldn't be looking down on me like this."


translate English day9_ar_caa3c43e:


    "Yeah. That's what I should have done.{w} In fact, it's not too late."


translate English day9_ar_810fef36:


    "With a loud cry, I grope about as I crawl, grasping the shovel that must have fallen out of the locker with me. Though my legs are exhausted, I manage to get myself up."


translate English day9_ar_98881868:


    et "I run out into the hallway. I have to kill them right here, right now, or else I'll never--"


translate English day9_ar_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_ar_7012e37a:


    "\n \"Brother [na2].\""


translate English day9_ar_9f9ea387:


    "I hear Arnie's voice from deep in my memories."


translate English day9_ar_0a8a1154:


    "The never-before-seen color radiating in my vision suddenly dims, like a candle going out."


translate English day9_ar_b45e15a8:


    "Her voice as she called my name has always been soft, and had a resolve her kindness could never hide.{w} The resolve to carry this relationship hardens with each time she's nice to me."


translate English day9_ar_83d86d50:


    et "As the lights come back on, I see my feet as they're moving forward through sheer momentum.{w} In my memories, she opens her mouth to speak again."


translate English day9_ar_9cddefd9:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I have utmost faith in you.\""


translate English day9_ar_f829b095:


    "The shovel in my hands clatters to the floor with a heavy, metallic sound."


translate English day9_ar_d1e09be9:


    et "I look down at my empty hands. It's as though I can feel the warmth of her hands on them."


translate English day9_ar_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_ar_f814cfbd:


    "\n She always expressed her faith in me, her voice never changing, regardless of the situation."


translate English day9_ar_33bd3052:


    "She's said so many, many times. She has faith in me. And here I was, trying to kill someone?"


translate English day9_ar_0a9654f4:


    "I give an empty laugh for some reason. My body, held up by sheer force of will, rapidly becomes heavier and wearier until I eventually slump down."


translate English day9_ar_eccfc36e:


    et "I don't want to do anything.{w} Not anymore..."


translate English day9_ar_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_ar_8da891b3:


    "\n Everyone dreams of Paradise at least once in their life."


translate English day9_ar_e5795759:


    "I did too--under that fond, annoying ceiling I used to see countless paradises."


translate English day9_ar_70320801:


    "It wouldn't be someone the adults provided to me, a woman linked to me by blood. It would be a bride of my own choosing, a lively town, people celebrating our happiness, a workplace where I could use my talents, a family we created with the money I made..."


translate English day9_ar_2b0c4f9b:


    et "I haven't accomplished a single one of those, but I felt like when I was with her, I was happy.{w} Wherever she was--that was my Paradise."


translate English day9_ar_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_ar_2f9e7bb9:


    "\n ......"


translate English day9_ar_ed550419_1:


    et "......"


translate English day9_ar_a90c3800:


    ar "...Brother [na2].{w} You look unwell. Have you been involved in another accident of some sort?"


translate English day9_ar_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_ar_10181478:


    ar "I've prepared snacks to go with the tea this time.{w} I don't know if they'll be to your liking, but... If it pleases you, then take a seat."


translate English day9_ar_eb1e660c_2:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_ar_16affd7f:


    ar "...Brother [na2]?"


translate English day9_ar_d652fa11:


    pl "Arnie, let's get married."


translate English day9_ar_8f1fc252:


    ar "Married...?"


translate English day9_ar_ff6a8030:


    pl "I'm sorry for not having the courage until now but I can't just foist all the responsibility on you anymore."


translate English day9_ar_ade29fc4:


    pl "I want to marry you, Arnie.{w} Right this instant, even."


translate English day9_ar_f64466f1:


    ar "......"


translate English day9_ar_c5668775:


    nar "With every time I say the word \"marry,\" my voice gets a lot brighter, more cheerful."


translate English day9_ar_26b1a346:


    nar "It has no shadow or gloom--it arcs straight towards the future."


translate English day9_ar_be12b18d:


    nar "She gives me a confused look; it's all so sudden. But she quickly realizes what my intentions are and gives me her usual smile."


translate English day9_ar_05a5d517:


    pl "I'll get you a ring once I have a little more money. I should get my first month's paycheck in about three weeks. "


translate English day9_ar_fa83f2a3:


    pl "By that time, I'll have transferred to the Magic Department, too."


translate English day9_ar_3cb85632:


    pl "The wedding dress can be white and have one of those long things that drags on the floor. "


translate English day9_ar_1dfb0a74:


    pl "In my homeland, women don't get to wear special dresses during weddings, so I've always wanted to see one at least once... "


translate English day9_ar_4e170ec0:


    pl "Before now, I didn't care who, but now I want you to wear one. You'll look gorgeous. I just know it. "


translate English day9_ar_213a210c:


    pl "I bet everyone at the temple who came would be jealous... Ha ha ha. You want kids, right? I do too. "


translate English day9_ar_781e3a86:


    pl "I don't really know much about the Magic Department's culture, but I figure three is a good number. "


translate English day9_ar_6878ddcf:


    pl "If we can have kids, I bet they'd be strong like you. I'm okay with having a girl, but I'd be able to play with a boy all I wanted. "


translate English day9_ar_f54ac359:


    pl "Also, I want a house. Not to bring another family to, but a house for newlyweds where the two of us can live as a family. "


translate English day9_ar_92ef567a:


    pl "You're okay with that, aren't you?{w} Oh, oops. This whole time I've been talking about myself... What would you want to do if we got married, Arnie?"


translate English day9_ar_11a5a8b2:


    ar "...Brother, it brings me joy greater than I've ever felt before to hear those words."


translate English day9_ar_54093726:


    ar "I am already happy that you're thinking so seriously about our relationship, but to know you're even thinking about our future... It brings me such happiness that I don't know what to do with all of it."


translate English day9_ar_6b136f4f:


    ar "But despite having a married couple's level of affection for each other, we wouldn't be able to have an official marriage."


translate English day9_ar_a52096ab:


    pl "Why not?!" with sshake


translate English day9_ar_af6489e0:


    nar "SLAM. The teacups on the table shake."


translate English day9_ar_408241e1:


    nar "It's not just my hands shaking, but my lips too, probably because I rushed through a shower before coming here."


translate English day9_ar_78c9474b:


    nar "She doesn't get flustered. She just keeps looking at me with that questioning expression."


translate English day9_ar_f7ca6450:


    ar "I feel I must apologize. My inability to properly express myself seems to have caused a misunderstanding."


translate English day9_ar_2f1c335b:


    ar "Upon entering this temple, we all become priests serving God and give up the option to get married."


translate English day9_ar_a5053851:


    ar "That doesn't only apply to me--it applies to you as well, Brother."


translate English day9_ar_b02e6556:


    nar "Misunderstanding..."


translate English day9_ar_b3a1fab6:


    ar "In addition, I've had an important duty for a long time--to inherit the Magic Department's bishop's seat."


translate English day9_ar_9053b161:


    ar "Not only is that my uncle's wish, it's also my own goal--one I've dreamed of since I was young."


translate English day9_ar_52a9474d:


    ar "After receiving that honor from my uncle, I have dedicated my life to escaping my own helplessness."


translate English day9_ar_859bdc1c:


    ar "Because of this, I likely won't be able to leave this temple in the future."


translate English day9_ar_eb914e32:


    nar "G-Goal..."


translate English day9_ar_98b4ad61:


    ar "I know my opinion may not line up with yours, Brother. But I've never cared about the ceremony."


translate English day9_ar_69b5fad8:


    ar "Enoch and I aren't related by blood either, but we were still able to become like family to one another, right?"


translate English day9_ar_24453f6d:


    ar "I am prepared to devote the rest of my life to you, Brother [na2]."


translate English day9_ar_36a99edb:


    ar "This is why you needn't feel like you must give me anything in return."


translate English day9_ar_32666fcf:


    ar "If I can do no more than borrow your name, that alone will be enough for me."


translate English day9_ar_f5055df2:


    nar "Devote..."


translate English day9_ar_f488180d:


    ar "...And as I've said before, you've already given something incredibly precious to me, Brother [na2]."


translate English day9_ar_34ec16f7:


    ar "I want to be someone who can stand at your side, without shame, in a way I can be satisfied with personally."


translate English day9_ar_eb9fbcdc:


    pl "Then have sex with me. Right now."


translate English day9_ar_3571f09d:


    ar "What...?"


translate English day9_ar_0bbc1fb7:


    nar "I sweep the still-shaking cups off the table."


translate English day9_ar_ea74c6d8:


    nar "The red tea water--and the snacks I didn't even glance at--fall to our feet. Under the shadow I cast on her, she gives me an uneasy look."


translate English day9_ar_5b7ea39f:


    nar "She looks up at me carefully, as though more worried about me than her own safety."


translate English day9_ar_c96044f4:


    nar "Maybe I really did misunderstand this.{w} She's been prioritizing me in everything, after all."


translate English day9_ar_3b211e10:


    nar "Since she thinks she's here specifically for me--someone who came to the temple without any knowledge of it."


translate English day9_ar_27665f8d:


    ar "Brothe--"


translate English day9_ar_6df5be38:


    nar "I press against her body, then get on top of her.{w} The act makes my hands tremble--makes all of me tremble." with sshake


translate English day9_ar_8a93634a:


    nar "Her hair falls and spreads over the sofa's armrest."


translate English day9_ar_bc3df0d3:


    pl "Why didn't you explain it to me before?"


translate English day9_ar_e76a65ac:


    pl "It's been like this ever since I got here. \"Oh, everyone here knows this or that.\" Well, I don't."


translate English day9_ar_e65a98ef:


    pl "But you got to hear everything. Must be nice. I guess that's how you were raised."


translate English day9_ar_e9211f38:


    pl "But what about me?"


translate English day9_ar_c1109fcc:


    pl "I have no idea what your life has been like, the kind of things you've thought during your life--I don't know anything!"


translate English day9_ar_de2f1d9c:


    pl "Every time you want me to understand something, every time you explain something like it's obvious..."


translate English day9_ar_7f2bae9c:


    pl "I don't understand a damn bit of it!!! Not one damn bit of it!" with sshake


translate English day9_ar_fe12bb02:


    ar "I... I'm terribly sorry, I truly--"


translate English day9_ar_cc958bc3:


    pl "I'm tired of hearing you say that."


translate English day9_ar_1500d2ca:


    nar "My voice goes lower than I've ever heard it go."


translate English day9_ar_e1dfd9e4:


    nar "But my voice probably isn't why she stops speaking--it's because my hand has grabbed her skin."


translate English day9_ar_da5238ab:


    ar "There are people outside..."


translate English day9_ar_5ccfc423:


    pl "Spread your legs."


translate English day9_ar_f64466f1_1:


    ar "......"


translate English day9_ar_f2a1eaa4:


    pl "Spread them... Damn it, just spread them already...!!!"


translate English day9_ar_490dd8d0:


    nar "I press on the round stigmata on her leg, then move my hands to touch her stomach, then reach for the place protruding beneath."


translate English day9_ar_f08eb331:


    nar "The place which--if our life goes exactly how she's pictured it--will forever remain open."


translate English day9_ar_4d50c883:


    pl "I've worked so hard for your sake, Arnie. I try to do anything I possibly can. And I have."


translate English day9_ar_186dee15:


    pl "You're the only part of my life that matters now. Without you, I have nothing left...{w} You said you loved me, didn't you?"


translate English day9_ar_26dd2e42:


    pl "Then take responsibility. Make me your husband and the father of your children!"


translate English day9_ar_03b01ed1:


    pl "Give me back the life I've dedicated to you!!!" with sshake


translate English day9_ar_9a5ca315:


    nar "Her face--I thought it would steadily turn red, but for some reason it loses its color instead. Her eyes go elsewhere, searching."


translate English day9_ar_00e2b6b8:


    nar "I don't like that, so I press my palm down on her hair."


translate English day9_ar_cd56b20e:


    nar "I didn't actually intend to grab her hair, but it's so long that it ends up in my hand anyway."


translate English day9_ar_92df23b8:


    nar "As the clump of hair I grabbed falls from my hand, her body seems to have lost its strength."


translate English day9_ar_9fe54fe4:


    pl "...Don't worry too much about it. Your father was a priest, but he had you, right?"


translate English day9_ar_6b62e1ed:


    pl "Just because it's a woman in his shoes now, it shouldn't make a difference..."


translate English day9_ar_ece172c1:


    nar "Straddling her in her powerlessness, I put my hands on my leather belt."


translate English day9_ar_f64466f1_2:


    ar "......"


translate English day9_ar_fab17604:


    ar "Very well, then.{w} I may not be worthy, but please, continue."


translate English day9_ar_2bc27c71:


    nar "Her voice no longer shakes as I hear it from beneath my palm.{w} Not only that, but the shame and worry have disappeared too."


translate English day9_ar_8cdde254:


    nar "But her voice isn't filled with curiosity, given to a moment's passion, nor embarrassed at entrusting her body to me."


translate English day9_ar_9146705b:


    nar "Nor is it a threatening voice, one suppressing anger or sadness."


translate English day9_ar_6ecbcacc:


    nar "There's just...nothing there.{w} She sounds like she's given up on everything, like she's entirely become an offering to my insatiable lust."


translate English day9_ar_194c314a:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_ar_ab3512c4:


    pl "Ha ha ha..."


translate English day9_ar_326f421e:


    nar "What I feel then is terror."


translate English day9_ar_221c1c5f:


    nar "In the quiet room, now devoid even of clothing touching, the only thing I hear is my own breathing."


translate English day9_ar_79d28b39:


    nar "The breathing is shaky, excitement still evident in it, but it steadily calms down and grows quieter."


translate English day9_ar_d1de077b:


    nar "Without saying anything, I step away from the sofa. She stays quiet as well, not speaking."


translate English day9_ar_a311abfc:


    nar "Before I close the door and leave, she sits up, disheveled, and looks at me--but her expression is still hidden behind her hair."


translate English day9_ar_da0abe24:



    nvl clear
    "\n I've always thought it was strange. Nevertheless, I preferred not to pop open the lid and peer inside."


translate English day9_ar_983c69f9:


    "Because I knew that if I started to suspect that group of something--Arnie of something--then I'd lose all the happiness I'd gained."


translate English day9_ar_c83de879:


    "But I HAVE been suspecting them. I've just been denying it this whole time--even though it's so obvious.{w} Something everyone knows except for me."


translate English day9_ar_45d44070:


    "That was why those jerks made fun of me for being favored by the Magic Department, and why they'd told me to \"do my best.\""


translate English day9_ar_53de9443:


    et "I mean, look at the situation. Once again, I'm the only idiot around."


translate English day9_ar_52b0f923:



    nvl clear
    "\n Everything the bishop said was correct. And so I tried even harder to deny it.{w} Everything I did, in the end, was like reaching out for a well-honed blade."


translate English day9_ar_985701d4:


    "But I thought that each time corrupted blood fell from my sliced hand, it would carry my sins with it; that new blood would begin to circulate, purifying my defiled body."


translate English day9_ar_1b7d32d0:


    "I couldn't have been further from the truth."


translate English day9_ar_cd1421a4:


    et "I wanted to arrive there safely. But there's no place for me there."


translate English day9_ar_e7786228:



    nvl clear
    "\n That place where she is--it's just somewhere for her to live a radiant life. Not my Paradise.{w} It never mattered who came to her."


translate English day9_ar_69589c80:


    "Arnie's a miserable person who can't tell the difference between her own emotions and loyalty to her family."


translate English day9_ar_72824afe:


    "She denied it, but that's just because she doesn't even know it."


translate English day9_ar_49592554:


    "If it was for the sake of the mission she'd been given, she'd open her legs to anyone--the parents who gave birth to her, the brother she was raised with, or even someone she'd never met before."


translate English day9_ar_e91ef320:


    "Why did I ever think integrity was beautiful? Why did I ever think the closer to perfect she was, the safer I would be?"


translate English day9_ar_79ada728:


    "In the end, I couldn't even lay a finger on her."


translate English day9_ar_cc2fc906:


    et "But I still... I still, honestly, truly, genuinely love her."


translate English day9_ar_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_ar_76b2fe88_7:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_ar_20590218:


    "\n A plate sits on a dark table, and a woman with pure white skin rests on the plate."


translate English day9_ar_4b42c58e:


    "There's no illumination; in fact, it seems like the plate itself is emitting a light of its own."


translate English day9_ar_c6b30732:


    "Her black hair, adorned with golden decorations, is spread out beneath her, reminiscent of a heaping helping of sauce or a salad partition."


translate English day9_ar_eab9fdcb:


    et "Her hands rest neatly on her chest, giving a glimpse of her pink nipples through the gaps."


translate English day9_ar_278319fa:



    nvl clear
    "\n In the capital, where if something attached to your body was severable, people would sell it. The fact that her hair is this long is an indication of her social standing."


translate English day9_ar_43bd9b05:


    "Her fair skin still has color in it--it's not bluish white. It has a little bit of a red tint to it."


translate English day9_ar_0b87ca5c:


    "Her thighs decorate her silhouette with their moderate body fat, while her toenails are translucent, as though they're made of glass."


translate English day9_ar_ed1d00e7:


    "This is the body of a woman who has only eaten pure, high-quality food--who has a servant to take care of each and every one of her strands of hairs."


translate English day9_ar_9a97474d:


    et "She is doubtless the highest quality meat, fed and nurtured with mountains of money.{w} And now she's being offered to me--because I'm a guest they feel the need to cater to."


translate English day9_ar_70f6efa1:



    nvl clear
    "\n The flesh has been made to be so soft that even my clumsily inserted knife would cut through it with ease."


translate English day9_ar_14081817:


    "Almost like the meat is absorbing the blade. I put it in my mouth. It tastes very fresh, and very sweet."


translate English day9_ar_ebbfbf50:


    "I want to let the meat roll around on my tongue as long as I can to taste it more fully, but when the warm juices flow through my back teeth and down my throat, I have to quickly swallow."


translate English day9_ar_2e5cd4b3:


    "As it slides down my esophagus, it melts, becoming a part of me.{w} I didn't need any words of special praise."


translate English day9_ar_18856f98:


    et "Patting my warmed-up stomach, I reach for another piece. No adults are around. I don't need to look good in front of anyone."


translate English day9_ar_49edc4aa:



    nvl clear
    "\n I've never understood table manners in the slightest, so I toss my knife and fork aside."


translate English day9_ar_8a2e587f:


    "I peck the meat like an animal, like a bird with a soft, round beak, grabbing with nails I haven't maintained in days."


translate English day9_ar_b3aa0f38:


    "Wherever my tongue touches, I enjoy to its fullest. I rub the smell of the plump, raw meat against my gums and all over my mouth.{w} I almost suffocate from the euphoria."


translate English day9_ar_dd5e57cd:


    "The blood spurts out endlessly, wetting my mouth and dirtying my clothes. The warm, damp feeling that only fresh meat has makes my head spin."


translate English day9_ar_e2092599:


    "I want more. I want to dirty my face more. I want to fill my stomach with this disgusting sense of satiety."


translate English day9_ar_d6897ce5:


    "I use my teeth to rip away the long organs packed so tightly within. When I look up, I see her looking at me--a calm expression constantly on her face."


translate English day9_ar_415054bd:


    et "Those blue eyes that remind me of the skies back home--I can't see them now."


translate English day9_ar_a4c3e181:



    nvl clear
    "\n The blood covering the table drips down underneath my chair.{w} The sound is regular, like the ticking of a clock, or the beating of a heart."


translate English day9_ar_ed0a8d36:


    "Did I only ever want her out of sheer greed?"


translate English day9_ar_557d1f19:


    et "I lay my face on her stomach, torn open and crimson, feeling a wave of happiness mixed with sadness."


translate English day9_ar_76b2fe88_8:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_ar_1714ca9e:


    "\n I knew from the beginning that this was simply her corpse--not some rare type of meat."


translate English day9_ar_5dbafd29:


    "But I can't stop.{w} I don't even try."


translate English day9_ar_65a2a855:


    "It's warm inside her. The vivid scarlet fills my vision. The sweetness still lingers in my mouth. The warm, soft walls of flesh bring me calm."


translate English day9_ar_7d5b6511:


    et "Paradise was never somewhere around her--it was within her the whole time."


translate English day9_ar_f89270b9:



    nvl clear
    "\n I want to live here.{w} Ahh, I wish I could have been born a tiny insect."


translate English day9_ar_2814fdb3:


    "Every day would be sunny if only I could live inside your corpse.{w} I could feel the sun's warmth from here, too."


translate English day9_ar_f713e8a9:


    "If I could live here forever, then tomorrow, and the day after that, I would never need to look at the sky."


translate English day9_ar_8e1a728b:


    et "That must be what it means to become a part of someone's life."


