    nvl clear


translate English day10_ar_1d228a84:



    nvl clear
    "\n I blink several times. I must have been tossing and turning a lot, since one of my legs is now rolled up in my blanket."


translate English day10_ar_3680cb0b:


    "The fragmented memories of my dream--and the bliss that came from them--stimulate my hazy mind, then disappear."


translate English day10_ar_561d79fb:


    "The sky outside the window is shining white and it's quiet outside my door. That's when I instinctively know I've overslept."


translate English day10_ar_103febdf:


    "I made the decision never to be late again. Now that this accident has reminded me of that resolve I had, I get depressed."


translate English day10_ar_87d7fc7e:


    et "Feeling like it's pointless, I pull the blanket back over me and close my eyes, trying to go back to sleep. I don't want to wake up.{w} I'm not sure I even can."


translate English day10_ar_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_ar_cf3f9d77:


    "\n I don't want to be part of the disposal team anymore.{w} I'm sick of cleaning up dead bodies and wiping dirty floors."


translate English day10_ar_901192d1:


    "I'd rather die than have to face THEM again. And that goes for the others, too."


translate English day10_ar_fe4bd7de:


    "Those people who look at my suffering, ignore it, and laugh at me--those people who won't even congratulate me on my happiness--they're not my friends."


translate English day10_ar_89cf558e:


    "I'm trying to do my best here. I've held out an entire week without knowing anything beforehand, not to mention I still can't even speak the language well. Isn't that more than enough to deserve praise?"


translate English day10_ar_2257f0a2:


    et "But no matter how hard I try, they'll never really care. In fact, they told me as much.{w} \"There's nothing you can do. Why not think about your own fate instead?\""


translate English day10_ar_746bad0c:



    nvl clear
    "\n I should have realized what those words really meant before now. I can't even bear the burden of my own life and yet I'm trying to enter another's?"


translate English day10_ar_4fbf2880:


    "I never received a real education, I've never accomplished anything worth talking about, and I'm lazy by nature. I don't WANT to learn."


translate English day10_ar_52659bdc:


    "I didn't get any talents or special abilities that would make me better than others. I can only manage makeshift little tricks--and they'd only be enough to fool children."


translate English day10_ar_12a89e62:


    "I should have looked back on my own life earlier. Instead, I wasted the whole thing."


translate English day10_ar_4beaafee:


    "And I'm an adult now? How do other people grow up to become adults?"


translate English day10_ar_7ddbb6b3:


    et "I always thought the reason I was fed up with life was because of this suffocating environment, but I'm really just done with people in general."


translate English day10_ar_2c4d73c9:



    nvl clear
    "\n And so everything that happened between Arnie and me was like a dream."


translate English day10_ar_e9e59acf:


    "For some reason, she was nice to me at our first meeting. She was more perfect than anyone else. But in front of me, she always bowed her head and treated me the most kindly."


translate English day10_ar_107f857c:


    "And she even said she loved me. Why wouldn't I fall for someone like her?"


translate English day10_ar_e17d6460:


    "Man cannot go against providence--we just have to go along with what fate has in store for us."


translate English day10_ar_a054b436:


    et "There are plenty of other people who like her, but she belongs to me, and me alone."


translate English day10_ar_4f3a8bb7:



    nvl clear
    "\n Naturally, loving a girl like her didn't go smoothly. I'm not really suited for her, after all."


translate English day10_ar_90ae0d24:


    "But she... I was always misunderstanding things, not her. She never belonged to me to begin with. And I think I always realized that."


translate English day10_ar_7fef6c0e:


    "Yesterday, even though I realized I had sinned, I didn't offer the angel a prayer."


translate English day10_ar_f568b31d:


    et "I lost sight of why I should keep on believing in an angel who tries to break Arnie and me apart."


translate English day10_ar_8623d324:



    nvl clear
    "\n Why HAVE I trusted her until now? Because I decided it was only natural to?"


translate English day10_ar_c27e7be5:


    "I just want to be happy with Arnie."


translate English day10_ar_51f6a92f:


    "Arnie, Arnie, Arnie...{w} I love you. I love you. I love you so much, Arnie. I still love you.{w} Living at the temple is a difficult, torturous experience, but you answered my trust. You're the only one who did."


translate English day10_ar_99b41553:


    et "Arnie may be a priest who worships God, but in my world, she's a god herself..."


translate English day10_ar_13c67cfc:



    nvl clear
    "\n But she wasn't a god. That's why she betrayed me. What she loves is family--and I couldn't become that, even at the very end."


translate English day10_ar_3ffa098a:


    "I needed some proof that she and I were connected.{w} And now that a goddess like her has betrayed me, I have nothing left."


translate English day10_ar_f24585db:


    "Whatever the Magic Department needs from the eldest Alternata, however the magicians want to be praised by the world--none of it has anything to do with me."


translate English day10_ar_e20a0f99:


    "All I needed was that one person--Arne Alternata.{w} But is even that wrong?"


translate English day10_ar_79c6f6cb:


    et "I did it for her. Just for her.{w} I was... Her..."


translate English day10_ar_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_ar_47a899cd:


    "\n I open my eyes again, and it's midday. I must have fallen asleep."


translate English day10_ar_70d35a6c:


    et "It's still the same color as morning outside, but there's something I've managed to understand.{w} It's like I came to a conclusion within that dream I can't remember."


translate English day10_ar_68dfebbe:


    nar "It's cold outside. Usually, I'd take a shower or something, but today I don't want to go anywhere, so I just change my clothes instead."


translate English day10_ar_3c0d5d8b:


    nar "The temple seen from the outside looks a little different from yesterday. There's a disquieting fog today, like the blackest ashes being carried by the wind."



translate English day10_ar_f1332baf:


    nar "But there isn't any actual fog--that's just how I'm feeling.{w} That's how scary \"outside\" feels to me right now."


translate English day10_ar_098155a3:


    nar "It's like my emotions have created a field--just like I heard before."


translate English day10_ar_c676eb9a:


    nar "I hurry to the training grounds, which are noisy as usual.{w} This place isn't safe either."


translate English day10_ar_d93f825f:


    nar "Several people look my way as I search for Arnie."


translate English day10_ar_f8351d86:


    nar "Today, almost at the same time as I open the door, she approaches me."


translate English day10_ar_95f643ee:


    nar "Her face is uncharacteristically disturbed--she looks like she's about to cry. It's like a scene out of a movie."


translate English day10_ar_bc701c99:


    ar "Brother, yesterday, I... I'm so, so sorry."


translate English day10_ar_f4578279:


    pl "...Huh? For what...?"


translate English day10_ar_ee7b5377:


    ar "It was my carelessness that brought on that misunderstanding, and I've hurt you deeply because of it."


translate English day10_ar_788c89f7:


    ar "No matter what I say, I will never, ever make excuses.{w} I would understand if you've lost all hope in me because of this."


translate English day10_ar_b2a3ce1c:


    ar "So allow me to apologize from the bottom of my heart."


translate English day10_ar_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day10_ar_1251bebd:


    nar "What am I supposed to say now? I can't think of anything at all."


translate English day10_ar_aad8aa15:


    nar "She's right. I can get as angry as I want with her."


translate English day10_ar_139e04d9:


    nar "Or I can forgive her, comfort her like I always do, and pretend like it never happened."


translate English day10_ar_221853dd:


    nar "But I don't want to do either of those things."


translate English day10_ar_d316d1da:


    pl "...If you're really sorry, then...{w} Will you spend the day with me?"


translate English day10_ar_e9812050:


    ar "A-ah..."


translate English day10_ar_23d81f94:


    pl "Before, we'd just talk if we got a little free time. But we haven't really been able to spend time with each other lately."


translate English day10_ar_f4e0a03b:


    pl "Even if we did run into each other, you'd go straight to work. We'd say hello, then leave."


translate English day10_ar_6f59a5c3:


    pl "And you've never really come to see me, so... Spend the rest of the day with me. Please."


translate English day10_ar_a1ec8cdb:


    pl "I want to be with you."


translate English day10_ar_ab475648:


    nar "With each word I speak, my head grows heavier."


translate English day10_ar_13580560:


    nar "I said the last part of it in a quiet, almost inaudible voice, so I don't know if she heard it or not. But she stands there, unmoving."


translate English day10_ar_951d617e:


    nar "Growing anxious, I look up again. She just blinking at me.{w} I get the feeling I know exactly how she feels."


translate English day10_ar_f920438c:


    ar "...Yes. Let's do that."


translate English day10_ar_7138afb3:


    nar "\"However,\" she says at the end."


translate English day10_ar_966d4aba:


    ar "...Are you sure that's all you need?"


translate English day10_ar_7f3cba45:


    nar "Her response was so flat, so indifferent, that I don't feel happiness or gratitude--mostly just emptiness."


translate English day10_ar_e3c3787a:


    nar "I feel like all the emotions are gone. But I do realize one thing."


translate English day10_ar_9dc85f7d:


    nar "When it comes to my feelings, my state of mind--she doesn't understand any of it."


translate English day10_ar_2f546c19:


    nar "She agreed to a proposal I offered, and that's all--she didn't say yes because she's empathizing with me."


translate English day10_ar_14af5f1e:


    ar "I shall get ready, then.{w} I will return immediately, so please wait for a moment in the back."


translate English day10_ar_eaaaf92a:


    nar "Because I don't expect anything, I'm not uneasy."


translate English day10_ar_a1441da0:


    nar "But before she closes the door, in that moment I see her talking to him, I get grumpy.{w} I still don't trust her."


translate English day10_ar_ee0cbe74:


    nar "Trust isn't a one-way road, and the trust she shows me isn't trust in the true sense of the word, either."


translate English day10_ar_d776f325:


    nar "She interprets everything so that it makes sense for her, disregarding the other person's feelings.{w} Is that really what trust is?"


translate English day10_ar_32dda69e:


    nar "As I stand there and watch her as she goes, and as she steps inside, I realize that I resent what I'm doing at this very moment."


translate English day10_ar_6e99e5b4:


    nar "Nobody has ever been present when I think about the future."


translate English day10_ar_776efa09:


    nar "I've always kind of figured someone would be next to me, but I've never once imagined a specific person to be there."


translate English day10_ar_b5e085f3:


    nar "And I don't want to."


translate English day10_ar_571070ea:


    nar "To my young eyes, being with someone like that is akin to suppressing oneself, locking oneself away."


translate English day10_ar_c72a5780:


    nar "In the world inside my head, I am free.{w} Countless possibilities extend in every direction."


translate English day10_ar_04ef5e67:


    nar "Having a connection to another person is just one of those possibilities, and for me and my life, it's not even a big one."


translate English day10_ar_361d8b97:


    nar "Everyone learns how to live for another, and lives for that purpose--but I became an adult without understanding any of it."


translate English day10_ar_ef03b11e:


    nar "That's why I don't know what my own heart is doing most of the time."


translate English day10_ar_1cbc657e:


    nar "She's only respecting my freedom and being considerate of it, which makes me want to claim she's to blame for everything. But that isn't right."


translate English day10_ar_cf5b790f:


    nar "I want to be suppressed--and I want it to be by her. I--someone useless--wanted to deny it so much, even if that really happened."


translate English day10_ar_b637bcc1:


    ar "Thank you for waiting, Brother [na2]."


translate English day10_ar_ff4188a2:


    pl "Hey..."


translate English day10_ar_b54f7622:


    nar "She bows her head. From behind her, a tall man fidgets, then enters the room."


translate English day10_ar_3311287a:


    nar "I don't feel betrayed. I wasn't expecting anything to begin with."


translate English day10_ar_075aaeab:


    pl "Oh, hey, you're here too. Great. Take a seat already, would you?"


translate English day10_ar_a55bedc4:


    en "Um, I... I should probably leave..."


translate English day10_ar_f4c7e5a3:


    pl "What are you talking about? Ha ha ha. For this lady's little brother, you sure are weirdly reserved."


translate English day10_ar_7630bdc0:


    pl "More fun with all three of us than just two of us, right?"


translate English day10_ar_128091bf:


    en "Oh, um, sure... Ha...ha ha..."


translate English day10_ar_9cb9fbd8:


    nar "If you knew you'd be in the way, then stay away to begin with, doofus. Seeing him be so hesitant and indecisive sours my mood."


translate English day10_ar_c3f015c4:


    nar "And the same goes for the sister. Did she not realize I wanted to be alone with her?"


translate English day10_ar_d0974517:


    nar "Am I your lover or your little brother? Make it make sense already!"


translate English day10_ar_1c6c611d:


    pl "Did you two eat yet?"


translate English day10_ar_3e306f8e:


    pl "It's lunchtime, right? If you haven't eaten, then you can go ahead. Don't mind me."


translate English day10_ar_840e18de:


    en "I had a little, but Sis here..."


translate English day10_ar_a1e0e8ee:


    ar "I had enough. But Enoch, you..."


translate English day10_ar_27b51fe4:


    pl "Which is it?"


translate English day10_ar_66da3784:


    en "Like I said before, oatmeal isn't enough for a meal."


translate English day10_ar_9462c194:


    ar "It isn't oatmeal. It's porridge.{w} There is no better way to get protein."


translate English day10_ar_0b9c3690:


    ar "And do you intend to claim that a salad consisting entirely of chicken breast and cabbage is sufficient nutrition?"


translate English day10_ar_800d6979:


    en "It wasn't a salad, it was a sandwich.{w} And chicken breast has plenty of protein in it too!"


translate English day10_ar_35ade460:


    en "You agree with me, right, [na]?!"


translate English day10_ar_37b44184:


    ar "Mgh..."


translate English day10_ar_8073e4a6:


    pl "From my point of view, they're both the same.{w} Hey, how come you don't eat in the cafeteria?"


translate English day10_ar_a667778a:


    pl "I feel like the cafeteria is always people from the Cleanup Department or Health Department."


translate English day10_ar_e720e45c:


    en "Well... In our case, it's just because we choose easy meals for convenience. Work keeps us pretty busy, after all."


translate English day10_ar_c8287464:


    en "The other priests generally eat earlier so that they don't run into the other departments too."


translate English day10_ar_a5c0c11d:


    pl "Wait, really? Why's that? Don't tell me the Magic Department gets their own special meals..."


translate English day10_ar_7c0a113c:


    en "No, no, of course not. There's only so many ingredients to go around anyway. It's because of when training sessions are."


translate English day10_ar_8c8b3b0e:


    en "Basically, they do it because it's rational and it keeps everyone on good terms."


translate English day10_ar_9fabae89:


    pl "Oh, because...if a Magic Department priest was sitting next to you during your valuable eating time, you'd choke on your food?"


translate English day10_ar_74e0510c:


    en "Hey! You don't have to say it like that--"


translate English day10_ar_b7251c1f:


    ar "Yes, that is correct."


translate English day10_ar_f9d1d9f8:


    en "Sis..."


translate English day10_ar_e8058bb8:


    ar "Because priests in the Magic Department lend such importance to our shared culture, we have forgotten how to be friends with priests in other departments."


translate English day10_ar_3271c2c5:


    ar "It's only natural those we can't trust think of us with discomfort."


translate English day10_ar_b58bebd1:


    pl "You know about the problems this department has, huh?"


translate English day10_ar_ffba88b3:


    ar "I would not be able to lead without having a good grasp of them. But our strong points are the same--the two exist simultaneously."


translate English day10_ar_c2dbcc34:


    pl "I guess that's why they say that everyone has strengths and weaknesses, huh?"


translate English day10_ar_6031b6fe:


    ar "Yes. It's obviously important to know your strengths, but it is only by knowing your weaknesses that you can know a person's character."


translate English day10_ar_d7f4b534:


    ar "Strengths in particular tend to be a convenient poison, and overdoing it will worsen your character. But sometimes, those strengths support you."


translate English day10_ar_adbb4056:


    ar "What I'm saying is this.{w} One must never presume to judge one person over another."


translate English day10_ar_11b47bc7:


    pl "I like the sound of that. What are Enoch's weaknesses?"


translate English day10_ar_09f8148e:


    en "Huh? What?"


translate English day10_ar_3e5ce7cc:


    ar "One of them is how he struggles to assert himself."


translate English day10_ar_52a20e30:


    ar "Ever since we were young, he was always in the position of taking orders. So he still can't make his own perspectives clear, and instead lets his complaints and dissatisfaction pile up."


translate English day10_ar_eb87923e:


    ar "Another weakness is how he always tends to say one thing too many."


translate English day10_ar_9127a1cc:


    en "H-Hey, look...!"


translate English day10_ar_8d0bbff5:


    ar "Because of that, his friendships are wide-reaching, he speaks little, and he has a strong sense of responsibility. I can trust him with the work that needs to be done."


translate English day10_ar_fe390161:


    ar "In that way, a weakness can sometimes have two sides to it."


translate English day10_ar_6fc27004:


    en "A-Aww, Sis...!"


translate English day10_ar_308a9214:


    ar "Enoch, you must always be clear with your opinions."


translate English day10_ar_cb0d2f82:


    ar "You must not be so quick to run from your own goals, and you must not feel guilt or shame in saying no."


translate English day10_ar_fb2344e6:


    ar "Your perspective is broader than mine. In fact, that may mean your goal disappears from sight."


translate English day10_ar_8bb18164:


    ar "But rather than think you've lost your way, you must open your mind to other possibilities."


translate English day10_ar_141be01c:


    ar "You are capable of obtaining anything you desire. Your are capable of doing anything you put your mind to."


translate English day10_ar_bdba1030:


    en "Right. I always consider it an honor to be able to be an aide to you, Sis."


translate English day10_ar_848b2055:


    en "And I'd like to continue in that honored position."


translate English day10_ar_6dcf6c9d:


    ar "Very well."


translate English day10_ar_cd23185e:


    nar "Another stupid tangent. Don't they know when to rein it back in?"


translate English day10_ar_5fb700b4:


    nar "Read the room and shut up, will you?{w} There's a guest right in front of you. Don't sit so close to Arnie either."


translate English day10_ar_b3e7a0b0:


    pl "Now that you mention it, you do seem pretty well-known for a magic department priest, Enoch."


translate English day10_ar_0fae0d5e:


    en "What do you mean, \"for a magic department priest\"...?"


translate English day10_ar_6545b0f1:


    pl "Well, you know...{w} You're on good terms with the Academics Department, at least, right? I think."


translate English day10_ar_241f876b:


    en "Oh, you mean Lavi!"


translate English day10_ar_e45bdda7:


    en "I didn't end up friends with her because I wanted to \"broaden my friendships\" or whatever, but after talking to her once or twice, we started getting along."


translate English day10_ar_d9e536d8:


    en "Haha. Makes me think I could make a hundred friends if I traveled all around the temple!"


translate English day10_ar_2f974f67:


    ar "I see... That would be good exercise, too."


translate English day10_ar_edc223e1:


    en "Uh, Sis... You gotta stop taking things so literally..."


translate English day10_ar_612375ae:


    pl "Well, you were pretty persistent about talking to me too, Enoch, and now, here we are!"


translate English day10_ar_45097072:


    en "Urk... Aren't you more popular than me, [na]?"


translate English day10_ar_85f048e7:


    pl "I mean, all I do is walk around a lot. Going around the temple over and over again, you know."


translate English day10_ar_3222d52b:


    pl "I've basically memorized the layout, even though I usually only come here these days."


translate English day10_ar_94311ff1:


    ar "I consider that an honor, but would ask that you not forget to build relationships with your other friends as well."


translate English day10_ar_cfe850f8:


    pl "Nah! You're the only one for me. Haha."


translate English day10_ar_e0a017dd:


    ar "Hee hee..."


translate English day10_ar_b8625ebc:


    nar "I wasn't joking, though."


translate English day10_ar_141e405c:


    pl "So why don't I ever see the Academics Department in the cafeteria?"


translate English day10_ar_2afd098c:


    en "Hmm... I feel like it might just be that they skip meals."


translate English day10_ar_55fd56b6:


    en "Lavi always forgets to take the time to eat too.{w} I can't believe she survives on just a piece of candy and a scrap of chocolate some days..."


translate English day10_ar_32eac9fb:


    en "It's living proof that their bodies just work differently from ours."


translate English day10_ar_49e297b6:


    pl "I can survive on just a scrap of bread and an apple."


translate English day10_ar_7e85da58:


    ar "I've been wondering this since you came here, but... Did you skip meals today, Brother?"


translate English day10_ar_8d830fbc:


    pl "I was in a hurry since I was wondering what I'd do without you. I can just eat later--it's fine!"


translate English day10_ar_5971f7da:


    en "Come on, and YOU were griping at us for it...?{w} We should all be getting the proper nutrition!"


translate English day10_ar_552fb926:


    nar "Eventually, the bell rings to signify the end of lunch break.{w} The two of them, the conversation stopped, look idly into the air."


translate English day10_ar_10fff387:


    nar "In the end, I wasted time on pointless conversation. Precious time."


translate English day10_ar_de95f1fc:


    nar "I know exactly what will happen after this. He'll waste it yet again."


translate English day10_ar_2508be08:


    pl "...What will you two do?"


translate English day10_ar_1572893d:


    en "Oh, you mean what we were talking about before... Hmm..."


translate English day10_ar_bcb17db9:


    en "This is just my opinion, but I think I should take on Sis's work and keep it a secret from the bishop--"


translate English day10_ar_c1ac840e:


    ar "No, that will not do."


translate English day10_ar_884a0f88:


    ar "Priests of the Magic Department must keep their wills as one. There is no room for lies or deceit."


translate English day10_ar_22381022:


    en "Yeah, I mean, I know that, but..."


translate English day10_ar_a97e5b74:


    pl "Then what ARE you gonna do?"


translate English day10_ar_93f17c81:


    ar "There is only one method. I shall ask my uncle's permission directly to make time this afternoon."


translate English day10_ar_34ea8f29:


    pl "Hey, your brother's offering, isn't he? Maybe lose the weird stubbornness for the day and take him up on it."


translate English day10_ar_633caf3a:


    ar "That will not do. All must be done with my uncle's permission."


translate English day10_ar_17032140:


    pl "Then if he told you to die, would you?"


translate English day10_ar_df2c62be:


    ar "Are you feeling anxiety about this, Brother?"


translate English day10_ar_018a49d6:


    pl "Yeah, of course I am!"


translate English day10_ar_36de46cb:


    pl "You think you--YOU, of all people--can just walk up to that bad-mannered bishop and tell him you want to play hooky today without any warning and have him say \"oh, okay, sure\" or something?"


translate English day10_ar_f9d499cf:


    pl "If you honestly think that's going to work, then you're just being arrogant!"


translate English day10_ar_dcec2281:


    en "Why don't we just calm down, [na]--"


translate English day10_ar_4f17e1b6:


    pl "Calm down? Calm down? How?! You follow her around every single day like a little puppy! How could you ever know how I feel?!"


translate English day10_ar_4e684b3e:


    pl "Did I ask for something outrageous? All I did... All I ever did was be honest, and...{w} I just wanted us to support each other."


translate English day10_ar_40765653:


    pl "But I can't put my faith in you anymore."


translate English day10_ar_ea38cf03:


    pl "You may be the most reliable person here when it comes to working, but all you've ever done to me is make me anxious."


translate English day10_ar_c6882fbd:


    pl "I'm begging you, just... Think about my position even HALF as much as you think about your family!!!" with sshake


translate English day10_ar_9d35ab80:


    nar "The more words spring from the depths of my heart, the blanker my mind becomes."


translate English day10_ar_e3b08b61:


    nar "Nobody attempts to carry on the conversation at this point. While I thought Enoch would be angry at the insults, he looks at me with a little bit of...depression, for some reason."


translate English day10_ar_d8eb9c27:


    nar "It's like he's looking at an abandoned animal--clearly pitying my position."


translate English day10_ar_d1b91701:


    nar "I want to spit in his face."


translate English day10_ar_1c1ee359:


    nar "Meanwhile, she's sitting there with the same, calm expression as usual. What even am I to her?"


translate English day10_ar_173d89a2:


    ar "...Then I suppose you hate me now, Brother."


translate English day10_ar_fec7743c:


    nar "The two of us both look at her.{w} She speaks plainly, choosing her cruel words carefully."


translate English day10_ar_69d677fa:


    ar "I had intended to keep you ever in my mind, but I never noticed anything like that, even once..."


translate English day10_ar_11509a71:


    ar "It is only natural that you hate me. My ineptitude demands it."


translate English day10_ar_d934b5a0:


    pl "And it's because you realized it so late that we turned into this."


translate English day10_ar_7ffa96a2:


    ar "...I am well aware that nothing I say will matter. I must prove myself with my actions."


translate English day10_ar_1926cc8b:


    ar "My faith, Brother, will never waver."


translate English day10_ar_21ca6fdd:


    ar "And my feelings are ones I must prove to you on my own. For what point would there be to borrow the help of another?"


translate English day10_ar_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day10_ar_266e1eda:


    ar "I will not pester you to give me another chance. I also don't believe I'll ever regain your hope in me--your expectations of me."


translate English day10_ar_aef1720a:


    ar "If you have no more place in your heart for me, then I am fine with that."


translate English day10_ar_4332a699:


    ar "But in the name of Arne Alternata, I will uphold my oath."


translate English day10_ar_8472dc3e:


    nar "I don't say anything. I can only watch, head down, as they leave the room."


translate English day10_ar_d674953f:


    nar "A heavy emptiness settles over me. An emptiness so dark it blinds the eyes."


translate English day10_ar_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_ar_ccf4398d:


    "\n Until she said the word \"hate,\" I hadn't figured out what I've been feeling. I love her."


translate English day10_ar_41fa38f0:


    "She keeps talking about sincerity--and I know I've got some of that too."


translate English day10_ar_5c7cb1fd:


    "But that man doesn't seem to agree. Damn him and those pitying eyes of his, seeing straight through me..."


translate English day10_ar_617e7f6e:


    et "I don't know how amazing he considers his own love to be, but seeing him look at me with all that pity--I'm so frustrated I want to cry."


translate English day10_ar_4e80dae6:



    nvl clear
    "\n Don't pity me. I love her. I really do."


translate English day10_ar_c2cd6a6c:


    "So much that when she passes away, I'd like to ask for her beautiful white bones so I can place my tongue into her empty eye sockets and lap up the flesh still remaining.{w} I imagine it would be a fruit with a flavor unlike any I've ever tasted."


translate English day10_ar_e142752e:


    "Thinking about it reminds me of what happiness still is."


translate English day10_ar_4569e255:


    et "It means the hatred and resentment I feel are proof that I haven't fully been able to cut myself off from her."


translate English day10_ar_cc37a2ff:



    nvl clear
    "\n I'm so angry I want to rip him to shreds.{w} And even in this situation, I want to break her neck for continuing to choose her own justice instead of me."


translate English day10_ar_9e7221f3:


    "I envy those who can truly put their faith in her."


translate English day10_ar_0033becb:


    "Her convenient, dream-like platitudes will end as just that--dreams. And now I understand that."


translate English day10_ar_0b4e729f:


    et "And me--I managed to fall in love with someone, so I wanted to love them straightforwardly and sincerely.{w} Like a normal person. Like him..."


translate English day10_ar_9b362225:


    ar "Uncle, please excuse my sudden visit."


translate English day10_ar_37692ee2:


    er "Excuse it? You're always welcome here, anytime.{w} Though... For you to come at this particular time means it can't just be my niece coming to say hello."


translate English day10_ar_e482c266:


    er "Something happened, yes? An accident?"


translate English day10_ar_61a4ccaa:


    ar "No. Today I am here as your only niece, not as an auxiliary bishop of the Magic Department, with a request."


translate English day10_ar_fb99487d:


    er "Oh? Interesting.{w} Especially when it is noon--and work has already started."


translate English day10_ar_08cb951f:


    er "What is this wish that you--the one who should be overseeing the work at this hour--have come here to stop my own work?"


translate English day10_ar_f25314a3:


    er "Let's hear it."


translate English day10_ar_8e741358:


    ar "...I don't ask for anything complicated. I'd like to be released from my duties for the remainder of the day."


translate English day10_ar_6c7c4fc2:


    ar "Would you be gracious enough to give me one day--no, half of it?"


translate English day10_ar_52532f55:


    er "You want to be excused from your afternoon duties?{w} Sounds simple enough. Is there any particular reason for it?"


translate English day10_ar_53feb478:


    ar "There is not. This is purely my own decision."


translate English day10_ar_c17d7e32:


    er "Arne, I was entrusted with you when you were very young, and I've spent more time with you now than your father did."


translate English day10_ar_9fbd9389:


    er "And in those long years, this is the first time I've ever heard you ask for something for yourself. It's rather charming, really."


translate English day10_ar_8ead10e3:


    er "I suppose you were quite an unmanageable girl when you were young, but we'll leave that aside."


translate English day10_ar_ee0954d6:


    ar "I'm so terribly sorry for this display of incompetence, Uncle."


translate English day10_ar_f9754155:


    er "No... You've grown into a fine woman."


translate English day10_ar_0f3bb0aa:


    er "They do say that children are a parent's treasure. Thanks to you, I've been able to feel like a true parent--a feeling I never would have had otherwise."


translate English day10_ar_eb57ca0a:


    er "But that isn't only because of your impeccability, your talents, or your uprightness."


translate English day10_ar_ce34b94e:


    er "Even without any of that, I'm proud to call you my child..."


translate English day10_ar_4d6430a0:


    er "So if you have anything to ask for yourself, it only makes sense that I would grant it, no matter what it is."


translate English day10_ar_3c1870f6:


    ar "Uncle, then you mean..."


translate English day10_ar_3dd169e3:


    er "It is such a shame that all must end today."


translate English day10_ar_3571f09d:


    ar "What...?"


translate English day10_ar_ca56ff97:


    er "I doubt this is purely your own decision. I treasure you too much to think otherwise--you're doing this for someone else."


translate English day10_ar_9cbf9985:


    ar "No, I truly wish for a personal break..."


translate English day10_ar_eeabdce4:


    er "Well, I suppose that is praiseworthy in itself.{w} Taking responsibility for another's incompetence upon yourself..."


translate English day10_ar_ded50cd5:


    er "Yes, you are certainly my dear Arne. You are worthy of being called the Magic Department's next bishop."


translate English day10_ar_fc185ea8:


    er "I've made this decision because a lie, a falsehood, has come from your mouth."


translate English day10_ar_097f3f41:


    ar "...!"


translate English day10_ar_45f1ca25:


    er "I trust you. That's why I am able to come to such a conclusion..."


translate English day10_ar_ce00fc84:


    er "However, attempting to hide the truth means that you apparently don't trust me.{w} I would ask why."


translate English day10_ar_87260c70:


    er "Who is the one borrowing your lips to utter falsehoods? The young priests here?{w} Or perhaps...my son-in-law?"


translate English day10_ar_7b405d51:


    ar "No...!{w} In my incompetence, in my lack of dedication, I've truly come here of my own volition. It has nothing to do with others..."


translate English day10_ar_af280038:


    er "See? To hide a lie, you tell another. Soon they will number one hundred, then one thousand."


translate English day10_ar_c82e4928:


    er "You have at last learned how to lie. From now on, your words will invite disaster again..."


translate English day10_ar_78192175:


    ar "Disaster..."


translate English day10_ar_6bab310f:


    er "Now that it's come to this, I will teach you something."


translate English day10_ar_a45440cb:


    er "Man does not lie to hide his sins--his soul becomes sinful for having lied."


translate English day10_ar_5217b62e:


    ar "But, but I...{w} If I agree with you, then even what I said to that someone will turn into a lie..."


translate English day10_ar_58daefbf:


    er "What is at its root a pure heart may change depending on the situation."


translate English day10_ar_a3bb1626:


    er "You simply lack an awareness of what you lack--and you have made a promise you cannot keep."


translate English day10_ar_9f0c2313:


    er "You must take responsibility for that.{w} You cannot ask for my help in this."


translate English day10_ar_f64466f1:


    ar "......"


translate English day10_ar_102faf19:


    ar "...Yes, Uncle. Please forgive my foolishness."


translate English day10_ar_abf9551a:


    ar "I discarded humility, overestimated my abilities, and offended you. I will gladly accept any punishment for these sins you might levy."


translate English day10_ar_768493e9:


    ar "Please, grant this incompetent woman your teachings."


translate English day10_ar_cee6696a:


    er "Now, now. I'm happy just getting to see your face...{w} Return to your position and do what needs be done."


translate English day10_ar_8b146ade:


    ar "...Yes, Uncle."


translate English day10_ar_669bb0bf:


    nar "......"


translate English day10_ar_add93493:


    nar "I hear footsteps in the distance."


translate English day10_ar_d0f0976f:


    nar "They're going at a walking pace, but at uneven intervals, as though the person is hurrying. After a few moments, the door opens without so much as a knock."


translate English day10_ar_210eba45:


    nar "The faceless silhouette of a Magic Department priest I'd been imagining while staring at the door overlaps with her for a moment."


translate English day10_ar_900e0123:


    ar "Brother... You waited for me."


translate English day10_ar_b2c20e0f:


    nar "Her resolute gaze is blurred by joy and relief."


translate English day10_ar_f3824ffa:


    nar "The darkened room seems to regain its former light as she enters and catches her breath. She's almost making ME run out of breath just looking at her."


translate English day10_ar_9bc3a1b6:


    nar "After her quiet, deep breaths comes what sounds like a sigh."


translate English day10_ar_3613b8de:


    ar "...May I sit next to you?"


translate English day10_ar_c04d5b2d:


    pl "Go right ahead."


translate English day10_ar_83b26b46:


    ar "Thank you..."


translate English day10_ar_eb1e660c_2:


    pl "......"


translate English day10_ar_50b13b71:


    ar "...First, I must apologize."


translate English day10_ar_76337604:


    pl "It's fine."


translate English day10_ar_64c7268f:


    nar "My answer comes out before she even tells me."


translate English day10_ar_e4be4eee:


    ar "As you know, I am a boring woman, without a single proper hobby..."


translate English day10_ar_807c6aa6:


    ar "Now that I've suddenly received a day's worth of time, I'm not entirely sure what will satisfy you, Brother..."


translate English day10_ar_a46478f0:


    pl "...Huh?{w} Wait, wait, don't mind that stuff. You got the day off? Seriously?"


translate English day10_ar_70955604:


    pl "Arnie, did the bishop seriously say you could skip work?"


translate English day10_ar_d00d9e9d:


    ar "Yes. More precisely, just this afternoon's work, not the entire day."


translate English day10_ar_166f70a6:


    pl "B-But how?{w} The Magic Department is all about group activities, right? Aren't you basically propping the rest of them up?"


translate English day10_ar_ac4b4b54:


    pl "And work has already started by now, too."


translate English day10_ar_b498bb23:


    ar "Those duties are, of course, ones I can't be away from even temporarily.{w} To others, this must look like simple selfishness."


translate English day10_ar_e4285bf6:


    ar "But you did tell me to prioritize myself once in a while, didn't you?{w} And I already promised that I would spend the day with you."


translate English day10_ar_1b54a588:


    ar "For me, right now, fulfilling that promise is only my highest priority."


translate English day10_ar_cf39e60c:


    pl "I don't get it... How in the world did you...?"


translate English day10_ar_6911064f:


    ar "I told him that this was atonement.{w} He understood."


translate English day10_ar_83973a65:


    pl "...Did you mention me in any of this?"


translate English day10_ar_e3ab7d37:


    ar "I'm certain he knew."


translate English day10_ar_8e71eef9:


    pl "...Hah. Then he'll probably want me to handle something later."


translate English day10_ar_7e5da882:


    pl "He's basically saying \"do it, if you think you can.\" Today's the last day...{w} Right?"


translate English day10_ar_d9aacc92:


    ar "As a priest of the Magic Department, I must take responsibility for the sins I've committed. I must not lose the trust of others."


translate English day10_ar_8613d507:


    ar "My uncle has protected the department's auxiliary bishop, not Arne Alternata."


translate English day10_ar_a6df42c7:


    ar "All so that, through this atonement, I may continue to live proudly."


translate English day10_ar_eb1e660c_3:


    pl "......"


translate English day10_ar_d2fb0153:


    ar "However... If it's the case that you won't forgive me, then my uncle will likely scold me quite harshly."


translate English day10_ar_93275124:


    pl "What? You got a chance, so now you're passing the buck?"


translate English day10_ar_b7251c1f_1:


    ar "Yes, that is correct."


translate English day10_ar_2dd2ec6f:


    ar "I belong to you, do I not? Allow me to at least take responsibility as such."


translate English day10_ar_989670f3:


    pl "......"


translate English day10_ar_d40397e1:


    pl "...I'm sorry about all this, Arnie.{w} I forgive you. All of it."


translate English day10_ar_b3b5d0b6:


    ar "It's been a while since you've called me that..."


translate English day10_ar_5870491f:


    nar "I take her hand, but unsatisfied with just that, I embrace her."


translate English day10_ar_83dcae47:


    nar "Her shoulders and back tremble in my arms as her breath passes my ears."


translate English day10_ar_beaed6e9:


    ar "Oh... I'm sorry."


translate English day10_ar_e437ccc1:


    pl "Something happened, didn't it?"


translate English day10_ar_a61419bf:


    ar "No, do not worry. I am just relieved."


translate English day10_ar_98892770:


    ar "I know it was the right thing to do, but this is the first time I've asked my uncle for something for myself--something that strays from our proper path of Magic."


translate English day10_ar_40c37f44:


    ar "And now I can't stop shaking...{w} I'm worried I've let you down in so many ways."


translate English day10_ar_6bb023fb:


    pl "I didn't fall in love with you just for your looks, you know.{w} So I won't lose hope in you."


translate English day10_ar_ef285a28:


    ar "...I'm honored you would say so."


translate English day10_ar_1bfc4324:



    nvl clear
    "\n Our alone time that afternoon was short."


translate English day10_ar_f14420d4:


    "It passes in a flash. We don't even leave the room, much less the temple--we just sit on the small sofas,"


translate English day10_ar_a6b2f6e3:


    "talking about silly, pointless things."


translate English day10_ar_3414d32d:


    "We bring topics up as we think of them--old memories, how other people we know are doing, the rumors going around the temple..."


translate English day10_ar_4bf3a979:


    et "And at some point, we start talking about how much we love the other person, and what about them we love--all without any shame."


translate English day10_ar_50d31e01:



    nvl clear
    "\n Eventually, I confess to her about the awful feelings I've been having more and more of towards her.{w} The loneliness, the jealousy, the greed--all of it embarrassing."


translate English day10_ar_b0edd240:


    "Blushing a little, she told me she was happy to hear it."


translate English day10_ar_5c99c805:


    "When I asked why, she grew more embarrassed, then said she wanted me to feel even more greed towards her.{w} I said the same thing."


translate English day10_ar_d8441103:


    "Just like that, I confided in her. Normally, I wouldn't have been able to do this in front of her, and yet I poured all my emotions as if she weren't there. I laughed out loud, and yet still felt lonely."


translate English day10_ar_1ca358f7:


    "There were moments I got worried this was all a dream, too."


translate English day10_ar_f2513bae:


    et "But each time I did, she would hold my hand. That was how we spent the uneventful day together."


translate English day10_ar_1cb30fc2:


    pl "Isn't it time to go back to the others?"


translate English day10_ar_51474c68:


    ar "My, my, the time passed by in a flash, didn't it?"


translate English day10_ar_97edd934:


    pl "That's what happens when you're having fun. I got to talk to you a lot, so I'm pretty satisfied."


translate English day10_ar_72a70eb3:


    ar "It isn't over yet."


translate English day10_ar_508c333b:


    pl "Hm?"


translate English day10_ar_433cf125:


    ar "Did you not say you wanted to be together all day?{w} The day is not yet over."


translate English day10_ar_1b3ebf12:


    ar "Would you like to stay the night upstairs?"


translate English day10_ar_a6382fac:


    pl "Upstairs... I-In your room, you mean?"


translate English day10_ar_7f59d686:


    ar "Ah... Unless you don't want to."


translate English day10_ar_da8f5755:


    pl "N-No, I...{w} I'll come."


translate English day10_ar_5c35fce2:


    ar "...Oh, good.{w} I'm embarrassed to say, but I was worried what I'd do if you refused."


translate English day10_ar_d7d28a9e:


    pl "Would you have brought me there by force?"


translate English day10_ar_8c98e461:


    ar "That was an option."


translate English day10_ar_22b38730:


    pl "Ha ha... You don't need to worry about that."


translate English day10_ar_4852bbd7:


    nar "Probably due to obligations to the other priests, she went to and from the room until later that night."


translate English day10_ar_45440d38:


    nar "I stayed cooped up in her room until everyone else was in bed."


translate English day10_ar_22d69aa8:


    nar "Obviously, I didn't want to leave, since I didn't want to bump into anyone."


translate English day10_ar_b42ee4e9:


    nar "I didn't even want to think of what I'd do tomorrow morning.{w} So I got cozy in her bed, the blanket draped over me."


translate English day10_ar_faa5b090:


    nar "I didn't know if all the Magic Department beds were like this or if hers was just special."


translate English day10_ar_4a503f1b:


    nar "It's a really big bed, though. We could sleep side by side and not touch at all."


translate English day10_ar_7c6c8a5f:


    nar "When I close my eyes, the exhaustion of the day hits me. I recall a lot of things, but I do my best to only think about my time with her."


translate English day10_ar_f65f3bd1:


    nar "She's a wonderful human being.{w} The fact that just believing in her, trusting her, can solve everything has gotta be some form of magic."


translate English day10_ar_a4b35db3:


    nar "I can see why the Magic Department maintains its dignity--it's because a person like her is at the center."


translate English day10_ar_343380cc:


    nar "Suddenly, I awaken and sit up. I look down and see Arnie lying next to me, not moving."


translate English day10_ar_c30abaa3:


    nar "But I can tell she's not asleep yet.{w} A tapered candlestick still burns next to her."


translate English day10_ar_db860596:


    pl "Arnie, you can't just let a guy into your room like that. I can't be held responsible for what happens, you know."


translate English day10_ar_f438bf56:


    ar "Are we not to become husband and wife soon anyway? We must grow accustomed to this."


translate English day10_ar_6bad434a:


    pl "Well, we're not. Not yet. We're essentially still strangers.{w} But you'd be okay no matter what a person like that did to you?"


translate English day10_ar_57b6ea0c:


    ar "Yes. Even if I was unable to achieve my goal of devoting myself to you, my heart would not change."


translate English day10_ar_12f0c3a0:


    ar "And ever since you told me what was hidden in yours, it became like a spike that drove itself into my life."


translate English day10_ar_4632a50d:


    pl "Talk about a noble bride...{w} Well, then what about this?"


translate English day10_ar_2906f287:


    pl "What if I was actually a greedy lunatic, and wanted to kill you, not sleep with you?"


translate English day10_ar_313e6f45:


    ar "What is making you so uneasy, Brother?"


translate English day10_ar_a82786e9:


    pl "I'm scared you'll just die out of nowhere one day."


translate English day10_ar_d1b57de4:


    pl "I don't know if it's a prophecy or fate or whatever. I'm just worried.{w} I mean, just yesterday I had a dream that you died."


translate English day10_ar_3b2cf101:


    ar "A dream where I died?{w} You're exaggerating quite a bit today--though Enoch was too."


translate English day10_ar_5e0eb906:


    ar "I'm happy that you'd worry about me just from having a dream about me, but I won't die."


translate English day10_ar_e3b8100d:


    pl "Hey, but you're the one who said she wasn't scared to die, remember?"


translate English day10_ar_b081a959:


    ar "My thinking hasn't changed, of course.{w} If it is through death I will be acknowledged as the eldest Alternata..."


translate English day10_ar_36516e23:


    ar "...then I will be able to cast off my incompetence. Abiding by the divine revelation is an honor."


translate English day10_ar_846fe8c8:


    ar "However... The reason I've been able to obey such a thing is that the Pestis owns my body."


translate English day10_ar_87e0a542:


    ar "From now on, this body will be yours, and if you wish for me to keep living, then I shall do so."


translate English day10_ar_2af37f3d:


    pl "...Ha. I feel like someone like you really COULD become immortal if you wanted."


translate English day10_ar_46309104:


    ar "Hee hee. I doubt that..."


translate English day10_ar_2ab45a63:


    ar "I sincerely apologize for all the worry I've caused you.{w} But it'll be okay now. It'll all be okay..."


translate English day10_ar_0b87d491:


    nar "Her warm hand touches my cheek. She probably meant to stroke it, but her eyes are still hidden behind her eyelids."


translate English day10_ar_0460c67a:


    nar "It's more like she's feeling out something in a dream; slowly, her hand moves from my cheek to my eyes.{w} And then it slowly falls."


translate English day10_ar_cdb45e78:


    ar "...Oh? Not...crying.{w} Why did I think there were tears...?"


translate English day10_ar_569687b7:


    nar "And then her eyes close fully."


translate English day10_ar_ecceb4d0:


    nar "After her voice faded out, she smoothly fell asleep."


translate English day10_ar_5b3e0bf5:


    nar "Anxious, I hold her hand."


translate English day10_ar_e67a1dc3:


    nar "I sense its warmth, hear the breath from her slightly open mouth, and see her chest rising and falling."


translate English day10_ar_9d692c64:


    nar "I still can't let go of my greed. I want to boast to the world that she's my woman.{w} I want to stay by her side forever, helping her."


translate English day10_ar_d2bba46f:


    nar "To do that, I have to take a step into her life, first.{w} I want to marry her."


translate English day10_ar_8a014348:


    nar "That desire grows stronger the longer I'm with her, but I know I need to give up on it."


translate English day10_ar_0cca4cf5:


    nar "From now on, I need to respect her future, not mine."


translate English day10_ar_bcacdeca:


    nar "My hand joined with hers, I lie back down and put my other hand on the back of hers.{w} Almost in a gesture of prayer."


translate English day10_ar_3459b106:


    nar "...But just as the sleepiness takes over, a knock at the door pulls me right out of it."


translate English day10_ar_741429ff:


    nar "Arnie slowly opens her eyes and sits up.{w} I'm surprised at her reaction speed, but judging by her foggy expression, she WAS definitely asleep."


translate English day10_ar_05ba6fe9:


    nar "Rather than untangle our fingers, she pulls me along."


translate English day10_ar_d1f823de:


    ar "Enter."


translate English day10_ar_f7c34c03:


    en "...It's Enoch.{w} I am so, so sorry to interrupt your time together."


translate English day10_ar_c209ee31:


    pl "What do you want? It's so late."


translate English day10_ar_2f17c554:


    en "I know, but an urgent matter has come up. Arnie and I are being dispatched outside."


translate English day10_ar_0b10cbd1:


    en "It's by the bishop's orders."


translate English day10_ar_eb1e660c_4:


    pl "......"


translate English day10_ar_94d6f50e:


    en "I... I swear, this wasn't on purpose."


translate English day10_ar_3500267c:


    en "I didn't think you'd be asleep already.{w} I'm sorry for waking you up..."


translate English day10_ar_9273e247:


    ar "It's alright, Enoch. I was just resting my eyes a little."


translate English day10_ar_6a688e65:


    ar "The day I received from my uncle is nearing its end, and it is a magician's duty to work for the sake of the people, whether day or night..."


translate English day10_ar_c81d08bb:


    pl "Arnie, are you leaving?"


translate English day10_ar_771a3cfb:


    ar "I will abide by your decision, Brother."


translate English day10_ar_b11b4df9:


    pl "I..."


translate English day10_ar_989670f3_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day10_ar_989670f3_2:


    pl "......"


translate English day10_ar_f22c07b9:


    pl "...It's fine. I needed some sleep anyway. It's important, right? Get going."


translate English day10_ar_5b0f1d5f:


    ar "Very well. I will be back soon, Brother [na2].{w} I apologize for not being able to spend the night with you."


translate English day10_ar_1d2ccdbe:


    pl "U-Uhh, um...{w} What are you even talking about? Just get going!!!"


translate English day10_ar_88229dc3:


    en "Are you sure it's alright...?"


translate English day10_ar_7bc8d24e:


    ar "Yes. Let's quickly prepare."


translate English day10_ar_04b93c21:


    en "Right."


translate English day10_ar_93faf8d0:


    nar "The bed without Arnie is too big--it feels like I'm looking out over an expanse of grassy plains."


translate English day10_ar_4cfd9f66:


    nar "It's still warm where she lay.{w} I can still feel the warmth of her hand in mine."


translate English day10_ar_840304f0:


    nar "In truth, I wanted to stop her, to tell her not to go."


translate English day10_ar_c6140689:


    nar "And I probably could have, too. But I couldn't overlook it--not given what she said about an ideal life, responsibility, and duty."


translate English day10_ar_bdb24aff:


    nar "I'll be a new me tomorrow.{w} I won't only be thinking of myself--I'll be thinking of how we'll live together."


translate English day10_ar_ab09d10f:


    nar "I'll do my best to become someone truly worthy of being with her."


translate English day10_ar_10f79f57:


    nar "But that day would never come."


translate English day10_ar_b46a3f57:


    nar "The next morning, an unfamiliar Magic Department priest knocked on the door and informed me that Arnie had died."


translate English day10_ar_9ae4a83b:


    nar "I soundly slept through her death."


translate English day10_ar_f51203a4:


    nar "I wanted to try hard for her, and yet...{w} The sun is already bright outside, yet Arnie hasn't returned."


translate English day10_ar_7adfc4d2:


    nar "If I had let myself be more childish, if I'd been honest with her and pestered her to stay with me..."


translate English day10_ar_90b552a6:


    nar "Maybe then she wouldn't have died."


translate English day10_ar_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_61f08850:



    nvl clear
    "\n The path is muddy because of the rain that poured all night. Water droplets still hang from the grasses brightening up spots around the temple."


translate English day11_ar_bea1e407:


    "Feeling particular warmth from the wind grazing my face, I look up and see the sun is still bright as ever, high in the sky."


translate English day11_ar_b4c09a1e:


    "Judging by how much the temperature has gone up, they're probably starting to cut down the overgrown weeds back home."


translate English day11_ar_bea5f045:


    "Olive season won't be for a little while--the season of golden flowers blooming from tall, straight trees. If we have a future, we'll probably end up gazing at them, just the two of us."


translate English day11_ar_8af1b71f:



    nvl clear
    "\n The Magic Department priests were running all over the temple earlier this morning, and once noon arrived, there was a small funeral in the training grounds, where tears were shed."


translate English day11_ar_c93f2581:


    "\"We all know where she now goes. Our sister arrived at the end of her path and fought valiantly. Now her travels are complete."


translate English day11_ar_73b66573:


    "We now receive of her soul, which has protected our faith without faltering, without corruption. She is with us always.\""


translate English day11_ar_9a8b0523:


    "After hearing the priests' soft sobs for a little while, I burst out of the training grounds."


translate English day11_ar_24dbd1cd:


    et "It's not because I can't stand the sadness or the anger. It's literally only because Arnie isn't there."


translate English day11_ar_9e92dff0:



    nvl clear
    "\n I'm not sure whether it's just how the temple does things or if she's a special case, but her corpse isn't in the coffin."


translate English day11_ar_093937f7:


    "The funeral only had an empty casket and a framed picture of her in place of her body."


translate English day11_ar_193718e8:


    "The priests, their hands neatly together, all look in the direction of the photograph."


translate English day11_ar_0536f796:


    "Even they must know how ridiculous it is to be praying to an empty coffin."


translate English day11_ar_a0657ab5:


    et "Seeing dozens of people all praying to a little picture makes it seem more like a ceremony to praise God.{w} It's all show, and I don't want to be there anymore."


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_e4a5c072:


    "\n The priests all talk about how they feel holes in their hearts now, but I don't feel lonely.{w} She's still alive in my head."


translate English day11_ar_69d2bdc4:


    "She speaks to me, her voice kind and calm in equal measure."


translate English day11_ar_af0c6d03:


    "I'm the kind of person who acts based on my interests. That's why I believed everyone else would easily deceive others, and that there was always an ulterior motive for their goodwill."


translate English day11_ar_26050d5d:


    et "So, to me, she was the most suspicious of all."


translate English day11_ar_3bb8950c:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"What are you saying? Aren't you also family, Brother [na2]?\""


translate English day11_ar_e6c10127:


    "She repeatedly showed her trust in me, but I kept trying to assign some kind of motive to it."


translate English day11_ar_b050d94a:


    "When I look back on it now, I think I was being naive in a way."


translate English day11_ar_abdbf4dd:


    "All the times I complained to her--those weren't because of any lies she was telling, but more like the suffocating situation making me explode and venting it all on her."


translate English day11_ar_33bdda1d:


    "And I wanted to know how far they would bend over to accept my selfishness.{w} It was pure spite on my part."


translate English day11_ar_7a4ff33b:


    et "In the end, though, I never got to see her angry."


translate English day11_ar_a8ebc0b9:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I want to listen to your desires and grant them if possible. To do so brings me great joy.\""


translate English day11_ar_0b19dfec:


    "If a person needs a reason to fall in love with another person, then there were a million of reasons I could have fallen in love with her."


translate English day11_ar_3fbe3087:


    "If she hadn't fallen in love with me, I probably wouldn't have fallen in love with her either."


translate English day11_ar_50df03ae:


    "But she DID fall in love with me, and that was all the reason I needed."


translate English day11_ar_60a29154:


    et "She had the kindness a human being is supposed to have and the talent to draw out...instinct, or something like that.{w} That's why I loved her."


translate English day11_ar_c3d75428:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I want to know everything about the place in which you were raised.\""


translate English day11_ar_bff132cc:


    et "I really loved her."


translate English day11_ar_b15fbb2d:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Very well, then.{w} I may not be worthy, but please, continue.\""


translate English day11_ar_50fb3f70:


    "I made up all kinds of reasons why she might have started to like me at all, but none of them really mattered."


translate English day11_ar_522756d9:


    "What were money or honor? I taught her how to have fun. I taught her happiness."


translate English day11_ar_19344c06:


    et "I wanted to be happy by her side. I wanted to give her that fun. That was all it was. And yet..."


translate English day11_ar_aae59fa0:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"In this moment, I'm sincerely thinking only of you.\""


translate English day11_ar_a1f3ce1a:


    et "\"If causes for unease still remain in your heart after this answer, then I will do anything to prove it to you.\""


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_cab8eecb:


    "\n I want to see her."


translate English day11_ar_2c1e5fba:


    et "Right then, what I felt was not that I wanted to see her \"again,\" but only that I wanted to see her."


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_bc9cab9e:


    "\n The temple is totally silent, probably because of the funeral. The path I'm on is even quieter.{w} It's a good thing I'm still part of the Cleanup Department. Taking my key out of my pocket, I enter the room labeled \"Morgue.\""


translate English day11_ar_93fc13a6:


    "The cloudy weather is making the room as dark as sunset. For the moment, I take a new candle out of the box next to the entrance and switch it out with my now-dirty candlestick."


translate English day11_ar_900d223f:


    et "As indistinct light fills the room, I see her.{w} She's wearing the same clothes, but there's still dust and dirt on her, as though nobody has been able to clean her up since the accident."


translate English day11_ar_c87718a5:



    nvl clear
    "\n I pick the burial cloth up off her face. It's clean, with no decay, but there's a fresh knife wound on her neck, telling me that she is, in fact, dead. The moment her corpse was discovered, they severed the nerves to her head and body."


translate English day11_ar_ceae36ec:


    "All to prevent her from coming back as one of the Lost. The line in her neck is like the line separating life from death."


translate English day11_ar_994492ca:


    "But she's still so beautiful I almost forget about that obvious fact.{w} While a living human can be beautiful, they can't be called a work of art--because they're still alive."


translate English day11_ar_2bf4cb7c:


    et "But her face, even paler now that death has stolen her vitality, already has an inorganic beauty to it. That's why I'm not sad or horrified--I'm actually moved, feeling like I'm looking at an insane artist's masterpiece."


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_00453c88:


    "\n \"Good morning, Arnie.\""


translate English day11_ar_e6f0de11:


    "And as I greet her, I even feel delight. Not because her corpse is arousing, but because I was able to say something to her that I couldn't before.{w} Looking back, at this point, my heart may have still held some hope, somewhere deep down."


translate English day11_ar_1a91ff69:


    et "So I embrace her. Her body is already cold and stiff, unmoving. She doesn't answer my greeting. But that's okay. The only sound in the room is, vexingly, a single heartbeat."


translate English day11_ar_9e3c482f:



    nvl clear
    "\n It's then that I finally realize that the back of my hand is bleeding.{w} I must have scraped it against something on the way here."


translate English day11_ar_1d12141c:


    "I scoop it up with my thumb and smear it on her lifeless lips.{w} As the hard, rough sensation of her dried lips passes, her face gains just a little bit of life."


translate English day11_ar_1dd90040:


    "According to her, women in the capital color their lips like this before getting married. And they wear a white veil over their faces."


translate English day11_ar_90164cbd:


    et "My attempt is clumsy and awkward, but she sleeps through the whole thing, not saying a word. This must be what dying means."


translate English day11_ar_df4c5b2d:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Ha... Perfect for us, huh?\""


translate English day11_ar_b547419c:


    "Satisfied with my lame attempt, I kiss her on her cold, dead lips."


translate English day11_ar_8e77841b:


    "It's a long, long kiss--probably the first and last one I'll ever experience. It's like drowning in water.{w} A regular kiss would have been fine, but her jaws hang open, offering no resistance."


translate English day11_ar_946fd017:


    "The sound of air going through my nose puts me off, so I take a page from her book and hold my breath for a long while. The bloody, muddy taste spreads through my mouth, and I lick her rubbery tongue. I even bite it a little, but the pliant tongue doesn't move at all."


translate English day11_ar_ad7338f6:


    et "I taste nothing from between her two thin lips. The saliva on her mouth gleans in the light."


translate English day11_ar_79929497:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"......\""


translate English day11_ar_3a18291d:


    et "We need words to be an oath. We need to go through the proper steps, like everyone else."


translate English day11_ar_e2d3e354:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I love you, Arnie.\""


translate English day11_ar_7cc21da9:


    et "That's the first time I've said it out loud, and I only realize it right then and there. I've said it in my head a ridiculous number of times, but I can't help but be shocked that I couldn't actually tell her until now."


translate English day11_ar_0c87925e:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I love you, Arnie. I really do.{w} I love you more than anything!\""


translate English day11_ar_eecfbb2a:


    "I repeat those words until I've memorized them, linking the phrase to similar words."


translate English day11_ar_a056a76b:


    et "I love you. You're the only one for me. I want to marry you. I'd do anything for you... Words like those."


translate English day11_ar_098e9aef:



    nvl clear
    "\n Arnie was deeply moved by each and every one of my flimsy words. She thanked me each time, and considered it an honor."


translate English day11_ar_e2121041:


    et "In truth, I wish I could have thanked her more.{w} Her just being nice to me was an honor. I was so happy for every bit of goodwill she showed me."


translate English day11_ar_b6fdfe22:



    nvl clear
    "\n I put my hand into her now-dirty skirt and stroke her leg. In the place where her stigmata was is a slash the same as the one on her neck.{w} Bodies begin to rot from where they were wounded, so while her skirt covers her calves right now, as time passes, the decay will rise up to her thighs."


translate English day11_ar_65edb78b:


    et "A corpse I saw once before appears in my mind, but I shake my head.{w} I don't need to think about that."


translate English day11_ar_8222f23e:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I was happy when you touched me. When you blinked at me, breathed near me, listened to my words seriously. Every word you spoke helped me so much, and I wanted to become someone wonderful enough to be with you. I wanted to live my life with you...\""


translate English day11_ar_5879c4af:


    "Memories of days past float by behind my eyelids.{w} She promised me so many things."


translate English day11_ar_9061f2e4:


    et "I was her number one. She always looked for my strengths. She always got snacks ready when we had tea together.{w} She spent that whole day with me.{w} And..."


translate English day11_ar_398660eb:



    nvl clear
    "\n She never lied to me. No matter how impossible what she promised to me seemed, she always followed through."


translate English day11_ar_57f42f61:


    "She said she'd live forever, so if I wanted her to live, she'd probably live forever."


translate English day11_ar_b98f56dc:


    et "She's alive. I just have to wish for it. If I wish for her to live...{w} If I can give some of my sacred power to her..."


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88_7:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_c3167019:


    "\n With a cracking noise, the corpse's head falls.{w} It sounds like a wet piece of wood splitting. Her black hair, no longer glossy, sullies the floor."


translate English day11_ar_0f7d39d9:


    "Before the dim candle illuminating the room fades, I turn back to look inside one more time."


translate English day11_ar_d617cac4:


    "There's nothing there that I embraced.{w} Arne Alternata couldn't go against her preordained fate...and died."


translate English day11_ar_5f5966b0:


    "They all said her soul would be with us, but that's just empty comfort meant to let us escape from this unsalvageable reality."


translate English day11_ar_ffc745d9:


    et "I open the door and start walking.{w} There is no soul here. Only a corpse that no longer moves--and its stinging stench."


translate English day11_ar_a12b517e:


    nar "On the path leading outside, he sits on one of the chairs, wearing immaculate clothing."


translate English day11_ar_801eb1d0:


    nar "I'm not used to seeing him so heavy-eyed--he must have been up all night.{w} He frowns when he sees me, immediately sighing."


translate English day11_ar_ba42ab5c:


    en "...Oh, so this is where you were. I was starting to get worried."


translate English day11_ar_18dd568f:


    pl "I'm surprised to see you here too, Enoch."


translate English day11_ar_d60b3e43:


    en "I just wanted to see her face one last time. I know it's not very dignified of me, but..."


translate English day11_ar_972c9435:


    pl "...You were the last one with her, right? Where were you this morning?"


translate English day11_ar_612eeae8:


    en "The hospital.{w} I made a selfish request of my own and asked the Health Department to do everything they possibly could."


translate English day11_ar_eeae5c8e:


    en "But by the time I brought her back last night, she was already..."


translate English day11_ar_249b7d1d:


    en "Ha ha ha. There was just nothing else I could do, I guess..."


translate English day11_ar_f843722e:


    pl "What are you laughing about?"


translate English day11_ar_a463fe78:


    en "It's just... Even at a time like this, I can laugh, I can cry, I can get angry..."


translate English day11_ar_945d1f87:


    en "It really makes me feel alive--and it hurts like hell."


translate English day11_ar_bff956f7:


    nar "He answers without looking at me, his hands clasped all the while.{w} Is he offering a prayer? Or confessing something?"


translate English day11_ar_fb5ff535:


    en "I'm sorry I couldn't protect her."


translate English day11_ar_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day11_ar_72e43a4c:


    en "I was the only one there who could have. Even shaming myself by fleeing in the face of the enemy wasn't enough to save her in the end."


translate English day11_ar_1c143241:


    en "I couldn't even see the enemy coming. It's all my fault."


translate English day11_ar_a4065ebb:


    nar "What are you apologizing for?"


translate English day11_ar_bd6afa74:


    en "You were closer to her than anyone, and I'm sure that just makes it hurt all the more for you."


translate English day11_ar_933ad422:


    en "I'm really, really sorry."


translate English day11_ar_cbba9a92:


    en "As for your departmental transfer, I plan to ask the bishop to handle things with as little fuss as possible."


translate English day11_ar_f570329e:


    en "You're free to stay with the Cleanup Department or leave the temple to do a different job if you'd like."


translate English day11_ar_1dcb45e6:


    nar "Why does he feel the need to console me?{w} Because Arnie's dead?"


translate English day11_ar_4bdd2efe:


    nar "Because he knows I love her?"


translate English day11_ar_66dbd3f0:


    en "You don't need to worry about it. We'll respect whatever decision you make."


translate English day11_ar_2d3661d3:


    en "The Magic Department will wait for your decision until you're able to get your thoughts straight."


translate English day11_ar_650e8057:


    en "I'm sure that's what she would have wanted..."


translate English day11_ar_855df5d4:


    nar "Don't need to worry? I SHOULD be worrying about my position right now, idiot. He probably doesn't know what I was just doing."


translate English day11_ar_ecf182be:


    nar "And it's always been like this. He doesn't know anything, and now that I'm seriously not bothered by any of this, THEN he comes up and says he'll respect my decision?"


translate English day11_ar_95cf2ff7:


    nar "He should be mad, but instead, he's pretending to be generous and tell me it's all going to be okay and not to worry about anything, and that's just such bullshit--he's making me out to be the stupid one that NEEDS consideration."


translate English day11_ar_057a0410:


    nar "It's been like that since the start! You all--your ENTIRE family has always been like that!"


translate English day11_ar_2e02325b:


    pl "Yeah. You did ruin everything, Enoch. You know, it was all going so well, too."


translate English day11_ar_2bef01e5:


    pl "If you loved her that much, you should have just told her so."


translate English day11_ar_41982f35:


    pl "And then you could have envied me for being so young and attractive with a bright future ahead of me."


translate English day11_ar_d2dfab49:


    pl "If you were going to be satisfied by putting yourself in my shoes, you should have just told her."


translate English day11_ar_1b774d6a:


    pl "I mean, the two of us have been getting along just great. I'm the most important one in her life, chosen by God himself."


translate English day11_ar_4cbc3c0c:


    pl "We were gonna get the bishop's blessing, get married, and then buy a huge house in the capital, have kids, and live in peace and happiness."


translate English day11_ar_98af14bd:


    pl "You should have just gotten it over with and gotten rejected, Enoch!"


translate English day11_ar_5e80c14a:


    en "............"


translate English day11_ar_75ff1d67:


    en "[na]...{w} I know you're going through a lot, but you need to accept it."


translate English day11_ar_346607cc:


    en "She's not... She's...!"


translate English day11_ar_044be996:


    pl "I took her virginity."


translate English day11_ar_59769392:


    en "Uh... huh? You... You and her...?{w} Wait. When? Yesterday?"


translate English day11_ar_dd9563ed:


    pl "No, not yesterday.{w} Just now."


translate English day11_ar_67cc0fbf:


    nar "He looks at me blankly, lips trembling for a moment--then immediately shows me a face I've never seen him make."


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88_8:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88_9:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_5f727859:


    "\n And then my head falls straight into the ground, upside-down.{w} My skin stings under the heavy fist pressing into me--and then I stop feeling it at all." with sshake


translate English day11_ar_fd6e1fd5:


    "I hear a noise from the cold floor, and then a roar the likes of which I've never heard before."


translate English day11_ar_b2e94062:


    "\"Let me go!\"" with sshake


translate English day11_ar_f444aff9:


    "His large frame swaying side to side, he kicks me in the legs and stomach, over and over." with sshake


translate English day11_ar_d472a67b:


    et "Given how popular he is at the temple, we've got a big audience again."


translate English day11_ar_2ba0a8ed:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"...You should have never come here, you bastard!!!\""


translate English day11_ar_3d9adca6:


    "That's the only sentence I can make out; his voice is like the roar of a beast just shot in the neck with an arrow." with sshake


translate English day11_ar_4702b6ab:


    "It trembles, given to emotion as it shouts."


translate English day11_ar_0cb5c8d9:


    "Part of me thinks, \"That makes sense.\" But my mouth nearly says \"Why?\""


translate English day11_ar_525a79e2:


    "Or maybe I wanted to say this--\"I can't believe an idiot like you was at her side protecting her this whole time.\"" with sshake


translate English day11_ar_3f12f9b9:


    "Someone like you, who would be violent with someone else with everyone watching..."


translate English day11_ar_cf93ebd9:


    et "But I don't have the time to open my mouth. He grabs my neck, then finally pulls me face to face with him."


translate English day11_ar_792e760a:



    nvl clear
    "\n I can hear sharp breaths escaping his clenched teeth."


translate English day11_ar_b0b595f2:


    "His eyes are opened wide and fully bloodshot, and I get a close look at the nasty gaze he's always kept hidden." with sshake


translate English day11_ar_83924176:


    "Both his eyes are wide, reminding me of blades--and his glare is enough to slice me in two."


translate English day11_ar_070194e0:


    "That aside, his eyeballs are even out of whack with each other. I almost burst out laughing." with sshake


translate English day11_ar_7e10b1a5:


    et "People have told me I'm an outcast, but I finally feel like I understand.{w} At this point, it's like God made me with his left hand."


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88_10:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_a99b7373:


    "\n Warm blood rises through the gaps in my suffocated breathing. I rapidly begin to lose consciousness." with sshake


translate English day11_ar_d401f948:


    "Before I completely go under, I do my best to force out one last yell, but I doubt I was actually able to form words." with sshake


translate English day11_ar_14da1c6f:


    "But I think I got the laughing across, at least."


translate English day11_ar_2a0c439c:


    "Severs you right. Turns out you weren't right for her either.{w} Obviously not--I'm the only one who is." with sshake


translate English day11_ar_cbd7480a:


    et "And I'm the only one who can stay at her side.{w} I'm the one God chose. I'm the one she yearned for."


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88_11:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_ar_faedfdfe:


    "\n And then, finally, I feel like I want to see Arnie again."


translate English day11_ar_76b2fe88_12:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_ar_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_ar_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_ar_d06c1dd2:


    nar "I'm in a cramped, dark space that smells of dust. I squint against the hot, white light coming in through the small window."


translate English day12_ar_a9edb545:


    nar "The floor is cold and my way is blocked by a portcullis. Those at the temple called this insidious place the Sacrament of Penance."


translate English day12_ar_ec986074:


    nar "I hear the creak of the rusted door opening immediately followed by the appearance of a shadowy figure against the bars."


translate English day12_ar_365edb2b:


    nar "The long silhouette, as large as the wall, grows shorter and shorter until the person at last stands in front of me."


translate English day12_ar_12d4362a:


    er "How has life in prison being treating you? Enjoying yourself?"


translate English day12_ar_fc1ca049:


    er "Oh, don't make such an odd face. A problem occurred with the Magic Department's priests, and as their bishop, it's only natural I'd come here."


translate English day12_ar_54c25a36:


    er "Enoch was sent to the abandoned ward for the sin of harming you."


translate English day12_ar_dd9e39ee:


    er "Normally, he would have been sitting right there next to you, but he spoke of some very vulgar matters..."


translate English day12_ar_cc57e2d8:


    er "For an exemplary magician to commit such a barbaric act, he will not escape severe punishment and the stripping of his rank."


translate English day12_ar_100e2532:


    er "I thought I'd raised him like my own son, but apparently, I let my arrogance get the better of me."


translate English day12_ar_c15f3c58:


    er "Either way, this happened because I didn't take good enough care of him."


translate English day12_ar_689392d5:


    er "...That said, [na].{w} From my point of view, Enoch is not the only one who warrants criticism."


translate English day12_ar_ed69352d:


    er "Do you remember our conversation before? When I asked about Arne, you didn't give me an answer."


translate English day12_ar_9bc0b9f2:


    er "What did you feel during your time spent with her?"


translate English day12_ar_15bf0abc:


    er "Did you consider what you'd be able to do for her? Dedicate yourself to becoming a better person?{w} And were those feelings real and true?"


translate English day12_ar_5249951d:


    er "When you grew close with the one you loved, you didn't have any real thoughts about the future, did you?"


translate English day12_ar_fde754dc:


    er "I know you have plenty of other things to look back on. But try taking another good look at yourself.{w} What do you see?"


translate English day12_ar_59fd25c6:


    er "I see a man who is just as weak and lazy as he ever was.{w} Did any of those words you spouted about breaking free of that ever come true?"


translate English day12_ar_ed01ddba:


    hk "Bishop, it's time."


translate English day12_ar_ad61c6bc:


    nar "A woman's low voice cuts Bishop Erzsebet off. He looks away from me and glares at her."


translate English day12_ar_d858101a:


    er "...It is truly regrettable what happened to Arne, especially with it being the work of a yet unidentified phantom killer."


translate English day12_ar_51cbfe4e:


    er "But I already know who the culprit is--indeed, there is no doubt.{w} I will beat them to death.{w} With my own hands. No matter what that should bring."


translate English day12_ar_3909e5d9:


    nar "Without saying anything more, he slowly leaves."


translate English day12_ar_f2df17bc:


    nar "The Cleanup Department bishop watches him go, then comes up to me and gives me a formal smile."


translate English day12_ar_9ad50c4a:


    hk "Hello, Brother. It's my sincerest regret that we have to meet like this."


translate English day12_ar_5b0b8a57:


    hk "But all of this happened because I was never able to properly understand you."


translate English day12_ar_f61bb26a:


    hk "It seems to me that this occurred because I was unable to lead you down the proper path, and for that, I am truly, truly sorry."


translate English day12_ar_8d7292b2:


    hk "I know you must be uneasy about where you are, but there is no need to worry."


translate English day12_ar_116e0e17:


    hk "This is the Sacrament of Penance and Reconciliation. It is not a place to keep you imprisoned. It is a place meant to give you an opportunity to reflect and repent."


translate English day12_ar_1118c559:


    hk "Of course, if fighting with a Magic Department priest was all you had done, the temple would not have handed down much punishment."


translate English day12_ar_6cd9905f:


    hkn "But the sin you must now carry is more than that.{w} And I know you understand this most of all."


translate English day12_ar_aeed48ed:


    hkn "As I also know you understand that you must be punished.{w} It would be easy, of course, to torture you and have you confess to your sins."


translate English day12_ar_687ef10e:


    hkn "But we've kept you alive as a sinner nonetheless.{w} For only by reflecting on one's own sins can one find the true path to repentance."


translate English day12_ar_cfb215a0:


    hkn "What have you learned here at this temple?{w} What was it you truly wanted to do?"


translate English day12_ar_8ef10532:


    hkn "And what should you have done to achieve that?{w} You would do well to ponder these things and repent while there is still time."


translate English day12_ar_989670f3:


    pl "......"


translate English day12_ar_48f5c99e:


    hk "...Farewell, my beloved Brother."


translate English day12_ar_629f2ccd:



    nvl clear
    "\n When she leaves, I'm left completely alone."


translate English day12_ar_d1f7ceb7:


    "Everyone sins."


translate English day12_ar_dfa25b33:


    "Sinless worlds exist only in the realm of angels, and in the capital's words, sins are like those fields.{w} You can avoid them, but you can never resist them."


translate English day12_ar_916b8719:


    "The light shines through the bars, splitting into two before it gets to the wall.{w} One light congratulates the dutiful, wise, good man, while the other punishes the sinner."


translate English day12_ar_b89fd588:


    "Here I am, but I can gaze outside.{w} I could even leave here, if I wanted to."


translate English day12_ar_f9b3ba35:


    et "After all, the bishop left the door to the confessional open."


translate English day12_ar_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_ar_ffd2857e:


    "\n I inhale a bit. I can easily hear it in the quiet.{w} Is this the opportunity for confession that the woman had talked to me about?"


translate English day12_ar_931c623f:


    "Amidst the silence, my once-hidden conscience appears again.{w} The bishop, crushed, has allowed me to reflect on my life thus far."


translate English day12_ar_4f3973f2:


    "It's brutal and it's cold.{w} I can't stand the anguish, and so all I can do is cry and wail."


translate English day12_ar_d306c243:


    "The light overhead slowly shifts, gradually bathing me in its glow.{w} That light connects me to the outside world."


translate English day12_ar_abd8d7cc:


    "I'm more scared of it than anything else, but at the same time, it gently guides the way to my survival--to the salvation of my very soul."


translate English day12_ar_6ed2d0ea:


    "It's so brilliant, blinding.{w} Here I am once again--trapped in a Hell within a Paradise."


translate English day12_ar_5015be07:


    et "Which light should I look at? Which light should I chase?"


translate English day12_ar_bd7cb410:



    nvl clear
    "\n The tears are still falling. I feel as though they'll never stop.{w} Her face is clear and vivid in my mind."


translate English day12_ar_56add34b:


    et "Each time I remember her, I feel as though I grow more ugly and cowardly.{w} If this pain is to be my punishment, then I'll..."


translate English day12_ar_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_ar_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_ar_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English ar_end_1_e951837e:


    nar "A moment later, the unbearable terror wells up, almost like bile from my stomach." with sshake


translate English ar_end_1_f3dec803:


    nar "I suddenly realize that swallowing it is part of my reflection."


translate English ar_end_1_58a2c47e:


    nar "Until now, all I've been doing is wailing and wallowing in regret--I haven't reflected at all."


translate English ar_end_1_1c170081:


    nar "But now, I can accept everything.{w} Arnie is dead.{w} The two of us will never be united as one."


translate English ar_end_1_683182ff:


    nar "The pounding of my heart returns to its regular speed.{w} I look back on the sins I've committed.{w} They're heavy and they're ugly, but they're mine."


translate English ar_end_1_04e210fa:


    nar "Nobody will make this weigh less for me.{w} I can't abandon any of it, even if I told someone else.{w} The angel was an illusion, born of my own human cowardice."


translate English ar_end_1_1405ec32:


    nar "I can properly feel the regret and pain now.{w} Instead of blaming anyone else, I sigh and think to myself--I did this."


translate English ar_end_1_f4b52724:


    nar "And it's time to admit to myself that there WAS a choice--and I chose to do this."


translate English ar_end_1_6d3c68fe:


    nar "I can't forgive myself. All that's left for me now is to live with the guilt--forever."


translate English ar_end_1_e710726a:


    nar "Death cannot remove that weight from me.{w} Instead, I make an oath never to forget this agony."


translate English ar_end_1_14cdab1c:


    nar "Even if my life is short, even if I can never get back lost time, if I had just one chance to do it over..."


translate English ar_end_1_69c3abde:


    nar "If I did, then..."


translate English ar_end_1_3459b106:


    nar "...But just as the sleepiness takes over, a knock at the door pulls me right out of it."


translate English ar_end_1_741429ff:


    nar "Arnie slowly opens her eyes and sits up.{w} I'm surprised at her reaction speed, but judging by her foggy expression, she WAS definitely asleep."


translate English ar_end_1_05ba6fe9:


    nar "Rather than untangle our fingers, she pulls me along."


translate English ar_end_1_d1f823de:


    ar "Enter."


translate English ar_end_1_f7c34c03:


    en "...It's Enoch.{w} I am so, so sorry to interrupt your time together."


translate English ar_end_1_c209ee31:


    pl "What do you want? It's so late."


translate English ar_end_1_2f17c554:


    en "I know, but an urgent matter has come up. Arnie and I are being dispatched outside."


translate English ar_end_1_0b10cbd1:


    en "It's by the bishop's orders."


translate English ar_end_1_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English ar_end_1_94d6f50e:


    en "I... I swear, this wasn't on purpose."


translate English ar_end_1_3500267c:


    en "I didn't think you'd be asleep already.{w} I'm sorry for waking you up..."


translate English ar_end_1_9273e247:


    ar "It's alright, Enoch. I was just resting my eyes a little."


translate English ar_end_1_6a688e65:


    ar "The day I received from my uncle is nearing its end, and it is a magician's duty to work for the sake of the people, whether day or night..."


translate English ar_end_1_c81d08bb:


    pl "Arnie, are you leaving?"


translate English ar_end_1_771a3cfb:


    ar "I will abide by your decision, Brother."


translate English ar_end_1_b11b4df9:


    pl "I..."


translate English ar_end_1_1eb3240c:


    pl "...I want you to stay here, Arnie.{w} I know best of all I'm being selfish! But..."


translate English ar_end_1_b3ba2752:


    pl "But the day isn't over yet, right? Spend it with me, just this one day...{w} Please don't go, Arnie."


translate English ar_end_1_851182f6:


    ar "...Brother [na2]."


translate English ar_end_1_56104b1f:


    ar "...If that is what you wish, then I have no reason to leave your side."


translate English ar_end_1_25c7eed4:


    pl "...!!!"


translate English ar_end_1_751f4555:


    ar "Enoch. Unfortunately, I have business to handle tonight as well, and will likely not be able to accompany you.{w} Can you handle this?"


translate English ar_end_1_a8d09835:


    en "Oh, uh... Yes, of course!"


translate English ar_end_1_4c736c2d:


    en "...How should I put this? That makes me kind of happy."


translate English ar_end_1_49d1a548:


    en "You've really never thought about doing anything for anyone but the bishop and the Magic Department, so I guess maybe you never understood what YOU wanted to do..."


translate English ar_end_1_4fc9213f:


    en "I was really worried you'd never enjoy anything for your own sake."


translate English ar_end_1_763ba3c7:


    en "But seeing you this happy finally sets my mind at ease!"


translate English ar_end_1_af4c451c:


    ar "So you say, right in front of me."


translate English ar_end_1_ded623ae:


    pl "Well, it's true--she's a stubborn one.{w} Anyway... Thanks, Enoch."


translate English ar_end_1_65299065:


    pl "You, well... You really do like Arnie, huh?"


translate English ar_end_1_b4bcf09e:


    en "...Yes."


translate English ar_end_1_9c201991:


    extend " Wait, no, I'm the one who should be thanking you! Thank you for showing her the way."


translate English ar_end_1_9d0e9668:


    en "I just had a pretty bad dream recently, so I've been nervous..."


translate English ar_end_1_9063eb0b:


    en "Anyway, you can leave the rest to me--Enoch Apis!"


translate English ar_end_1_6c280cdc:


    nar "The door closes, shutting the room back into silence."


translate English ar_end_1_36990d7c:


    nar "I tighten my grip on her hand and look at her.{w} She smiles at me, the same as she always does."


translate English ar_end_1_669bb0bf:


    nar "......"


translate English ar_end_1_b9888692:


    nar "...Clap!"


translate English ar_end_1_864c47aa:


    nar "The clap of a hand wakes me up. The artificial light in the training grounds fills my blurry vision.{w} Apparently I fell sound asleep here."


translate English ar_end_1_908436da:


    ar "Brother?"


translate English ar_end_1_7fe05ad0:


    nar "As I try to get my eyes to focus, the woman I love speaks to me.{w} I replay her voice over and over in my head."


translate English ar_end_1_e3868a54:


    ar "Are you awake?"


translate English ar_end_1_3e385a24:


    nar "And then I hug her.{w} Everything I can see is bright, but I could see it all clearly."


translate English ar_end_1_af6f14a0:


    pl "Good morning, Arnie."


translate English ar_end_1_5c5dac12:


    nar "I finally said the words threatening to burst out of me. In her warmth, she stiffens a little, confused, but eventually hugs me back.{w} I can feel her heartbeat."


translate English ar_end_1_f5307288:


    ar "Good morning, Brother."


translate English ar_end_1_19192cff:


    pl "Mm, yeah... Morning."


translate English ar_end_1_de6f9916:


    ar "Hee hee hee. It seems like you've become a bit spoiled.{w} Did you have a nightmare?"


translate English ar_end_1_9c881337:


    pl "I don't know... I just wanted to see you as soon as I could."


translate English ar_end_1_6b4c72b4:


    ar "Oh, that is a problem. In that case, you can be assured that Arne Alternata will stay by your side always--until you are satisfied."


translate English ar_end_1_ad70a07d:


    en "...Umm... Sorry to interrupt this little scene, but the father-in-law is here, right?"


translate English ar_end_1_53721d1b:


    er "Oh, just leave them. They're getting along swimmingly, aren't they?{w} Read the room and step out of the way--that's for the best."


translate English ar_end_1_9d2fcc9e:


    pl "Wh-What the heck?! If you were with him, at least make yourself known!" with sshake


translate English ar_end_1_ec028b88:


    en "Well, I... I've been here from the start."


translate English ar_end_1_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English ar_end_1_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English ar_end_1_5ea29b86:


    en "Anyway, who cares! The bishop's right--don't mind us. Continue!"


translate English ar_end_1_07f830ea:


    pl "You can say stuff like that all you want, but--{w} W-Wait, Arnie, you can let go of me now!"


translate English ar_end_1_43bfc2bf:


    ar "Are you embarrassed to be with me?"


translate English ar_end_1_8b600926:


